#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:48
msgid ""
"Next is the :guilabel:`Prompt` field. In Odoo, :ref:`prompts <ai/agents/"
"prompts-in-odoo>` define the instructions that guide the |AI| when "
"generating or improving the content of the |AI| field. The prompt tells the "
"system what kind of information to produce, how to format it, and what tone "
"or style to use."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje je polje :guilabel:`Poziv`. V Odoo :ref:`pozivi <ai/agents/prompts-"
"in-odoo>` opredelijo navodila, ki vodijo |AI| pri ustvarjanju ali "
"izboljševanju vsebine polja |AI|. Poziv sistemu pove, kakšno vrsto "
"informacij naj ustvari, kako naj jih oblikuje in kakšen ton ali slog naj "
"uporabi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:53
msgid ""
"When creating a prompt, use the `/field` command to reference specific "
"fields in the database. For example, to reference the :guilabel:`Company` "
"field on a record, enter `/field`, and click the :guilabel:`Field Selector` "
"option. Type `Company` in the search bar, and select :guilabel:`Company` "
"from the list."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju poziva uporabite ukaz `/field` za sklicevanje na določena "
"polja v podatkovni bazi. Na primer, za sklicevanje na "
"polje :guilabel:`Podjetje` na zapisu vnesite `/field` in kliknite "
"možnost :guilabel:`Izbirnik polja`. V iskalno vrstico vnesite `Company` in s "
"seznama izberite :guilabel:`Podjetje`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:None
msgid "The add a field pop-up where the ai prompt is entered."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno za dodajanje polja, kjer je vnesen poziv umetne inteligence."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:61
msgid ""
"Once the prompt is complete, click :guilabel:`Add Field`. Before closing "
"**Studio**, click on the left sidebar and update the :guilabel:`Label` field "
"with a title for the new |AI| field. Then click :guilabel:`Close` to exit "
"**Studio**."
msgstr ""
"Ko je poziv dokončan, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj polje`. Preden zaprete "
"**Studio**, kliknite na levo stransko vrstico in posodobite "
"polje :guilabel:`Oznaka` z naslovom za novo polje |AI|. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Zapri`, da zapustite **Studio**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:65
msgid ""
"After the field is added, click the |AI| icon to refresh the field value."
msgstr "Ko je polje dodano, kliknite ikono |AI|, da osvežite vrednost polja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:68
msgid ""
"If the |AI| is unable to complete the request, a warning message is "
"generated. This could mean that the prompt is asking for information that is "
"not available, in the given context, or that the prompt is providing unclear "
"instructions. Use this as an indication to revisit the prompt and add "
"additional context or instructions."
msgstr ""
"Če |AI| ne more dokončati zahteve, se ustvari opozorilno sporočilo. To lahko "
"pomeni, da poziv zahteva informacije, ki niso na voljo v danem kontekstu, "
"ali da poziv podaja nejasna navodila. To uporabite kot znak, da ponovno "
"pregledate poziv in dodate dodatni kontekst ali navodila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:0
msgid "A warning message indicating the AI was unable to complete the request."
msgstr "Opozorilno sporočilo, ki nakazuje, da UI ni mogla dokončati zahteve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:79
msgid "Add via edit properties"
msgstr "Dodajanje prek urejanja lastnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:81
msgid ""
"|AI| fields can also be added as property fields without opening the "
"**Studio** app. Click on the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` icon and "
"select :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`Edit Properties`. Tick the :guilabel:`AI` "
"checkbox, confirm the field should be |AI|-enabled, then follow the "
"steps :ref:`above <ai/add-a-new-field>` to define the field type and enter "
"the prompt."
msgstr ""
"Polja |AI| je mogoče dodati tudi kot polja lastnosti, ne da bi odprli "
"aplikacijo **Studio**. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in "
"izberite :icon:`fa-cogs` :guilabel:`Uredi lastnosti`. Označite potrditveno "
"polje :guilabel:`UI`, potrdite, da naj bo polje omogočeno za |AI|, nato "
"sledite korakom :ref:`zgoraj <ai/add-a-new-field>`, da opredelite vrsto "
"polja in vnesete poziv."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:None
msgid "The edit properties pop-up on a form view."
msgstr "Pojavno okno za urejanje lastnosti v obrazcu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:90
msgid ""
":ref:`Property fields <property_field/add>` can only be added to form views."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Polja lastnosti <property_field/add>` je mogoče dodati samo v poglede "
"obrazcev."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:93
msgid "Computing AI fields"
msgstr "Izračunavanje polj UI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:95
msgid ""
"To compute, or refresh, an |AI| field, click on the |AI| icon next to the "
"field. Clicking the button updates the field based on the prompt."
msgstr ""
"Za izračun ali osvežitev polja |AI| kliknite ikono |AI| poleg polja. Klik na "
"gumb posodobi polje na podlagi poziva."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:98
msgid ""
"Additionally, a scheduled action runs once a day to fill text and property |"
"AI| fields that are currently empty. This action is active by default."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega se enkrat na dan izvede načrtovano dejanje za izpolnjevanje "
"besedilnih polj in polj lastnosti |AI|, ki so trenutno prazna. To dejanje je "
"privzeto aktivno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/fields.rst:102
msgid ""
"To run the scheduled action manually, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings "
"app --> Technical --> Automation --> Scheduled Actions`. Click "
"on :guilabel:`AI Fields\\:\\ Compute AI fields` to open it, then "
"click :guilabel:`Run Manually`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ročno zagnati načrtovano dejanje, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Avtomatizacija --> "
"Načrtovana dejanja`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Polja UI\\:\\ Izračunaj polja UI`, "
"da ga odprete, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Zaženi ročno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:3
msgid "Write and improve text with AI"
msgstr "Pisanje in izboljšanje besedila z AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo |AI| can assist with writing and refining text across the database. "
"This makes it easier to draft emails, improve existing content, and quickly "
"extract key information from discussions or notes."
msgstr ""
"Odoo |AI| lahko pomaga pri pisanju in izboljševanju besedila v celotni "
"zbirki podatkov. To olajša pripravo osnutkov e-pošte, izboljšanje obstoječe "
"vsebine in hitro pridobivanje ključnih informacij iz razprav ali zapiskov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:11
msgid ""
"|AI| writing features are available in most rich-text environments in Odoo, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"Funkcije pisanja |AI| so na voljo v večini okolij za obogateno besedilo v "
"Odoo, vključno z:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:13
msgid "*Description* and *Notes* fields on records"
msgstr "Polja *Opis* in *Opombe* v zapisih"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:14
msgid "Email composers and email templates"
msgstr "Urejevalniki e-pošte in predloge e-pošte"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:15
msgid "**Knowledge** articles"
msgstr "Članki v **Znanju**"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:17
msgid ""
"These features are accessible through the text editor and the :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`, depending on the context."
msgstr ""
"Te funkcije so dostopne prek urejevalnika besedila in :ref:`powerboxa "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`, odvisno od konteksta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "A knowledge article with the AI improve text option visible."
msgstr "Članek znanja s prikazano možnostjo izboljšanja besedila z AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:24
msgid "Writing with AI"
msgstr "Pisanje z AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:26
msgid ""
"|AI| can generate new text based on a short prompt or partial input. This is "
"useful for drafting content such as emails, task descriptions, or internal "
"notes."
msgstr ""
"|AI| lahko ustvari novo besedilo na podlagi kratkega poziva ali delnega "
"vnosa. To je uporabno za osnutke vsebin, kot so e-poštna sporočila, opisi "
"opravil ali notranja opomba."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:29
msgid ""
"To generate text, either click the |AI| icon, or type `/` to open the "
"powerbox, and select :guilabel:`AI` from the drop-down menu. Both options "
"open a conversation window. Enter a short prompt describing the desired "
"content, then click the :icon:`fa-paper-plane-o` :guilabel:`(paper plane)` "
"icon. After the text is generated, hover over the response and "
"click :guilabel:`Use this` to add the content to the desired field or "
"document. Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-copy` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon "
"to copy the text to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje besedila kliknite ikono |AI| ali vnesite `/` za odpiranje "
"powerboxa in izberite :guilabel:`AI` iz spustnega menija. Obe možnosti "
"odpreta pogovorno okno. Vnesite kratek poziv z opisom želene vsebine in nato "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-paper-plane-o` :guilabel:`(papirnat letalček)`. Ko "
"je besedilo ustvarjeno, se premaknite nad odziv in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi to`, da dodate vsebino v želeno polje ali "
"dokument. Druga možnost je klikniti ikono :icon:`fa-"
"copy` :guilabel:`(kopiranje)`, da kopirate besedilo v odložišče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "A conversation window with an AI agent generating content."
msgstr "Pogovorno okno z agentom AI, ki ustvarja vsebino."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:39
msgid ""
"If unsatisfied with the content, send a follow-up message to the agent with "
"an expanded prompt or suggested changes."
msgstr ""
"Če niste zadovoljni z vsebino, pošljite nadaljnje sporočilo agentu z "
"razširjenim pozivom ali predlaganimi spremembami."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:43
msgid "Improving existing text"
msgstr "Izboljšanje obstoječega besedila"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:45
msgid ""
"|AI| can also be used to rewrite or improve existing text. This includes:"
msgstr ""
"|AI| lahko uporabite tudi za prepisovanje ali izboljšanje obstoječega "
"besedila. To vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:47
msgid "Making text clearer or more concise"
msgstr "Narediti besedilo jasnejše ali jedrnato"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:48
msgid "Adjusting tone or structure"
msgstr "Prilagajanje tona ali strukture"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:49
msgid "Correcting grammar or phrasing"
msgstr "Popravljanje slovnice ali fraziranja"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:51
msgid ""
"Select the text to improve, then click the |AI| icon to open a conversation "
"window. Click the :guilabel:`Rewrite selected` prompt. After the text is "
"generated, hover over the response and click :guilabel:`Use this` to add the "
"content to the desired field or document. Alternatively, click the :icon:`fa-"
"copy` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon to copy the text to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Izberite besedilo za izboljšanje in nato kliknite ikono |AI|, da odprete "
"pogovorno okno. Kliknite poziv :guilabel:`Prepiši izbrano`. Ko je besedilo "
"ustvarjeno, se premaknite nad odziv in kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi to`, da "
"dodate vsebino v želeno polje ali dokument. Druga možnost je klikniti "
"ikono :icon:`fa-copy` :guilabel:`(kopiranje)`, da kopirate besedilo v "
"odložišče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:None
msgid "The rewrite selected text in a conversation window."
msgstr "Prepisovanje izbranega besedila v pogovornem oknu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:60
msgid ""
"To add custom instructions to the prompt, such as suggestions on tone or "
"content, write the prompt directly in the conversation window. For example, "
"`Rewrite the selected text in a more professional tone`."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje lastnih navodil pozivu, kot so predlogi glede tona ali vsebine, "
"napišite poziv neposredno v pogovorno okno. Na primer, `Prepiši izbrano "
"besedilo v bolj profesionalnem tonu`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:65
msgid "Best practices for AI-assisted writing"
msgstr "Najboljše prakse za pisanje s pomočjo AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:67
msgid "For best results when using |AI| to write or improve text:"
msgstr ""
"Za najboljše rezultate pri uporabi |AI| za pisanje ali izboljševanje "
"besedila:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:69
msgid "Provide clear and specific context in prompts"
msgstr "Zagotovite jasen in specifičen kontekst v pozivih"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:70
msgid "Review AI-generated content before saving or sending"
msgstr "Preglejte vsebino, ustvarjeno z AI, pred shranjevanjem ali pošiljanjem"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:71
msgid "Adjust wording to match the company's tone and communication standards"
msgstr ""
"Prilagodite besedilo, da se ujema s tonom podjetja in standardi komunikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/improve_text.rst:73
msgid ""
"|AI|-assisted writing is designed to support productivity, while final "
"review and validation remain essential."
msgstr ""
"Pisanje s pomočjo |AI| je zasnovano za podporo produktivnosti, medtem ko sta "
"končni pregled in preverjanje še vedno ključna."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:3
msgid "AI live chat"
msgstr "AI klepet v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:5
msgid ""
"Odoo's **AI** application can be integrated with **Live Chat** to enable "
"agents to automatically respond to customer inquiries, qualify "
"conversations, and generate leads. When connected to a live chat channel, an "
"AI agent can answer common questions, request additional information, and "
"determine when a conversation needs to be escalated to a human operator."
msgstr ""
"Odoo aplikacija **AI** se lahko poveže z aplikacijo **Klepet v živo**, da "
"omogoči agentom samodejno odgovarjanje na poizvedbe strank, kvalificiranje "
"pogovorov in ustvarjanje potencialnih strank. Ko je agent povezan s kanalom "
"klepeta v živo, lahko AI agent odgovarja na pogosta vprašanja, zahteva "
"dodatne informacije in določi, kdaj je treba pogovor eskalirati k človeškemu "
"operaterju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:10
msgid ""
"AI responses are generated in real-time and follow the rules and "
"instructions defined in the assigned agent and topics."
msgstr ""
"AI odgovori so ustvarjeni v realnem času in sledijo pravilom ter navodilom, "
"določenim v dodeljenem agentu in temah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:14
msgid "Connecting an agent to live chat"
msgstr "Povezovanje agenta s klepetom v živo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:16
msgid ""
"First, confirm that both the **Live Chat** and **AI** applications are "
"installed."
msgstr ""
"Najprej potrdite, da sta nameščeni obe aplikaciji **Klepet v živo** in "
"**AI**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:19
msgid ""
"When both the **AI** and **Live Chat** apps are installed, a *Livechat AI "
"Agent* is added to the **AI** app. Other agents can be created and used for "
"live chat conversations, if desired."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta nameščeni aplikaciji **UI** in **Spletni klepet**, je agentu **UI** "
"dodan *Agent spletnega klepeta UI*. Po želji je mogoče ustvariti in "
"uporabiti druge agente za pogovore spletnega klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:0
msgid "The preconfigured AI Live Chat agent in the AI app."
msgstr "Vnaprej konfiguriran agent UI za spletni klepet v aplikaciji UI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:25
msgid ""
"Navigate to the **Live Chat** application and select a live chat channel. On "
"the channel card, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical "
"ellipsis)` icon, then click :guilabel:`Configure Channel`."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se do aplikacije **Spletni klepet** in izberite kanal spletnega "
"klepeta. Na kartici kanala kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`(navpične tropičje)`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj "
"kanal`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:29
msgid ""
"On the channel page, click on the :guilabel:`Rules` tab. Click on an "
"existing rule, or click :guilabel:`Add a line` to add a new rule. On the "
"*Open: Rules* pop-up, click in the :guilabel:`AI Agent` field, and select an "
"agent from the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"Na strani kanala kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Pravila`. Kliknite obstoječe "
"pravilo ali kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da dodate novo pravilo. V "
"pojavnem oknu *Odpri: Pravila* kliknite v polje :guilabel:`Agent UI` in iz "
"spustnega menija izberite agenta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:None
msgid "The rules pop-up window in the live chat app."
msgstr "Pojavno okno pravil v aplikaciji za spletni klepet."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:37
msgid ""
"If a channel has both a chatbot and an AI Agent assigned, the priority is "
"given to the AI agent workflow."
msgstr ""
"Če ima kanal dodeljen tako klepetalni robot kot agent UI, ima prednost potek "
"dela agenta UI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:41
msgid "Configuring AI behavior in live chat"
msgstr "Konfiguracija obnašanja UI v spletnem klepetu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:43
msgid ""
"The behavior and actions of the AI agent during a live chat conversation are "
"controlled through the agent's settings.  To configure the :doc:`agent "
"<agents>`, navigate to the :menuselection:`AI app --> Agents`. On the agent "
"card, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon, "
"then click :guilabel:`Configuration`."
msgstr ""
"Obnašanje in dejanja agenta UI med pogovorom spletnega klepeta se "
"nadzorujejo prek nastavitev agenta. Za konfiguracijo :doc:`agenta <agents>` "
"se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija UI --> Agenti`. Na kartici agenta "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpične tropičje)`, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguracija`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:48
msgid ""
"As the default *Livechat AI Agent* is configured to work with live chat, "
"this section lays out how the agent's prompt is used in a live chat "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Ker je privzeti *Agent spletnega klepeta UI* konfiguriran za delo s spletnim "
"klepetom, ta razdelek opisuje, kako se poziv agenta uporablja v pogovoru "
"spletnega klepeta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:52
msgid "Agent identity and goals"
msgstr "Identiteta in cilji agenta"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:54
msgid ""
"The *Livechat AI Agent* identity helps define the agent's communication "
"style and conversation goals. At a high level, the agent is focused on "
"answering customer questions accurately, while also being responsible for "
"initiating lead creation when a request cannot be handled confidently."
msgstr ""
"Identiteta *Agenta spletnega klepeta UI* pomaga opredeliti komunikacijski "
"slog agenta in cilje pogovora. Na visoki ravni je agent osredotočen na "
"natančno odgovarjanje na vprašanja strank, hkrati pa je odgovoren za začetek "
"ustvarjanja potencialnih strank, ko zahteve ni mogoče obravnavati zanesljivo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:58
msgid ""
"Rather than reacting message-by-message, the agent evaluates each "
"interaction against its defined priorities."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da bi reagiral od sporočila do sporočila, agent vsako interakcijo "
"ocenjuje glede na svoje opredeljene prednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:62
msgid "How the agent answers questions"
msgstr "Kako agent odgovarja na vprašanja"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:64
msgid ""
"During a conversation, each incoming message is evaluated against the "
"agent's decision rules. When sufficient information is available, the agent "
"responds directly with a clear and concise answer."
msgstr ""
"Med pogovorom se vsako prejeto sporočilo ovrednoti glede na pravila "
"odločanja agenta. Ko so na voljo zadostne informacije, agent neposredno "
"odgovori z jasnim in jedrnатим odgovorom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:67
msgid ""
"If the available information is incomplete or uncertain, the agent does not "
"guess or fabricate a response. Instead, it acknowledges the limitation and "
"prepares to transition the conversation toward human follow-up."
msgstr ""
"Če so razpoložljive informacije nepopolne ali negotove, agent ne ugiba ali "
"izmišlja odgovora. Namesto tega prizna omejitev in pripravi prehod pogovora "
"proti človeškemu spremljanju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:71
msgid "This ensures that automated responses remain accurate and trustworthy."
msgstr ""
"To zagotavlja, da samodejni odgovori ostanejo natančni in zaupanja vredni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:74
msgid "How escalation is triggered"
msgstr "Kako se sproži eskalacija"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:76
msgid ""
"Escalation to human follow-up is defined explicitly in the agent's prompt "
"and delegated to a dedicated topic."
msgstr ""
"Eskalacija k človeškemu spremljanju je eksplicitno opredeljena v pozivu "
"agenta in delegirana na namenskeno temo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:79
msgid "Conversations are escalated when one of the following occurs:"
msgstr "Pogovori se eskalirajo, ko pride do enega od naslednjega:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:81
msgid "The request requires custom pricing, contracts, or implementation work."
msgstr "Zahteva zahteva prilagojene cene, pogodbe ali izvedbeno delo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:82
msgid "The request involves account changes or troubleshooting."
msgstr "Zahteva vključuje spremembe računa ali odpravljanje težav."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:83
msgid "The user explicitly asks to be contacted or requests a demo."
msgstr "Uporabnik izrecno prosi, da ga kontaktirate, ali zahteva predstavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:84
msgid "The agent cannot respond with high confidence."
msgstr "Agent ne more odgovoriti z visoko zanesljivostjo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:86
msgid ""
"When one of these conditions is met, the agent activates the *Lead "
"Creation* :ref:`topic <ai/topics>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izpolnjen eden od teh pogojev, agent aktivira temo *Ustvarjanje "
"priložnosti* :ref:`topic <ai/topics>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:90
msgid "Lead creation topic"
msgstr "Tema ustvarjanja priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:92
msgid ""
"The Lead creation topic defines a structured, multi-step workflow that "
"governs how contact information is collected and how a lead is created."
msgstr ""
"Tema ustvarjanja priložnosti opredeljuje strukturiran večstopenjski potek "
"dela, ki določa, kako se zbirajo kontaktne informacije in kako se ustvari "
"priložnost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:95
msgid "This topic specifies:"
msgstr "Ta tema določa:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:97
msgid "when lead creation is appropriate"
msgstr "kdaj je ustvarjanje priložnosti primerno"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:98
msgid "what information must be collected"
msgstr "katere informacije je treba zbrati"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:99
msgid "how the conversation should progress"
msgstr "kako naj se pogovor nadaljuje"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:100
msgid "what language the agent may and may not use"
msgstr "kateri jezik sme in ne sme uporabljati agent"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:102
msgid ""
"Rather than immediately creating a lead, the agent completes the following "
"steps:"
msgstr ""
"Namesto da bi takoj ustvaril priložnost, agent izvede naslednje korake:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:104
msgid "Suggests human follow-up when appropriate"
msgstr "Po potrebi predlaga nadaljnje ukrepanje s strani človeka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:105
msgid "Collects missing contact details one at a time"
msgstr "Zbira manjkajoče kontaktne podatke enega po enega"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:106
msgid "Confirms known details before proceeding"
msgstr "Potrdi znane podatke pred nadaljevanjem"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:107
msgid "Calls the lead creation tool exactly once"
msgstr "Enkrat pokliče orodje za ustvarjanje priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:109
msgid ""
"The topic also enforces strict constraints to prevent system-centric "
"language, duplicate lead creation, or premature promises of follow-up."
msgstr ""
"Tema prav tako uvaja stroge omejitve, da prepreči sistemsko usmerjen jezik, "
"podvojeno ustvarjanje priložnosti ali predčasne obljube o nadaljnjih ukrepih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:112
msgid ""
"To view the detailed instructions for the lead creation topic, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`AI app --> Agents --> Topics`, and "
"click :guilabel:`Create Leads`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ogledati podrobna navodila za temo ustvarjanja priložnosti, "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`AI app --> Agents --> Topics` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Create Leads`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/live-chat.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:133
msgid ":doc:`AI Agents <agents>`"
msgstr ":doc:`AI Agents <agents>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:3
msgid "AI server actions"
msgstr "Strežniška dejanja AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:7
msgid ""
"|AI| server actions extend Odoo's automation framework by allowing "
"artificial intelligence to make decisions during a workflow."
msgstr ""
"Strežniška dejanja |AI| razširjajo ogrodje Odoo za avtomatizacijo tako, da "
"omogočajo umetni inteligenci sprejemanje odločitev med potekom dela."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:10
msgid ""
"They are designed for cases where logic cannot be expressed entirely through "
"fixed conditions, but still requires controlled execution through standard "
"server actions."
msgstr ""
"Zasnovana so za primere, kjer logike ni mogoče v celoti izraziti s fiksnimi "
"pogoji, vendar še vedno zahteva nadzorovano izvajanje prek standardnih "
"strežniških dejanj."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:14
msgid "How AI server actions work"
msgstr "Kako delujejo strežniška dejanja AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:16
msgid ""
"AI-driven workflows in Odoo are built around a clear separation of "
"responsibilities between the |AI| server action, or *the Manager*, and the "
"tool, or *the Worker*."
msgstr ""
"Delovni tokovi, ki jih poganja AI, so v Odoo zgrajeni okoli jasne razdelitve "
"odgovornosti med strežniškim dejanjem |AI| oziroma *Upraviteljem* in orodjem "
"oziroma *Delavcem*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:20
msgid "AI server action: the manager"
msgstr "Dejanje strežnika AI: upravitelj"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:22
msgid ""
"An |AI| server action acts as a decision maker, or a manager. It reads the "
"record and its context. It interprets the |AI| prompt. And it decides which "
"tool to call, and what arguments to use."
msgstr ""
"Dejanje strežnika |AI| deluje kot odločevalec ali upravitelj. Prebere zapis "
"in njegov kontekst. Interpretira poziv |AI|. In odloči, katero orodje "
"poklicati ter katere argumente uporabiti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:25
msgid ""
"The server action does not enforce business rules, modify records directly, "
"or guarantee the correctness of the operation. Its role is limited to "
"decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Dejanje strežnika ne uveljavlja poslovnih pravil, ne spreminja zapisov "
"neposredno in ne zagotavlja pravilnosti operacije. Njegova vloga je omejena "
"na odločanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:29
msgid "AI tool: the worker"
msgstr "Orodje AI: izvajalec"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:31
msgid ""
"A tool is a standard server action with the *Use in AI* option enabled in "
"its *Usage* tab. Tools contain all execution logic and perform record "
"updates, moves, or writes. Tools **must** enforce business rules explicitly "
"in Python code."
msgstr ""
"Orodje je standardno dejanje strežnika z omogočeno možnostjo *Uporabi v AI* "
"na zavihku *Uporaba*. Orodja vsebujejo vso logiko izvajanja ter izvajajo "
"posodobitve, premike ali zapise zapisov. Orodja **morajo** eksplicitno "
"uveljavljati poslovna pravila v kodi Python."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:35
msgid ""
"If a tool is called by the |AI| server action, it will execute "
"unconditionally, unless the code itself prevents it."
msgstr ""
"Če dejanje strežnika |AI| pokliče orodje, se bo to izvedlo brezpogojno, "
"razen če koda sama tega ne prepreči."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:39
msgid "AI server action workflow"
msgstr "Potek dela dejanja strežnika AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:41
msgid "The |AI| server action workflow follows this sequence:"
msgstr "Potek dela dejanja strežnika |AI| sledi temu zaporedju:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:43
msgid "A record triggers an |AI| server action."
msgstr "Zapis sproži dejanje strežnika |AI|."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:44
msgid "The |AI| prompt is evaluated, using the record as context."
msgstr "Poziv |AI| se ovrednoti z uporabo zapisa kot konteksta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:45
msgid "The |AI| selects one of the available tools."
msgstr "|AI| izbere eno od razpoložljivih orodij."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:46
msgid "The |AI| provides arguments expected by the tool."
msgstr "|AI| zagotovi argumente, ki jih orodje pričakuje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:47
msgid "The selected tool executes its Python code."
msgstr "Izbrano orodje izvede svojo kodo Python."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:50
msgid ""
"|AI| server actions work without custom logic only when the underlying "
"behavior already exists in Odoo, such as moving a document to a folder. In "
"these cases, the |AI| selects parameters, and Odoo executes the action."
msgstr ""
"Dejanja strežnika |AI| delujejo brez logike po meri samo, ko osnovno "
"obnašanje že obstaja v Odoo, na primer premikanje dokumenta v mapo. V teh "
"primerih |AI| izbere parametre, Odoo pa izvede dejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:55
msgid "Use case walkthrough"
msgstr "Predstavitev primera uporabe"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:57
msgid ""
"The *Auto-sort documents in Inbox* example demonstrates the full |AI| Server "
"Action pattern. Navigate to the *Server Actions* menu by going "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Technical --> Server Actions`."
msgstr ""
"Primer *Samodejno razvrsti dokumente v mapi Prejeto* prikazuje celoten "
"vzorec dejanja strežnika |AI|. Do menija *Dejanja strežnika* se pomaknite "
"tako, da greste na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Dejanja "
"strežnika`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:62
msgid ""
"This server action is designed to review documents for their content, and "
"add tags. The action itself does **not** move documents or add tags, it only "
"decides which tool should be used, based on the documents' content."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje strežnika je zasnovano za pregled vsebine dokumentov in dodajanje "
"oznak. Dejanje samo **ne** premika dokumentov ali dodaja oznak, temveč samo "
"odloči, katero orodje naj se uporabi, glede na vsebino dokumentov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:66
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Model` for the action is listed as *Document*, and "
"the :guilabel:`Type` is *AI*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Model` za dejanje je naveden kot *Dokument*, :guilabel:`Vrsta` pa "
"je *AI*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:None
msgid "The record for the Auto-sort documents in inbox server action."
msgstr "Zapis dejanja strežnika Samodejno razvrsti dokumente v mapi Prejeto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:71
msgid ""
"The prompt for this action provides context about the document, as well as "
"intent of the action."
msgstr "Poziv za to dejanje zagotavlja kontekst o dokumentu ter namen dejanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:73
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Tool` field includes several actions that may be taken based "
"on this prompt, including moving a document, adding tags, or creating "
"invoices or bills."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Orodje` vključuje več dejanj, ki se lahko izvedejo na "
"podlagi tega poziva, vključno s premikanjem dokumenta, dodajanjem oznak ali "
"ustvarjanjem računov ali predračunov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:77
msgid ""
"*AI: Add Tags*, *AI: Move to Folder*, and *AI: Rename Document* are all "
"*Execute Code* server actions, meaning they trigger python code."
msgstr ""
"*AI: Dodaj oznake*, *AI: Premakni v mapo* in *AI: Preimenuj dokument* so vsa "
"strežniška dejanja tipa *Izvedi kodo*, kar pomeni, da sprožijo pythonovo "
"kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:80
msgid ""
"For example, if the action determines, based on the content of the document, "
"that the most appropriate tool is *AI: Move to Folder*, the Python code "
"performs the following operation:"
msgstr ""
"Na primer, če dejanje na podlagi vsebine dokumenta določi, da je "
"najprimernejše orodje *AI: Premakni v mapo*, pythonova koda izvede naslednjo "
"operacijo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:87
msgid ""
"This code, executes unconditionally when called and performs the move using "
"an existing method."
msgstr ""
"Ta koda se izvede brezpogojno, ko je klicana, in izvede premik z uporabo "
"obstoječe metode."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:90
msgid ""
"The |AI| does not infer arguments from the Python code or from the method "
"signature. Instead, arguments passed to a tool are determined entirely by "
"the tool's configuration."
msgstr ""
"|AI| ne sklepa argumentov iz pythonove kode ali iz podpisa metode. Namesto "
"tega so argumenti, posredovani orodju, v celoti določeni s konfiguracijo "
"orodja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:93
msgid ""
"For the *AI: Move to Folder* tool, the Python code expects a variable named "
"`folder_id`. The |AI| knows to provide `folder_id` because it is explicitly "
"declared as an argument in the configuration. This can be found on the "
"*Usage* tab of the server action, in the :guilabel:`AI Schema` field. "
"The :guilabel:`Name` column under *AI Schema* must match the variable name "
"used in the Python code exactly."
msgstr ""
"Za orodje *AI: Premakni v mapo* pythonova koda pričakuje spremenljivko z "
"imenom `folder_id`. |AI| ve, da mora zagotoviti `folder_id`, ker je ta "
"eksplicitno deklariran kot argument v konfiguraciji. To najdete na zavihku "
"*Uporaba* strežniškega dejanja v polju :guilabel:`Shema AI`. "
"Stolpec :guilabel:`Ime` pod *Shema AI* se mora popolnoma ujemati z imenom "
"spremenljivke, uporabljeno v pythonovi kodi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:99
msgid ""
"The |AI| uses the argument description to understand what the parameter "
"represents, what type of value is expected, and when it is appropriate to "
"supply it."
msgstr ""
"|AI| uporablja opis argumenta za razumevanje, kaj parameter predstavlja, "
"kakšna vrsta vrednosti se pričakuje in kdaj je primerno, da ga zagotovi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:102
msgid ""
"If an argument is not defined in the Usage tab, the AI cannot provide it, "
"even if the Python code references it."
msgstr ""
"Če argument ni definiran na zavihku Uporaba, ga AI ne more zagotoviti, tudi "
"če se nanj sklicuje pythonova koda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:0
msgid "The usage tab of the AI move to folder server action."
msgstr "Zavihek uporabe strežniškega dejanja AI premakni v mapo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:109
msgid "Creating custom AI tools"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje orodij AI po meri"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:111
msgid ""
"The same pattern in the *Auto-sort documents in Inbox* example above can be "
"implemented using standard Odoo logic. For example, to create an action that "
"can update a task description, an *Execute Code* action could be created "
"with the following code:"
msgstr ""
"Enak vzorec v zgornjem primeru *Samodejno razvrsti dokumente v mapi Prejeto* "
"se lahko implementira z uporabo standardne Odoo logike. Na primer, za "
"ustvarjanje dejanja, ki lahko posodobi opis opravila, se lahko ustvari "
"dejanje *Izvedi kodo* z naslednjo kodo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:119
msgid ""
"To function correctly, `content` **must** be defined as an argument in "
"tool's *Usage* tab."
msgstr ""
"Da deluje pravilno, **mora** biti `content` definiran kot argument na "
"zavihku *Uporaba* orodja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:122
msgid ":ref:`Server Actions <reference/actions/server>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Strežniška dejanja <reference/actions/server>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:125
msgid "Common issues"
msgstr "Pogoste težave"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:128
msgid "Why is the Tools field empty?"
msgstr "Zakaj je polje Orodja prazno?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:130
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one server action has :guilabel:`Use in AI` enabled."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite, da ima vsaj eno strežniško dejanje omogočeno "
"možnost :guilabel:`Uporabi v AI`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:131
msgid ""
"Confirm that at least one tool is assigned to the same "
"model :guilabel:`Model` as the server action."
msgstr ""
"Potrdite, da je vsaj eno orodje dodeljeno istemu modelu :guilabel:`Model` "
"kot strežniško dejanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:135
msgid "Why did the tool run but nothing happened?"
msgstr "Zakaj se je orodje zagnalo, a se ni zgodilo nič?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:137
msgid "The Python code exited without changes."
msgstr "Pythonova koda se je zaključila brez sprememb."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:138
msgid "Required arguments were missing or empty."
msgstr "Zahtevani argumenti so manjkali ali so bili prazni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:139
msgid "Business conditions were not implemented in the tool logic."
msgstr "Poslovni pogoji niso bili implementirani v logiko orodja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:142
msgid "Why did the AI choose an unexpected tool?"
msgstr "Zakaj je UI izbral nepričakovano orodje?"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:144
msgid "The prompt lacked sufficient context."
msgstr "Poziv ni vseboval zadostnega konteksta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:145
msgid "Multiple tools matched the same intent."
msgstr "Več orodij se je ujemalo z istim namenom."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/server-actions.rst:146
msgid "No constraints were enforced at the tool level."
msgstr "Na ravni orodja niso bile uveljavljene nobene omejitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:3
msgid "AI in support workflows"
msgstr "UI v delovnih procesih podpore"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:7
msgid ""
"Utilizing Odoo's |AI| features in the **Helpdesk** app assists support "
"agents with their tasks, rather than replacing existing workflows. The goal "
"is to reduce repetitive tasks, accelerate ticket handling, and improve "
"consistency by allowing |AI| to analyze ticket content and suggest or "
"execute actions automatically."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba funkcij |AI| Odoo v aplikaciji **Služba za pomoč** pomaga agentom "
"podpore pri njihovih nalogah, namesto da bi nadomestila obstoječe delovne "
"procese. Cilj je zmanjšati ponavljajoče se naloge, pospešiti obravnavo "
"zahtevkov in izboljšati doslednost tako, da |AI| analizira vsebino zahtevkov "
"ter samodejno predlaga ali izvaja dejanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:12
msgid ""
"Instead of manually categorizing, prioritizing, and responding to every "
"request, support teams can rely on |AI| to interpret incoming information "
"and perform preliminary processing. Agents remain in control of decisions "
"and customer communication, while |AI| handles repetitive analysis and "
"drafting."
msgstr ""
"Namesto da bi ročno kategorizirala, določala prednost in odgovarjala na "
"vsako zahtevo, se lahko ekipe za podporo zanesejo na |AI|, da interpretira "
"prejete informacije in izvede predhodno obdelavo. Agenti ohranijo nadzor nad "
"odločitvami in komunikacijo s strankami, medtem ko |AI| obravnava "
"ponavljajoče se analize in osnutke."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:18
msgid "How AI works in Helpdesk"
msgstr "Kako UI deluje v Službi za pomoč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:20
msgid "|AI| capabilities in **Helpdesk** are built around three core ideas:"
msgstr ""
"Zmogljivosti |AI| v **Službi za pomoč** temeljijo na treh osnovnih idejah:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:22
msgid ""
"|AI| agents that interact with users or agents and generate responses based "
"on knowledge sources."
msgstr ""
"Agenti |AI|, ki komunicirajo z uporabniki ali agenti in generirajo odgovore "
"na podlagi virov znanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:23
msgid ""
"|AI| automations that update tickets automatically when records are created "
"or modified."
msgstr ""
"Avtomatizacije |AI|, ki samodejno posodabljajo zahtevke, ko so zapisi "
"ustvarjeni ali spremenjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:24
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields that generate structured information, such as summaries, "
"from unstructured text."
msgstr ""
"Polja, omogočena z |AI|, ki generirajo strukturirane informacije, kot so "
"povzetki, iz nestrukturiranega besedila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:30
msgid ""
"An |AI| agent is a configurable assistant that operates using prompts and "
"contextual knowledge. The agent itself does not contain business logic; "
"instead, it follows instructions defined by users and relies on provided "
"documentation."
msgstr ""
"Agent |AI| je nastavljiv pomočnik, ki deluje z uporabo pozivov in "
"kontekstualnega znanja. Agent sam ne vsebuje poslovne logike; namesto tega "
"sledi navodilom, ki jih določijo uporabniki, in se zanaša na priloženo "
"dokumentacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:34
msgid ""
"When an agent receives a request, it combines its system :ref:`prompt <ai/"
"agents/prompts-in-odoo>`, the current record context (such as a ticket), and "
"its knowledge :ref:`sources <ai/sources>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko agent prejme zahtevo, združi svoj sistemski :ref:`poziv <ai/agents/"
"prompts-in-odoo>`, kontekst trenutnega zapisa (kot je zahtevek) in "
"svoje :ref:`vire <ai/sources>` znanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:37
msgid ""
"This allows the agent to provide responses grounded in internal "
"documentation rather than generic language model output."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča agentu zagotavljanje odgovorov, utemeljenih na interni "
"dokumentaciji, namesto generičnega izpisa jezikovnega modela."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:40
msgid ""
"Agents can be restricted to specific sources or granted permissions to "
"perform actions using topics. This ensures that support assistants behave "
"predictably and remain aligned with organizational rules."
msgstr ""
"Agente je mogoče omejiti na določene vire ali jim podeliti dovoljenja za "
"izvajanje dejanj z uporabo tem. To zagotavlja, da se pomočniki za podporo "
"obnašajo predvidljivo in ostanejo usklajeni s pravili organizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:45
msgid "AI automations"
msgstr "Avtomatizacije UI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:47
msgid ""
"Automation rules allow |AI| to act during record lifecycle events. Instead "
"of waiting for an agent to categorize or prioritize tickets, |AI| can "
"perform these tasks automatically as soon as a ticket is created."
msgstr ""
"Pravila avtomatizacije omogočajo, da |AI| deluje med dogodki življenjskega "
"cikla zapisa. Namesto da bi čakala, da agent kategorizira ali določi "
"prednost zahtevkom, lahko |AI| te naloge izvede samodejno takoj, ko je "
"zahtevek ustvarjen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:51
msgid ""
"The key principle is that |AI| does not understand Odoo models directly. It "
"receives text extracted from fields and produces an output based on prompt "
"instructions. Users guide |AI| behavior through clear prompting and "
"carefully selected input fields."
msgstr ""
"Ključno načelo je, da |AI| ne razume modelov Odoo neposredno. Prejme "
"besedilo, pridobljeno iz polj, in ustvari izhod na podlagi navodil poziva. "
"Uporabniki vodijo obnašanje |AI| z jasnimi pozivi in skrbno izbranimi "
"vhodnimi polji."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:58
msgid ""
"|AI| enabled fields extend standard Odoo fields by allowing their values to "
"be generated automatically through prompts."
msgstr ""
"Polja, omogočena z |AI|, razširjajo standardna polja Odoo tako, da je mogoče "
"njihove vrednosti samodejno generirati s pozivi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:61
msgid ""
"These fields are useful when large amounts of text need to be condensed into "
"actionable information. For example, a long customer message can "
"automatically be summarized into a short list of key points, allowing agents "
"to understand issues quickly without reading full descriptions."
msgstr ""
"Ta polja so uporabna, kadar je treba velike količine besedila strniti v "
"uporabne informacije. Na primer, dolgo sporočilo stranke je mogoče samodejno "
"povzeti v kratek seznam ključnih točk, kar agentom omogoča, da hitro "
"razumejo težave brez branja celotnih opisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:69
msgid "Configuring an AI agent for support"
msgstr "Konfiguracija agenta AI za podporo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:71
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`agents <agents>` are configured in the **AI** application. To "
"configure an existing agent, navigate to :menuselection:`AI app` and click "
"the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` icon, then "
"click :guilabel:`Configuration` on the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`agenti <agents>` so konfigurirani v aplikaciji **AI**. Za "
"konfiguracijo obstoječega agenta se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"AI` in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tri-"
"pičje)`, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Konfiguracija` v spustnem meniju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:75
msgid ""
"Configuring begins by selecting a language model and defining a system "
"prompt describing how the agent should behave. The prompt determines tone, "
"scope, and responsibility. A support-focused agent might be instructed to "
"analyze issues and provide concise technical responses."
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracija se začne z izbiro jezikovnega modela in opredelitvijo "
"sistemskega poziva, ki opisuje, kako naj se agent obnaša. Poziv določa ton, "
"obseg in odgovornost. Agent, osredotočen na podporo, je lahko navodovan, da "
"analizira težave in zagotovi jedrnate tehnične odgovore."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:79
msgid ""
"The next step is defining the agent's *sources*. These :ref:`sources <ai/"
"sources>` form the agent's memory and should contain trusted documentation "
"such as product guides or FAQs. The quality of these sources directly "
"impacts the quality of AI responses."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji korak je opredelitev *virov* agenta. Ti :ref:`viri <ai/sources>` "
"tvorijo spomin agenta in morajo vsebovati zaupanja vredno dokumentacijo, kot "
"so vodniki za izdelke ali pogosta vprašanja. Kakovost teh virov neposredno "
"vpliva na kakovost odgovorov AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Restrict to Sources` to require the agent to **only** base "
"their responses on the supplied resources."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Omeji na vire`, da zahtevate, da agent svoje odgovore "
"osnuje **samo** na podanih virih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:87
msgid ""
"Users may also define *topics*, which grant the agent permission to perform "
"specific actions. :ref:`Topics <ai/topics>` allow advanced scenarios such as "
"record creation or automation triggers."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko opredelijo tudi *teme*, ki agentu dajejo dovoljenje za "
"izvajanje določenih dejanj. :ref:`Teme <ai/topics>` omogočajo napredne "
"scenarije, kot so ustvarjanje zapisov ali sprožilci avtomatizacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "An example support AI agent."
msgstr "Primer agenta AI za podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:93
msgid ""
"Once an agent exists, *default prompts* can be used to initiate a "
"conversation."
msgstr ""
"Ko agent obstaja, je mogoče uporabiti *privzete pozive* za začetek pogovora."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:95
msgid ""
"A default prompt defines where and when the |AI| appears inside Odoo. In the "
"**Helpdesk** app, this typically means allowing the |AI| button to appear on "
"ticket records. The default prompt specifies the model where it is "
"available, which agent is called, and additional contextual instructions."
msgstr ""
"Privzeti poziv določa, kje in kdaj se |AI| pojavi v Odoo. V aplikaciji "
"**Služba za pomoč** to običajno pomeni, da se gumb |AI| lahko prikaže na "
"zapisih zahtevkov. Privzeti poziv določa model, kjer je na voljo, kateri "
"agent je klican, in dodatna kontekstualna navodila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:None
msgid "A list of default prompts assigned to the Support Agent."
msgstr "Seznam privzetih pozivov, dodeljenih agentu za podporo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:102
msgid ""
"These instructions act as a second layer on top of the agent prompt, "
"adapting the agent's behavior to **Helpdesk** scenarios."
msgstr ""
"Ta navodila delujejo kot druga plast poleg poziva agenta in prilagajajo "
"vedenje agenta scenarijem **Službe za pomoč**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:106
msgid "Configuring AI automations"
msgstr "Konfiguracija avtomatizacij AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:108
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`server actions <server-actions>` are configured using standard "
"automated actions, with |AI| used as the update mechanism."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`strežniška dejanja <server-actions>` so konfigurirana z uporabo "
"standardnih avtomatiziranih dejanj, pri čemer se |AI| uporablja kot "
"mehanizem posodabljanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:111
msgid ""
"When defining a server action, users specify when the action should run, "
"such as when a new ticket is created. The |AI| prompt then explains how the "
"ticket should be interpreted and which field should be updated."
msgstr ""
"Pri opredelitvi strežniškega dejanja uporabniki določijo, kdaj naj se "
"dejanje izvede, na primer ko je ustvarjen nov zahtevek. Poziv |AI| nato "
"pojasni, kako naj se zahtevek interpretira in katero polje naj se posodobi."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:115
msgid ""
"This approach keeps automation predictable while allowing |AI| to make "
"contextual decisions."
msgstr ""
"Ta pristop ohranja avtomatizacijo predvidljivo, medtem ko omogoča |AI|, da "
"sprejema kontekstualne odločitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:118
msgid "Configuring AI fields"
msgstr "Konfiguracija polj AI"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:120
msgid ""
"|AI| :doc:`fields <fields>` are configured by enabling the |AI| option on a "
"custom or property field and providing a prompt describing the expected "
"result. Once configured, the field updates automatically when the record "
"changes, giving agents instant access to structured information."
msgstr ""
"|AI| :doc:`polja <fields>` so konfigurirana z omogočanjem možnosti |AI| na "
"polju po meri ali polju lastnosti in zagotavljanjem poziva, ki opisuje "
"pričakovani rezultat. Ko je konfigurirano, se polje samodejno posodobi, ko "
"se zapis spremeni, kar agentom omogoči takojšen dostop do strukturiranih "
"informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:125
msgid ""
"|AI| fields can be added to a record through the **Studio** app or property "
"field. :ref:`Installing Studio <general/install>` may impact the current "
"pricing plan for a database."
msgstr ""
"|AI| polja je mogoče dodati zapisu prek aplikacije **Studio** ali polja "
"lastnosti. :ref:`Namestitev aplikacije Studio <general/install>` lahko "
"vpliva na trenutni cenovni načrt za bazo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:128
msgid ""
"For more information, refer to `Odoo's pricing page <https://www.odoo.com/"
"pricing-plan>`_ or contact your account manager."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij glejte `cenik Odoo <https://www.odoo.com/pricing-plan>`_ "
"ali se obrnite na vašega vodjo računa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:132
msgid ":doc:`AI Fields <fields>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Polja AI <fields>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/support_operations.rst:134
msgid ":doc:`AI Server Actions <server-actions>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Dejanja AI Server <server-actions>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:3
msgid "AI voice transcription"
msgstr "Prepisovanje glasu z umetno inteligenco"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo |AI| can transcribe spoken audio into text and generate summaries from "
"that transcript. This feature supports both meeting recordings and real-time "
"dictation, making it easier to capture notes, decisions, and action items "
"without manual typing."
msgstr ""
"Odoo |AI| lahko pretvori govorjeni zvok v besedilo in iz prepisa ustvari "
"povzetke. Ta funkcija podpira tako posnetke sestankov kot narekovanje v "
"realnem času, kar olajša zajemanje zapiskov, odločitev in opravil brez "
"ročnega tipkanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:11
msgid ""
"Voice transcription converts spoken audio into a written transcript. Once a "
"transcript is available, Odoo |AI| can generate a summary that highlights "
"key information, such as:"
msgstr ""
"Prepisovanje glasu pretvori govorjeni zvok v pisni prepis. Ko je prepis na "
"voljo, lahko Odoo |AI| ustvari povzetek, ki poudari ključne informacije, kot "
"so:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:14
msgid "key discussion points"
msgstr "ključne točke razprave"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:15
msgid "decisions"
msgstr "odločitve"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:16
msgid "action items"
msgstr "opravila"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:17
msgid "next steps"
msgstr "naslednji koraki"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:19
msgid ""
"Transcription and summarization can be used for meetings, calls, quick "
"dictations, and internal notes."
msgstr ""
"Prepisovanje in povzemanje je mogoče uporabiti za sestanke, klice, hitro "
"narekovanje in interne zapiske."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:23
msgid ""
"Voice transcripts can be created in the *Description* and *Notes* fields of "
"most records, as well as in **Knowledge** articles."
msgstr ""
"Glasovne prepise je mogoče ustvariti v poljih *Opis* in *Opombe* večine "
"zapisov ter v člankih **Knowledge**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:0
msgid "The powerbox in the description tab of a task in the Projects app."
msgstr "Okno z ukazi na zavihku opisa opravila v aplikaciji Projects."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:29
msgid ""
"Voice transcription works by temporarily recording audio during the session, "
"replaying it for transcription, and generating a written transcript and "
"summary. Once the transcription process is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded. The recorded audio is not stored, replayable, or "
"accessible from the database."
msgstr ""
"Prepisovanje glasu deluje tako, da začasno posname zvok med sejo, ga "
"predvaja za prepisovanje in ustvari pisni prepis ter povzetek. Ko je "
"postopek prepisovanja končan, se zvočni posnetek samodejno zavrže. Posneti "
"zvok ni shranjen, ga ni mogoče predvajati ali dostopati do njega iz zbirke "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:35
msgid "Transcribe a meeting"
msgstr "Prepis sestanka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:37
msgid ""
"To create a voice transcript, type `/` to open the :ref:`powerbox "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`. Select :guilabel:`Voice Transcript` from "
"the drop-down list. This creates a new text block. Click :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`Notes` to add notes and details regarding the meeting. This "
"is where information, such as a meeting agenda and attendees, can be added. "
"Click :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transcript` to switch to a live view "
"of the transcript being created in real-time."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje glasovnega prepisa vnesite `/`, da odprete :ref:`okno z ukazi "
"<essentials/html_editor/commands>`. S spustnega seznama "
"izberite :guilabel:`Voice Transcript`. To ustvari nov besedilni blok. "
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-bars` :guilabel:`Notes`, da dodate zapiske in podrobnosti "
"o sestanku. Tu lahko dodate informacije, kot so dnevni red sestanka in "
"udeleženci. Kliknite :icon:`fa-microphone` :guilabel:`Transcript`, da "
"preklopite na pogled v živo prepisa, ki nastaja v realnem času."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:44
msgid ""
"When the meeting is ready to begin, click :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start "
"Recording`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je sestanek pripravljen za začetek, kliknite :icon:`fa-"
"circle` :guilabel:`Začni snemanje`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:47
msgid ""
"Clicking :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Start Recording` may cause a pop-up in "
"the browser, requesting access to a microphone. If permission is not given, "
"the recording stops, and an error message appears. To combat this error, "
"refresh the page and allow Odoo access to the microphone."
msgstr ""
"Klik na :icon:`fa-circle` :guilabel:`Začni snemanje` lahko v brskalniku "
"povzroči pojavno okno z zahtevo za dostop do mikrofona. Če dovoljenje ni "
"podano, se snemanje ustavi in prikaže se sporočilo o napaki. Za odpravo te "
"napake osvežite stran in dovolite Odoo-ju dostop do mikrofona."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:51
msgid ""
"When the meeting has ended, click :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Stop "
"Recording`. The recorded audio is then processed to generate a transcript "
"and an |AI| summary. Once processing is complete, the audio recording is "
"automatically discarded, leaving only the transcript and summary available."
msgstr ""
"Ko se sestanek konča, kliknite :icon:`fa-stop` :guilabel:`Ustavi snemanje`. "
"Posneti zvok se nato obdela za ustvarjanje prepisa in |AI| povzetka. Ko je "
"obdelava končana, se zvočni posnetek samodejno zavrže, na voljo ostaneta le "
"prepis in povzetek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:None
msgid "The AI summary of a meeting transctipt."
msgstr "Povzetek sestanka s prepisom, ki ga ustvari AI."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/ai/voice.rst:58
msgid ""
"The |AI| summary can be manually edited to provide additional insight, such "
"as identifying meeting attendees by name, or specifying key points. The "
"meeting notes can then be converted into an email recap, or shared directly "
"via email by clicking the :guilabel:`Share by email` button."
msgstr ""
"Povzetek |AI| je mogoče ročno urediti, da se zagotovijo dodatne informacije, "
"kot so identifikacija udeležencev sestanka po imenu ali določitev ključnih "
"točk. Zapiski sestanka se nato lahko pretvorijo v e-poštni povzetek ali "
"delijo neposredno po e-pošti s klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Deli po e-pošti`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:6
msgid "Appointments"
msgstr "Termini"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:8
msgid ""
"Odoo's **Appointments** app is a self-service scheduling app that simplifies "
"the process of booking meetings, consultations, or services. Integrated with "
"Odoo's suite of business apps, it allows companies to automate appointment "
"scheduling, reduce manual coordination, and provide a seamless experience "
"for clients. Appointments can be linked to calendars, **CRM** opportunities, "
"employee schedules, and more, making it an ideal tool for service-based "
"businesses seeking efficiency and organization."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Sestanki** od Odoo je samopostrežna aplikacija za razporejanje, "
"ki poenostavi postopek rezervacije sestankov, posvetovanj ali storitev. "
"Integrirana z Odoovim paketom poslovnih aplikacij omogoča podjetjem "
"avtomatizacijo razporejanja sestankov, zmanjšanje ročnega usklajevanja in "
"zagotavljanje nemotenega procesa za stranke. Sestanki se lahko povežejo s "
"koledarji, priložnostmi v **CRM**, urniki kadra in drugimi elementi, kar "
"aplikacijo naredi idealno orodje za storitveno naravnana podjetja, ki iščejo "
"učinkovitost in organiziranost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:18
msgid ""
"The **Appointments** app allows for new appointments to be scheduled based "
"on the availability of users, or the availability of *resources*, such as "
"meeting rooms or seating areas. To create a new resource, or manage existing "
"resources, navigate to :menuselection:`Appointments --> Configuration --> "
"Resources`. This opens a list of the available resources in the database, as "
"well as their individual capacity."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Sestanki** omogoča razporejanje novih sestankov na podlagi "
"razpoložljivosti uporabnikov ali razpoložljivosti *virov*, kot so sejne sobe "
"ali sedeži. Za ustvarjanje novega vira ali upravljanje obstoječih virov se "
"pomaknite na :menuselection:`Sestanki --> Konfiguracija --> Viri`. Odpre se "
"seznam razpoložljivih virov v bazi podatkov skupaj z njihovo posamezno "
"zmogljivostjo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:27
msgid "Resources"
msgstr "Viri"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:29
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to create a new resource. On the blank record, enter "
"a :guilabel:`Name` for the new resource. In the :guilabel:`Capacity` field, "
"enter the maximum number of people the resource can accommodate. Then, "
"confirm the :guilabel:`Timezone` for this resource."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite nov vir. V prazen zapis "
"vnesite :guilabel:`Ime` za nov vir. V polje :guilabel:`Zmogljivost` vnesite "
"največje število oseb, ki jih lahko vir sprejme. Nato "
"potrdite :guilabel:`Časovni pas` za ta vir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:33
msgid ""
"If desired, select one or more :guilabel:`Linked Resource` from the drop-"
"down. This option designates one or more resources that can be used in "
"combination to handled a bigger demand."
msgstr ""
"Če želite, v spustnem meniju izberite enega ali več :guilabel:`Povezanih "
"virov`. Ta možnost določa enega ali več virov, ki se lahko uporabljajo v "
"kombinaciji za obvladovanje večjega povpraševanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:37
msgid ""
"*Linked resources* are only used when using the :ref:`auto-assign "
"<appointments/configure>` :guilabel:`Assignment Method`."
msgstr ""
"*Povezani viri* se uporabljajo le pri uporabi :ref:`samodejne dodelitve "
"<appointments/configure>` kot :guilabel:`Metode dodeljevanja`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:40
msgid ""
"Lastly, add a :guilabel:`Description` for this resource. The contents of "
"the :guilabel:`Description` tab are visible to customers when booking an "
"appointment online."
msgstr ""
"Na koncu dodajte :guilabel:`Opis` za ta vir. Vsebina "
"zavihka :guilabel:`Opis` je vidna strankam pri spletnem rezerviranju "
"sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:44
msgid "Resource capacity"
msgstr "Kapaciteta vira"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:46
msgid ""
"When booking an appointment based on resource availability, the website only "
"displays capacity up to `12`. This occurs even if the resource has a higher "
"capacity. To avoid this, a new *System Parameter* needs to be added to the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Pri rezervaciji sestanka na podlagi razpoložljivosti vira spletna stran "
"prikaže kapaciteto samo do `12`. To se zgodi, tudi če ima vir višjo "
"kapaciteto. Da bi se temu izognili, je treba v podatkovno bazo dodati nov "
"*sistemski parameter*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:50
msgid ""
"First, ensure that :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` is enabled. Then, "
"navigate to the :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical --> Parameters --"
"> System Parameters`. Click :guilabel:`New` to add a new parameter."
msgstr ""
"Najprej preverite, ali je omogočen :ref:`razvijalski način <developer-"
"mode>`. Nato se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> "
"Parametri --> Sistemski parametri`. Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da dodate nov "
"parameter."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:54
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Key` field, enter "
"`appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed`. In the :guilabel:`Value` field, "
"enter the maximum capacity that should be allowed. Click :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Save manually)` when finished."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Ključ` vnesite "
"`appointment.resource_max_capacity_allowed`. V polje :guilabel:`Vrednost` "
"vnesite največjo dovoljeno kapaciteto. Ko končate, kliknite :icon:`fa-cloud-"
"upload` :guilabel:`(Shrani ročno)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:None
msgid "The new system parameter for capacity limits."
msgstr "Nov sistemski parameter za omejitve kapacitete."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:64
msgid "Appointment type configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija vrste sestanka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:66
msgid ""
"Before appointments can be scheduled or booked, an appointment type must be "
"created. Navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` app dashboard and "
"click :guilabel:`New`. On the new blank record, enter "
"an :guilabel:`Appointment Title`, then set a :guilabel:`Duration` for this "
"appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Preden je mogoče razporejati ali rezervirati sestanke, je treba ustvariti "
"vrsto sestanka. Pomaknite se na nadzorno plošo "
"aplikacije :menuselection:`Sestanki` in kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`. V nov "
"prazen zapis vnesite :guilabel:`Naslov sestanka`, nato "
"nastavite :guilabel:`Trajanje` za to vrsto sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:70
msgid ""
"Next, set a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time`. This is the minimum amount of time "
"between when an appointment can be booked and when the appointment can "
"begin. If the :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` is `1` hour, appointments must be "
"booked *at least* `1` hour in advance."
msgstr ""
"Nato nastavite :guilabel:`Čas predrezervacije`. To je najmanjši čas med tem, "
"ko je sestanek mogoče rezervirati, in med tem, ko se sestanek lahko začne. "
"Če je :guilabel:`Čas predrezervacije` `1` ura, je treba sestanke rezervirati "
"*vsaj* `1` uro vnaprej."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:75
msgid ""
"An appointment type is created for `Tennis Courts`, with "
"a :guilabel:`Duration` of `1` hour, and a :guilabel:`Pre-Booking Time` of "
"`1` hour. At `02:00` PM, a customer attempts to book an appointment for the "
"same day at `02:45` pm. The first available time is `04:00` pm."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjena je vrsta sestanka za `Teniška igrišča` s :guilabel:`Trajanjem` "
"`1` ure in :guilabel:`Časom predrezervacije` `1` ure. Ob `02:00` popoldne "
"stranka poskuša rezervirati sestanek za isti dan ob `02:45` popoldne. Prvi "
"razpoložljiv čas je `04:00` popoldne."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the booking calendar showing available times."
msgstr "Primer koledarja rezervacij, ki prikazuje razpoložljive čase."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:82
msgid "Select a :guilabel:`Scheduling Window`:"
msgstr "Izberite :guilabel:`Časovno okno razporejanja`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:84
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Available now` to allow customers to book an appointment "
"immediately. Use the :guilabel:`Up to X days into the future` field to "
"define how far in advance customers can schedule appointments. For example, "
"if `14` is entered, customers cannot book anything more than 14 days from "
"the current date."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Razpoložljivo zdaj`, da strankam omogočite takojšnjo "
"rezervacijo sestanka. Uporabite polje :guilabel:`Do X dni v prihodnost`, da "
"določite, kako daleč vnaprej lahko stranke razporejajo sestanke. Na primer, "
"če je vneseno `14`, stranke ne morejo rezervirati ničesar več kot 14 dni od "
"trenutnega datuma."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:88
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Within a date range` to limit bookings to a specific range "
"of dates. After selecting this option, click the :guilabel:`From` "
"and :guilabel:`to` fields, and use the calendar pop-up window to customize "
"the date and time range."
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Znotraj datumskega razpona`, da omejite rezervacije na "
"določen razpon datumov. Po izbiri te možnosti kliknite polji :guilabel:`Od` "
"in :guilabel:`do` ter uporabite pojavno okno s koledarjem za prilagoditev "
"datumskega in časovnega razpona."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:92
msgid ""
"Update the :guilabel:`Allow Cancelling` field to limit the amount of time "
"before an appointment where a customer can cancel. If this setting is "
"enabled, customers are unable to cancel within the designated time frame."
msgstr ""
"Posodobite polje :guilabel:`Dovoli preklic`, da omejite čas pred sestankom, "
"v katerem lahko stranka prekliče. Če je ta nastavitev omogočena, stranke ne "
"morejo preklicati znotraj določenega časovnega okvira."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:97
msgid ""
"If a customer does try to cancel within the time frame, they receive an "
"error message with contact information. If the appointment is for a "
"resource, the contact details are for the user that created the appointment "
"type. If the appointment is for a user, the contact details are for the user "
"the appointment is with."
msgstr ""
"Če stranka poskuša preklicati znotraj časovnega okvira, prejme sporočilo o "
"napaki s kontaktnimi podatki. Če je sestanek za vir, so kontaktni podatki za "
"uporabnika, ki je ustvaril vrsto sestanka. Če je sestanek za uporabnika, so "
"kontaktni podatki za uporabnika, s katerim je sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the message a customer sees when cancelling."
msgstr "Primer sporočila, ki ga stranka vidi ob preklicu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:105
msgid ""
"Next, designate whether this appointment type is based on :guilabel:`Users` "
"or :guilabel:`Resources`, by selecting the appropriate radio button. If it "
"is based on users, select one or more :guilabel:`Users` in the drop-down. If "
"it is based on :ref:`resources <appointments/resources>`, select one or "
"more :guilabel:`Resources` in the drop-down."
msgstr ""
"Nato določite, ali temelji ta vrsta sestanka na :guilabel:`Uporabnikih` "
"ali :guilabel:`Virih`, tako da izberete ustrezen izbirni gumb. Če temelji na "
"uporabnikih, v spustnem meniju izberite enega ali "
"več :guilabel:`Uporabnikov`. Če temelji na :ref:`virih <appointments/"
"resources>`, v spustnem meniju izberite enega ali več :guilabel:`Virov`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:111
msgid ""
"User-based appointment types can be used for scheduling sales meetings and "
"demos, as well as recruiting interviews."
msgstr ""
"Vrste sestankov, ki temeljijo na uporabnikih, se lahko uporabijo za "
"razporejanje prodajnih sestankov in predstavitev ter za zaposlovalne "
"razgovore."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:114
msgid ""
"Resource-based appointment types can be used for scheduling time in specific "
"rooms or locations."
msgstr ""
"Vrste sestankov, ki temeljijo na virih, se lahko uporabijo za razporejanje "
"časa v določenih sobah ali lokacijah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:116
msgid ""
"Selecting :guilabel:`Resources` in the :guilabel:`Availability on` field "
"reveals the :guilabel:`Manage Capacities` option. If selected, the "
"appointment limits the number of participants based on the capacity of the "
"resources selected."
msgstr ""
"Izbira :guilabel:`Virov` v polju :guilabel:`Razpoložljivost na` razkrije "
"možnost :guilabel:`Upravljaj zmogljivosti`. Če je izbrana, sestanek omeji "
"število udeležencev glede na zmogljivost izbranih virov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:120
msgid ""
"Choose an :guilabel:`Assignment Method` by selecting the appropriate radio "
"button:"
msgstr ""
"Izberite :guilabel:`Način dodelitve`, tako da izberete ustrezen izbirni gumb:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:122
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pick User/Resource then Time`: customers select from a list of "
"available users/resources, then select an open time slot."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izberi uporabnika/vir in nato čas`: stranke izberejo s seznama "
"razpoložljivih uporabnikov/virov, nato pa izberejo razpoložljiv časovni "
"termin."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then User/Resource`: customers choose a date and "
"time, then select from the list of available users/resources."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izberi čas in nato uporabnika/vir`: stranke izberejo datum in "
"čas, nato pa izberejo s seznama razpoložljivih uporabnikov/virov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:126
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Select Time then auto-assign`: customers select a time slot and "
"are automatically assigned a user/resource."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izberi čas in samodejno dodeli`: stranke izberejo časovni termin "
"in jim je samodejno dodeljen uporabnik/vir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:130
msgid "Schedule tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Urnik"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:132
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Schedule` tab is used to outline when this appointment type "
"is to be made available. The settings define the time slots shown on the "
"booking page."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Urnik` se uporablja za določitev, kdaj naj bo ta vrsta "
"sestanka na voljo. Nastavitve določajo časovne termine, prikazane na strani "
"za rezervacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:135
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to create a new time frame. Select a day of the "
"week from the :guilabel:`Every` drop-down menu, then update the times in "
"the :guilabel:`From` and :guilabel:`To` fields. Click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon to delete an entry. Multiple entries can be "
"included for a single day."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da ustvarite nov časovni okvir. Izberite "
"dan v tednu iz spustnega menija :guilabel:`Vsak`, nato pa posodobite čas v "
"poljih :guilabel:`Od` in :guilabel:`Do`. Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(koš)`, da izbrišete vnos. Za en dan je lahko vključenih več "
"vnosov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:141
msgid ""
"If an appointment should not be available at specific times, such as when "
"users are taking lunch, include time slots before and after."
msgstr ""
"Če sestanek ne bi smel biti na voljo ob določenih časih, kot je na primer "
"med odmori za malico, vključite časovne termine pred in po njem."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:0
msgid "An example of the Schedule tab in an appointment."
msgstr "Primer zavihka Urnik v sestanku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:234
msgid "Options tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Možnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:150
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Options` tab is used to customize the display options for "
"this appointment, as well as notification settings for customers and users."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Možnosti` se uporablja za prilagoditev možnosti prikaza "
"tega sestanka ter nastavitev obvestil za stranke in uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:153
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Front-End Display` field determines how the appointment is "
"presented on the website to customers. Select the :guilabel:`Show Pictures` "
"radio button to publish the default pictures of the user or resources for "
"this appointment on the website."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Prikaz na spletnem vmesniku` določa, kako je sestanek "
"predstavljen strankam na spletni strani. Izberite izbirni "
"gumb :guilabel:`Prikaži slike`, da na spletni strani objavite privzete slike "
"uporabnika ali virov za ta sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:157
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Timezone` and :guilabel:`Location` fields automatically "
"populate for resource appointments, based on where the resource is located. "
"For user-based appointments, the :guilabel:`Location` field defaults to an "
"`Online Meeting`, with a :guilabel:`Videoconference Link` automatically "
"generated. If this should not be an online meeting, select a different "
"option in the :guilabel:`Location` field."
msgstr ""
"Polji :guilabel:`Časovni pas` in :guilabel:`Lokacija` se pri sestankih z "
"viri samodejno izpolnita glede na lokacijo vira. Pri sestankih z uporabniki "
"polje :guilabel:`Lokacija` privzeto vsebuje `Spletni sestanek`, s samodejno "
"ustvarjeno :guilabel:`povezavo do videokonference`. Če to ne bi smel biti "
"spletni sestanek, izberite drugo možnost v polju :guilabel:`Lokacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:163
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Manual Confirmation` checkbox to require approval before "
"a meeting is accepted. If this feature is enabled, the appointment time slot "
"is still considered *reserved* until it is confirmed or rejected. Leave this "
"checkbox blank to automatically accept meetings created from this "
"appointment."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ročna potrditev`, da zahtevate "
"odobritev pred sprejetjem sestanka. Če je ta funkcija omogočena, je časovni "
"termin sestanka še vedno *rezerviran*, dokler ni potrjen ali zavrnjen. "
"Pustite to potrditveno polje prazno, če želite samodejno sprejeti sestanke, "
"ustvarjene iz tega sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:168
msgid ""
"The :doc:`Create Opportunities <appointments/create-opps>` feature adds an "
"opportunity to the **CRM** app for each scheduled appointment, which is "
"assigned to the responsible user. Tick the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` "
"checkbox to enable this option."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija :doc:`Ustvari priložnosti <appointments/create-opps>` doda "
"priložnost v aplikacijo **CRM** za vsak načrtovan sestanek, ki je dodeljena "
"odgovornemu uporabniku. Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"priložnosti`, da omogočite to možnost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:173
msgid ""
"This field is only visible if the **CRM** app is installed on the database."
msgstr ""
"To polje je vidno le, če je aplikacija **CRM** nameščena v zbirki podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:175
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Reminders` field is used to set how customers are to be "
"contacted before the appointment time. Select one or more options from the "
"drop-down, based on the communication method, and the time frame."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Opomniki` se uporablja za nastavitev, kako naj bodo stranke "
"obveščene pred časom sestanka. Izberite eno ali več možnosti iz spustnega "
"menija glede na način komunikacije in časovni okvir."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:179
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Allow Guests` checkbox to grant customers the ability to "
"add additional guests when registering for an appointment."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Dovoli goste`, da strankam omogočite "
"dodajanje dodatnih gostov pri registraciji za sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:185
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:204
msgid "Questions tab"
msgstr "Zavihek vprašanja"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:187
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab can be used to prompt customers for additional "
"information while they are booking an appointment. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line` to add a new question."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Vprašanja` se lahko uporablja za pridobivanje dodatnih "
"informacij od strank med rezervacijo sestanka. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"vrstico`, da dodate novo vprašanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:190
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Questions` pop-up window, enter "
"the :guilabel:`Question`, then choose an :guilabel:`Answer Type`."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari vprašanja` vnesite :guilabel:`Vprašanje`, "
"nato izberite :guilabel:`Vrsta odgovora`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:193
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Mandatory Answer` checkbox to require customers to "
"answer this question before they are allowed to book an appointment. "
"Click :guilabel:`Save & New` to add another question, or :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close` when finished."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Obvezen odgovor`, da zahtevate, da "
"stranke odgovorijo na to vprašanje, preden lahko rezervirajo sestanek. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in novo`, da dodate novo vprašanje, "
"ali :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`, ko končate."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:198
msgid "Messages tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Sporočila"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:200
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Messages` tab is used by the business to provide additional "
"information to customers regarding this appointment type."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Sporočila` uporablja podjetje za zagotavljanje dodatnih "
"informacij strankam glede te vrste sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:204
msgid ""
"The content in the :guilabel:`Messages` tab is visible to customers and "
"website visitors."
msgstr ""
"Vsebina v zavihku :guilabel:`Sporočila` je vidna strankam in obiskovalcem "
"spletnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field, add a short description of "
"the appointment type. This can include the topic of the appointment, a "
"meeting agenda, or an introduction to the users responsible for the meeting."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Uvodno sporočilo` dodajte kratek opis vrste sestanka. To "
"lahko vključuje temo sestanka, dnevni red sestanka ali predstavitev "
"uporabnikov, odgovornih za sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:210
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Extra Message on Confirmation` is displayed to a customer "
"after they have booked a meeting. Add any additional information here that "
"the customer should be aware of. This can include parking information, last "
"minute rules, or additional instructions."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Dodatno sporočilo ob potrditvi` se prikaže stranki, ko "
"rezervira sestanek. Sem dodajte vse dodatne informacije, ki bi jih morala "
"stranka vedeti. To lahko vključuje informacije o parkiranju, pravila v "
"zadnjem trenutku ali dodatna navodila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:215
msgid "Publishing an appointment"
msgstr "Objava sestanka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments.rst:217
msgid ""
"When an appointment is ready to publish, click the :guilabel:`Go to Website` "
"smart button at the top of the record. Then, slide the :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Unpublished` icon to :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"on` :guilabel:`Published`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je sestanek pripravljen za objavo, kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Pojdi "
"na spletno mesto` na vrhu zapisa. Nato premaknite ikono :icon:`fa-toggle-"
"off` :guilabel:`Neobjavljeno` na :icon:`fa-toggle-on` :guilabel:`Objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:3
msgid "Create opportunities from appointments"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje priložnosti iz sestankov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:5
msgid ""
"When creating a new appointment type in the **Appointments** application, "
"users have the option to create new *opportunities* with information from "
"new bookings. This option captures information from scheduled appointments "
"and creates opportunities in the **CRM** app."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju nove vrste sestanka v aplikaciji **Sestanki** imajo "
"uporabniki možnost ustvariti nove *priložnosti* z informacijami iz novih "
"rezervacij. Ta možnost zajame informacije iz načrtovanih sestankov in "
"ustvari priložnosti v aplikaciji **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:10
msgid ""
"This option is only available if the **CRM** application is installed on the "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Ta možnost je na voljo samo, če je aplikacija **CRM** nameščena v zbirki "
"podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:15
msgid ""
"Navigate to the **Appointments** app dashboard. Click :guilabel:`New` "
"to :doc:`create a new appointment type <../appointments>`. To edit an "
"existing appointment type, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Action` at the "
"far-right of the appointment line, to open the drop-down menu, then "
"click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na nadzorno ploščo aplikacije **Sestanki**. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da :doc:`ustvarite novo vrsto sestanka <../"
"appointments>`. Za urejanje obstoječe vrste sestanka kliknite :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Dejanje` na skrajni desni strani vrstice sestanka, da "
"odprete spustni meni, nato kliknite :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The edit button on an appointment type record."
msgstr "Gumb za urejanje na zapisu vrste sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:23
msgid ""
"On the appointment type record, click the :guilabel:`Options` tab, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Create Opportunities` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Na zapisu vrste sestanka kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Možnosti` in označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ustvari priložnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid "The options tab on an appointment type form."
msgstr "Zavihek možnosti na obrazcu vrste sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:30
msgid "Add questions"
msgstr "Dodajanje vprašanj"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:32
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Questions` tab allows users to :ref:`add questions "
"<appointments/questions>` to the appointment booking page. When customers "
"are booking an appointment slot, they are prompted to answer these "
"questions. The information provided by customers is available in "
"the :ref:`new opportunity <appointments/new-opp>`. Adding questions to the "
"appointment type is optional. However, the additional information captured "
"by the questions can be useful later in the sales pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek :guilabel:`Vprašanja` uporabnikom omogoča, da :ref:`dodajo vprašanja "
"<appointments/questions>` na stran za rezervacijo sestanka. Ko stranke "
"rezervirajo termin za sestanek, so pozvane, da odgovorijo na ta vprašanja. "
"Informacije, ki jih zagotovijo stranke, so na voljo v :ref:`novi priložnosti "
"<appointments/new-opp>`. Dodajanje vprašanj vrsti sestanka je neobvezno. "
"Vendar so dodatne informacije, zajete z vprašanji, lahko pozneje koristne v "
"prodajnem procesu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:39
msgid ""
"A furniture company creates a new appointment type for sales demos. "
"Customers reserve time with salespeople to discuss their furniture and "
"design needs. However, because the time is limited to only thirty minute "
"increments, salespeople do not have the time to show all of the available "
"furniture styles in every call. They add questions to the appointment type "
"to prompt customers to provide additional information about the products and "
"services they are interested in. Not only does this help when preparing for "
"the demo, it also provides clarity further along in the sales process."
msgstr ""
"Podjetje za pohištvo ustvari novo vrsto sestanka za prodajne predstavitve. "
"Stranke rezervirajo čas s prodajalci, da razpravljajo o svojih potrebah "
"glede pohištva in oblikovanja. Ker pa je čas omejen le na 30-minutne "
"intervale, prodajalci nimajo časa, da prikažejo vse razpoložljive sloge "
"pohištva v vsakem klicu. K vrsti sestanka dodajo vprašanja, da spodbudijo "
"stranke k zagotavljanju dodatnih informacij o izdelkih in storitvah, ki jih "
"zanimajo. To ne pomaga le pri pripravi na predstavitev, ampak tudi "
"zagotavlja jasnost pozneje v prodajnem procesu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:0
msgid "An appointment booking form with custom questions."
msgstr "Obrazec za rezervacijo sestanka z vprašanji po meri."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:53
msgid "Viewing the new opportunity"
msgstr "Ogled nove priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:55
msgid ""
"To view opportunities created from appointments, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`CRM` app dashboard. If necessary, remove any filters "
"from the search bar. Then, click the Kanban card for the appropriate "
"opportunity to open it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite si ogledati priložnosti, ustvarjene iz sestankov, odprite nadzorno "
"ploščo aplikacije :menuselection:`CRM`. Po potrebi odstranite vse filtre iz "
"iskalne vrstice. Nato kliknite na Kanban kartico ustrezne priložnosti, da jo "
"odprete."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:59
msgid ""
"The contact information from the appointment is added to the opportunity "
"record. The answers the customer provided to the optional questions are "
"included in the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab. The scheduled appointment is "
"listed in the *Chatter* of the record, and can be edited from there."
msgstr ""
"Kontaktni podatki iz sestanka so dodani k zapisu priložnosti. Odgovori, ki "
"jih je stranka podala na izbirna vprašanja, so vključeni v "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Interne opombe`. Načrtovani sestanek je naveden v "
"*Chatter* zapisa in ga je mogoče urejati od tam."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:None
msgid ""
"The chatter of an opportunity in the CRM with the scheduled appointment "
"information."
msgstr "Chatter priložnosti v CRM-ju z informacijami o načrtovanem sestanku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/create-opps.rst:67
msgid ""
"If an opportunity is created from a :ref:`resource based <appointments/"
"resources>` appointment type, the user who created the appointment type is "
"listed as the :guilabel:`Salesperson` for the opportunity. If it is created "
"from a user based appointment, the user the appointment is scheduled with is "
"assigned as the :guilabel:`Salesperson`."
msgstr ""
"Če je priložnost ustvarjena iz :ref:`na virih osnovanega <appointments/"
"resources>` tipa sestanka, je uporabnik, ki je ustvaril tip sestanka, "
"naveden kot :guilabel:`Prodajalec` za priložnost. Če je ustvarjena iz "
"uporabniško osnovanega sestanka, je uporabnik, s katerim je sestanek "
"načrtovan, dodeljen kot :guilabel:`Prodajalec`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:3
msgid "Google reserve integration"
msgstr "Integracija Google Reserve"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:5
msgid ""
"Google Reserve lets customers book appointments directly from Google Search, "
"Google Maps, and the Google Assistant. By connecting Odoo **Appointments** "
"to Google Reserve, bookings are added directly into Odoo without customers "
"needing to visit the company website."
msgstr ""
"Google Reserve strankam omogoča, da rezervirajo termine neposredno iz "
"Googlovega iskanja, Google Zemljevidov in Google Asistenta. Z povezavo Odoo "
"**Appointments** z Google Reserve se rezervacije dodajo neposredno v Odoo, "
"ne da bi stranke morale obiskati spletno stran podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:14
msgid ""
"First, navigate to the :guilabel:`Apps` application. Then, remove "
"the :guilabel:`Apps` filter from the search bar and type in `Google`. "
"Click :guilabel:`Install` on the :guilabel:`Appointment Google Reserve` "
"module."
msgstr ""
"Najprej se pomaknite na aplikacijo :guilabel:`Aplikacije`. Nato odstranite "
"filter :guilabel:`Aplikacije` iz iskalne vrstice in vnesite `Google`. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Namesti` na modulu :guilabel:`Appointment Google "
"Reserve`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "The Google Reserve module in the Odoo apps application."
msgstr "Modul Google Reserve v aplikaciji za aplikacije Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:21
msgid ""
"Next, navigate to the :menuselection:`Appointments` application. Open an "
"existing appointment type, or click :guilabel:`New` to :ref:`create a new "
"one <appointments/configure>`. Then click the :guilabel:`Google Bookings` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Nato se pomaknite na aplikacijo :menuselection:`Appointments`. Odprite "
"obstoječo vrsto termina ali kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da :ref:`ustvarite "
"novega <appointments/configure>`. Nato kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Google "
"Bookings`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:25
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant` field, and select an option "
"from the drop-down, or click :guilabel:`Create` to open "
"the :guilabel:`Create Google Reserve Merchant` form."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje :guilabel:`Google Reserve Merchant` in izberite možnost s "
"spustnega seznama ali kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari`, da odprete "
"obrazec :guilabel:`Create Google Reserve Merchant`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:28
msgid ""
"On the form, enter all required information. The business address **must** "
"match exactly what appears on Google Maps. Click :guilabel:`Save & Close`."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu vnesite vse zahtevane informacije. Poslovni naslov se **mora** "
"popolnoma ujemati s tistim, kar je prikazano na Google Zemljevidih. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:None
msgid "A create new google merchant form in the Appointments app."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec za ustvarjanje novega Google trgovca v aplikaciji Appointments."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the new merchant has been created, click :guilabel:`Synchronize with "
"Google Reserve`. The initial synchronization can take up to 24 hours to "
"propagate to Google's systems."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nov trgovec ustvarjen, kliknite :guilabel:`Synchronize with Google "
"Reserve`. Začetna sinhronizacija lahko traja do 24 ur, da se razširi na "
"Googlove sisteme."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/appointments/google_reserve.rst:38
msgid ""
"Ensure that the business address matches the Google Maps listing precisely, "
"including formatting and unit numbers. Mismatches may cause synchronization "
"to fail or prevent the listing from appearing on Google."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da se poslovni naslov natančno ujema z vnosom na Google "
"Zemljevidih, vključno z oblikovanjem in številkami enot. Neujemanja lahko "
"povzročijo napako pri sinhronizaciji ali preprečijo, da bi se vnos pojavil "
"na Googlu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:5
msgid "Calendar"
msgstr "Koledar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Calendar** is a scheduling app that allows users to integrate a "
"company's business flow into a single management platform. By integrating "
"with the other apps in Odoo's ecosystem, **Calendar** allows users to "
"schedule and organize meetings, schedule events, plan employee appraisals, "
"coordinate projects, and more."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Calendar** je aplikacija za razporejanje, ki uporabnikom omogoča "
"integracijo poslovnega poteka podjetja v eno platformo za upravljanje. Z "
"integracijo z drugimi aplikacijami v ekosistemu Odoo aplikacija **Calendar** "
"uporabnikom omogoča razporejanje in organizacijo sestankov, načrtovanje "
"dogodkov, načrtovanje ocenjevanj kadra, usklajevanje projektov in še več."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:12
msgid ""
"Upon opening the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, users have an overview of "
"their current meetings. The selected view option appears as "
"a :guilabel:`Day`, :guilabel:`Week`, :guilabel:`Month`, or :guilabel:`Year` "
"drop-down menu. Under the view options drop-down menu, users can also enable "
"or disable :guilabel:`Show weekends`."
msgstr ""
"Ob odprtju :menuselection:`aplikacije Koledar` imajo uporabniki pregled nad "
"svojimi trenutnimi sestanki. Izbrana možnost pogleda se pojavi kot spustni "
"meni :guilabel:`Dan`, :guilabel:`Teden`, :guilabel:`Mesec` "
"ali :guilabel:`Leto`. Pod spustnim menijem možnosti pogleda lahko uporabniki "
"tudi omogočijo ali onemogočijo :guilabel:`Prikaži vikende`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Calendar app."
msgstr "Pregled aplikacije Koledar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:21
msgid ""
"Depending on the selected view option, users can click the :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(left or right arrow)` buttons to "
"switch between days, weeks, etc., and switch back to the current day with "
"the :guilabel:`Today` button."
msgstr ""
"Glede na izbrano možnost pogleda lahko uporabniki kliknejo gumbe :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-left` :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(leva ali desna puščica)` za "
"preklop med dnevi, tedni itd. in se vrnejo na trenutni dan z "
"gumbom :guilabel:`Danes`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:26
msgid "Sync third-party calendars"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija koledarjev tretjih oseb"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:28
msgid ""
"Users can sync Odoo with existing :doc:`Outlook <calendar/outlook>` and/"
"or :doc:`Google <calendar/google>` calendars, by heading "
"to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --> Settings`. From here, "
"enter :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret`. There is also an "
"option to pause synchronization by ticking the checkbox, or automating "
"synchronization by keeping it blank."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko sinhronizirajo Odoo z obstoječimi koledarji :doc:`Outlook "
"<calendar/outlook>` in/ali :doc:`Google <calendar/google>` tako, da grejo "
"na :menuselection:`aplikacija Koledar --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. "
"Tukaj vnesite :guilabel:`ID odjemalca` in :guilabel:`Skrivnost odjemalca`. "
"Na voljo je tudi možnost za začasno zaustavitev sinhronizacije s "
"potrditvenim poljem ali samodejno sinhronizacijo, če ga pustite praznega."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:34
msgid ""
"Once the desired configurations are complete, click :guilabel:`Save` before "
"moving on."
msgstr ""
"Ko so želene konfiguracije dokončane, kliknite :guilabel:`Save`, preden "
"nadaljujete."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:36
msgid ""
"Events created in synced calendars automatically appear across the "
"integrated platforms."
msgstr ""
"Dogodki, ustvarjeni v sinhroniziranih koledarjih, se samodejno prikažejo na "
"vseh integriranih platformah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:39
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Outlook calendar with Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Sinhronizacija koledarja Outlook z Odoo <calendar/outlook>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:40
msgid ":doc:`Synchronize Google calendar with Odoo <calendar/google>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Sinhronizacija koledarja Google z Odoo <calendar/google>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:43
msgid "Create activities from chatter"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje dejavnosti iz chatter"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:45
msgid ""
"Instantly create new meetings anywhere in Odoo through an individual "
"record's chatter, like in a **CRM** opportunity card or task in the "
"**Project** app."
msgstr ""
"Takoj ustvarite nove sestanke kjer koli v Odoo prek klepetalnice posameznega "
"zapisa, na primer na kartici priložnosti v **CRM** ali opravilu v aplikaciji "
"**Project**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:48
msgid ""
"From the chatter, click on the :guilabel:`Activity` button. In "
"the :guilabel:`Schedule Activity` pop-up window, select the "
"desired :guilabel:`Activity Type`, which populates a set of buttons, "
"depending on the activity."
msgstr ""
"V klepetu kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Aktivnost`. V pojavnem "
"oknu :guilabel:`Načrtuj aktivnost` izberite želeno :guilabel:`Vrsto "
"aktivnosti`, kar prikaže nabor gumbov, odvisno od aktivnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:52
msgid ""
"Activities that involve other schedules, like :guilabel:`Meeting` "
"or :guilabel:`Call for Demo`, link to the **Calendar** app. Select one of "
"these activities to link to the **Calendar** app, then "
"hit :guilabel:`Schedule` to navigate back to the app."
msgstr ""
"Aktivnosti, ki vključujejo druge razporede, kot sta :guilabel:`Sestanek` "
"ali :guilabel:`Klic za predstavitev`, se povežejo z aplikacijo **Koledar**. "
"Izberite eno od teh aktivnosti za povezavo z aplikacijo **Koledar**, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Načrtuj`, da se vrnete v aplikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:57
msgid ":doc:`Schedule activities in Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Načrtovanje dejavnosti v Odoo <../essentials/activities>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:60
msgid "Plan an event"
msgstr "Načrtovanje dogodka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:62
msgid ""
"To put an event on the calendar, open the :menuselection:`Calendar app`, and "
"click into the target date. On the :guilabel:`New Event` pop-up window that "
"appears, start by adding the event title."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dogodek vnesti v koledar, odprite :menuselection:`aplikacijo "
"Koledar` in kliknite v ciljni datum. V pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Nov "
"dogodek`, ki se prikaže, najprej dodajte naslov dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Schedule an event window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Okno za načrtovanje dogodka v aplikaciji Koledar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:68
msgid ""
"The target date auto-populates in the :guilabel:`Start` field. This can be "
"changed by clicking into the date section, and selecting a date from the "
"calendar. For multi-day events, select the end date in the second field, "
"then click :guilabel:`Apply`."
msgstr ""
"Ciljni datum se samodejno izpolni v polju :guilabel:`Začetek`. To lahko "
"spremenite tako, da kliknete v razdelek datuma in izberete datum iz "
"koledarja. Za večdnevne dogodke izberite končni datum v drugem polju, nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Uporabi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:72
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`All Day` checkbox if there is no specific start or end "
"time."
msgstr ""
"Označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ves dan`, če ni določenega začetnega "
"ali končnega časa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:74
msgid ""
"For events with specific start and stop times, ensure the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox is unticked to enable time selection. With the :guilabel:`All "
"Day` checkbox unticked, time selections appear in the :guilabel:`Start` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Za dogodke s specifičnimi začetnimi in končnimi časi poskrbite, da je "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ves dan` odznačeno, da omogočite izbiro časa. "
"Ko je potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Ves dan` odznačeno, se v "
"polju :guilabel:`Začetek` prikažejo izbire časa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:78
msgid ""
"The signed-in user auto-populates as the first attendee. "
"Additional :guilabel:`Attendees` can be added or created from here, as well."
msgstr ""
"Prijavljeni uporabnik se samodejno izpolni kot prvi udeleženec. Od tukaj "
"lahko dodate ali ustvarite tudi dodatne :guilabel:`Udeležence`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:81
msgid ""
"For virtual meetings, copy and paste the URL into the space provided in "
"the :guilabel:`Videocall URL` field. Or, click :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`Video` to create a link."
msgstr ""
"Za virtualne sestanke kopirajte in prilepite URL v polje :guilabel:`URL "
"videoklica`. Ali kliknite :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`Video`, da ustvarite "
"povezavo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:84
msgid ""
"Next, either create the event by clicking :guilabel:`Save & Close`, or "
"select :guilabel:`More Options` to further configure the event."
msgstr ""
"Nato ustvarite dogodek s klikom na :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri` ali "
"izberite :guilabel:`Več možnosti`, da dodatno konfigurirate dogodek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:88
msgid ""
"Once the event is created, users can click into the virtual meeting directly "
"from the calendar event to access more configuration options."
msgstr ""
"Ko je dogodek ustvarjen, lahko uporabniki kliknejo neposredno v virtualni "
"sestanek iz dogodka v koledarju, da dostopajo do več konfiguracijskih "
"možnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "The full event form for a new calendar event."
msgstr "Celoten obrazec dogodka za nov dogodek v koledarju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:94
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Description` field allows users to add additional information "
"and details about the meeting."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Opis` uporabnikom omogoča dodajanje dodatnih informacij in "
"podrobnosti o sestanku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:97
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`More Options` to navigate to the meeting form, which "
"provides additional configurations for the event:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Več možnosti`, da se pomaknete na obrazec sestanka, ki "
"zagotavlja dodatne konfiguracije za dogodek:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:100
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Duration`: Define the length of the meeting in :guilabel:`hours`, "
"or toggle the :guilabel:`All Day` switch."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Trajanje`: Določite dolžino sestanka v :guilabel:`urah` ali "
"preklopite stikalo :guilabel:`Ves dan`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:102
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Organizer`: This is defaulted to the current Odoo user. Select a "
"new one from existing users, or create and edit a new user."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Organizator`: To je privzeto nastavljen na trenutnega uporabnika "
"Odoo. Izberite novega izmed obstoječih uporabnikov ali ustvarite in uredite "
"novega uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tags`: Add tags to the event, like `Customer Meeting` or "
"`Internal Meeting`. These can be searched and filtered in the **Calendar** "
"app when organizing multiple events."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Oznake`: Dodajte oznake dogodku, kot so `Sestanek s stranko` ali "
"`Interni sestanek`. Te lahko iščete in filtrirate v aplikaciji **Koledar** "
"pri organizaciji več dogodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:106
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Calendar description`: Add additional information or details "
"about the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opis koledarja`: dodajte dodatne informacije ali podrobnosti o "
"sestanku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:107
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Reminders`: Select notification options to send to attendees. "
"Choose a default notification, or configure new reminders."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opomniki`: Izberite možnosti obveščanja za pošiljanje "
"udeležencem. Izberite privzeto obvestilo ali konfigurirajte nove opomnike."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:109
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurrent`: Tick the checkbox to create a recurring meeting. Once "
"selected, this opens new fields:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponavljajoče`: Potrdite potrditveno polje za ustvarjanje "
"ponavljajočega sestanka. Ko je izbrano, se odprejo nova polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:112
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Repeat`: Select the recurring period of this meeting. Depending "
"on what type of recurrence has been selected, a subsequent field appears, in "
"which users can indicate when the meeting should recur. For example, "
"if :guilabel:`Monthly` is selected as the :guilabel:`Repeat` option, a new "
"field appears, in which the user decides on what :guilabel:`Day of Month` "
"the meeting should recur."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponovi`: Izberite ponavljajoče obdobje tega sestanka. Glede na "
"to, katera vrsta ponavljanja je bila izbrana, se prikaže naslednje polje, v "
"katerem uporabniki navedejo, kdaj naj se sestanek ponavlja. Na primer, če je "
"kot možnost :guilabel:`Ponovi` izbrano :guilabel:`Mesečno`, se prikaže novo "
"polje, v katerem uporabnik odloči, na kateri :guilabel:`Dan v mesecu` naj se "
"sestanek ponavlja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:117
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Until`: Select the limited :guilabel:`Number of repetitions` this "
"meeting should recur, the :guilabel:`End date` of when the recurrences "
"should stop, or if the meetings should recur :guilabel:`Forever`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Do`: Izberite omejeno :guilabel:`Število ponovitev`, kolikokrat "
"naj se sestanek ponavlja, :guilabel:`Končni datum`, kdaj naj se ponavljanja "
"ustavijo, ali pa naj se sestanki ponavljajo :guilabel:`Za vedno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:120
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: Select the timezone for which this meeting time is "
"specified."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Časovni pas`: Izberite časovni pas, za katerega je določen čas "
"tega sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:123
msgid "Coordinate with teams' availability"
msgstr "Uskladite se z razpoložljivostjo ekip"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:125
msgid ""
"When scheduling an event for multiple users, on the **Calendar** app "
"dashboard, tick the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Attendees` to view team "
"members' availability. Tick (or untick) the checkbox next to listed users to "
"show (or hide) individual calendars."
msgstr ""
"Pri načrtovanju dogodka za več uporabnikov na nadzorni plošči aplikacije "
"**Koledar** potrdite potrditveno polje poleg :guilabel:`Udeleženci`, da si "
"ogledate razpoložljivost članov ekipe. Potrdite (ali odznačite) potrditveno "
"polje poleg navedenih uporabnikov, da prikažete (ali skrijete) posamezne "
"koledarje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "View of Attendees section on Calendar app."
msgstr "Pogled razdelka Udeleženci v aplikaciji Koledar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:135
msgid "Share Availabilities"
msgstr "Razpoložljivosti delitev"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:137
msgid ""
"On the **Calendar** app main dashboard, click the :guilabel:`Share` button "
"at the top of the page, then select :guilabel:`Specific Slots` from the drop-"
"down. Next, click and drag to select the available times and dates on the "
"calendar to add them as options in the invitation."
msgstr ""
"Na glavni nadzorni plošči aplikacije **Koledar** kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Deli` na vrhu strani, nato v spustnem meniju "
"izberite :guilabel:`Določene termine`. Nato kliknite in povlecite, da "
"izberete razpoložljive čase in datume na koledarju ter jih dodate kot "
"možnosti v povabilu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Selecting availabilites on the Calendar dashboard."
msgstr "Izbira razpoložljivosti na nadzorni plošči Koledar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:145
msgid ""
"To remove a selected time range, hover over the availability to click "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za odstranitev izbranega časovnega razpona se premaknite nad razpoložljivost "
"in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(koš)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:148
msgid ""
"Once availability has been selected, click :icon:`fa-"
"clipboard` :guilabel:`Copy Link` to copy a sharable link to the clipboard. "
"Or, click :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Configure` icon button to navigate to "
"the associated appointment."
msgstr ""
"Ko je razpoložljivost izbrana, kliknite :icon:`fa-"
"clipboard` :guilabel:`Kopiraj povezavo`, da kopirate povezavo, ki jo lahko "
"delite, v odložišče. Ali kliknite gumb ikone :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj`, da odprete povezani sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:None
msgid "Share availability window on Calendar app."
msgstr "Okno za deljenje razpoložljivosti v aplikaciji Koledar."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:155
msgid ""
"On the **Share Availabilities** form, enter an :guilabel:`Appointment "
"Title`. Confirm the correct user is selected in the :guilabel:`Users` field. "
"To add a meeting room to the appointment, click the :guilabel:`Location` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu **Deli razpoložljivost** vnesite :guilabel:`Naslov sestanka`. "
"Preverite, da je v polju :guilabel:`Uporabniki` izbran pravilen uporabnik. "
"Če želite sestanku dodati sobo za sestanke, kliknite "
"polje :guilabel:`Lokacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:160
msgid ""
"If nothing is selected in the :guilabel:`Location` field, the appointment "
"defaults to an *Online Meeting*."
msgstr ""
"Če v polju :guilabel:`Lokacija` ni nič izbrano, je sestanek privzeto "
"*Spletni sestanek*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Video Link` field, select the type of video call link that "
"will be used for the generated appointments. If this field is left blank, no "
"meeting URLs will be created."
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Povezava za video` izberite vrsto povezave za videoklic, "
"ki bo uporabljena za ustvarjene sestanke. Če je to polje prazno, URL-ji "
"sestankov ne bodo ustvarjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:166
msgid ""
"To allow attendees to invite others to the event, tick the :guilabel:`Allow "
"invitations` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Če želite udeležencem dovoliti, da na dogodek povabijo druge, označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Dovoli povabila`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:168
msgid ""
"Add a message in the :guilabel:`Introduction Message` field. This is used as "
"a description for the event. Add a message to the :guilabel:`Extra Message "
"on Confirmation` field to be displayed after the appointment is booked."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte sporočilo v polje :guilabel:`Uvodno sporočilo`. To se uporabi kot "
"opis dogodka. Dodajte sporočilo v polje :guilabel:`Dodatno sporočilo ob "
"potrditvi`, ki se prikaže, ko je sestanek rezerviran."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:172
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Save & Copy Link`. To futher customize "
"the appointment, click the :icon:`fa-expand` :guilabel:`(expand)` icon at "
"the top of the pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-clipboard` :guilabel:`Shrani in kopiraj povezavo`. Za "
"nadaljnje prilagajanje sestanka kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"expand` :guilabel:`(razširi)` na vrhu pojavnega okna."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:175
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Preview` button to see how the appointment link looks "
"for attendees."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Predogled`, da si ogledate, kako bo povezava za "
"sestanek izgledala za udeležence."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:177
msgid "Optionally, configure the following tabs:"
msgstr "Po želji konfigurirajte naslednje zavihke:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:179
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-schedule`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:180
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-questions`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:181
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-messages`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:182
msgid ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"
msgstr ":ref:`calendar/appointment-options`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:184
msgid ""
"Once the configurations are finished, click the :guilabel:`Share` button to "
"generate a link to send directly, or click :guilabel:`Publish` to publish "
"the appointment selection on the connected Odoo website."
msgstr ""
"Ko so konfiguracije končane, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Deli`, da ustvarite "
"povezavo za neposredno pošiljanje, ali kliknite :guilabel:`Objavi`, da "
"objavite izbiro sestanka na povezani spletni strani Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:191
msgid "Availabilites tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Razpoložljivost"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:193
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Availabilites` tab of the appointment form, time slots can "
"be managed. The target date and time populate as the first time slots."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Razpoložljivost` obrazca za sestanek lahko upravljate "
"časovne termine. Ciljni datum in čas se prikažeta kot prvi časovni termini."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:196
msgid ""
"To add a new time slot, click :guilabel:`Add a line`. Click into the new "
"blank space under the :guilabel:`From` field, then select and enter the new "
"target start date and time, respectively. Repeat under the new blank space "
"under :guilabel:`To` to select and enter the new target end date and time."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje novega časovnega termina kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`. "
"Kliknite v nov prazen prostor pod poljem :guilabel:`Od`, nato izberite in "
"vnesite nov ciljni začetni datum in čas. Ponovite pod novim praznim "
"prostorom pod :guilabel:`Do`, da izberete in vnesete nov ciljni končni datum "
"in čas."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:206
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Questions` tab, add questions for the attendee to answer "
"when confirming their meeting. Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure "
"a :guilabel:`Question`. Then select a :guilabel:`Question Type`, optionally "
"add a :guilabel:`Placeholder` answer, and choose whether it is meeting. "
"Click :guilabel:`Add a line` to configure a :guilabel:`Question`. Then "
"select an :guilabel:`Answer Type`, optionally add a "
"placeholder :guilabel:`Answer`, and choose whether it "
"is :guilabel:`Mandatory`."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Vprašanja` dodajte vprašanja, na katera mora udeleženec "
"odgovoriti pri potrjevanju sestanka. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da "
"konfigurirate :guilabel:`Vprašanje`. Nato izberite :guilabel:`Vrsto "
"vprašanja`, po želji dodajte :guilabel:`Nadomestno besedilo` in izberite, "
"ali je obvezno. Kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da "
"konfigurirate :guilabel:`Vprašanje`. Nato izberite :guilabel:`Vrsto "
"odgovora`, po želji dodajte nadomestni :guilabel:`Odgovor` in izberite, ali "
"je :guilabel:`Obvezno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:213
msgid ""
"To learn how to create more comprehensive questionnaires, head to the "
"**Survey** app documentation on :doc:`creating and configuring data-"
"capturing questions <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvedeti, kako ustvariti obsežnejše vprašalnike, pojdite v "
"dokumentacijo aplikacije **Anketa** o :doc:`ustvarjanju in konfiguraciji "
"vprašanj za zajemanje podatkov <../marketing/surveys/questions>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:219
msgid "Communication tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Komunikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:221
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Introduction Page` field of the :guilabel:`Communication` "
"tab, add additional meeting information to appear on the invitation."
msgstr ""
"V polje :guilabel:`Uvodna stran` zavihka :guilabel:`Komunikacija` dodajte "
"dodatne informacije o sestanku, ki se bodo prikazale v povabilu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:224
msgid ""
"Information added to the :guilabel:`Confirmation Page` field appears once "
"the meeting is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Informacije, dodane v polje :guilabel:`Potrditvena stran`, se prikažejo, ko "
"je sestanek potrjen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:226
msgid ""
"Under the *Emails & SMS* heading, click the :guilabel:`Reminders` field to "
"add one or more methods of reminding attendees about the appointment. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Booking Email` field, and :guilabel:`Cancellation Email` "
"field, select an email template to be sent to attendees when booking or "
"cancelling meetings."
msgstr ""
"Pod naslovom *E-pošta in SMS* kliknite polje :guilabel:`Reminders`, da "
"dodate enega ali več načinov opominjanja udeležencev o sestanku. Pod "
"poljem :guilabel:`Booking Email` in poljem :guilabel:`Cancellation Email` "
"izberite predlogo e-pošte, ki bo poslana udeležencem pri rezervaciji ali "
"preklicu sestankov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:236
msgid "The :guilabel:`Options` tab provides additional configurations:"
msgstr "Zavihek :guilabel:`Možnosti` omogoča dodatne konfiguracije:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:238
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow invitations`: Tick the checkbox to allow attendees to "
"invite guests."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Allow invitations`: Označite potrditveno polje, da udeležencem "
"omogočite vabilo gostov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto Confirm`: Only shown if :guilabel:`Resources` has been "
"selected in the :guilabel:`Availability On` field. Tick the checkbox and "
"enter a maximum percentage of the selected resource(s)' total capacity to "
"create a manual confirmation requirement to finalize the meeting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Auto Confirm`: Prikazano samo, če je bilo v "
"polju :guilabel:`Availability On` izbrano :guilabel:`Resources`. Označite "
"potrditveno polje in vnesite največji odstotek celotne zmogljivosti izbranih "
"virov, da ustvarite zahtevo po ročni potrditvi za dokončanje sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:243
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Display pictures`: Tick the checkbox to display user or resource "
"images across the entire booking flow."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Display pictures`: Označite potrditveno polje za prikaz slik "
"uporabnikov ali virov skozi celoten postopek rezervacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:245
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create Opportunity`: When this is selected, each scheduled "
"appointment creates a new **CRM** opportunity."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Create Opportunity`: Ko je to izbrano, vsak načrtovan sestanek "
"ustvari novo priložnost v **CRM**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Up-front Payment`: Tick the checkbox to require users to pay "
"before confirming their booking. Once this is ticked, a link appears "
"to :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Configure Payment Providers`, which "
"enables online payments."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plačilo vnaprej`: potrdite potrditveno polje, da morajo "
"uporabniki plačati pred potrditvijo rezervacije. Ko je potrditveno polje "
"potrjeno, se prikaže povezava do :icon:`oi-arrow-"
"right` :guilabel:`Konfiguracija ponudnikov plačil`, ki omogoča spletna "
"plačila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:250
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Website`: Specify which website this meeting invitation will be "
"published on."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Spletna stran`: določite, na kateri spletni strani bo objavljeno "
"to vabilo na sestanek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:251
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: Select :guilabel:`Weekly` or :guilabel:`Flexible` "
"scheduling."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Schedule`: Izberite :guilabel:`Weekly` ali :guilabel:`Flexible` "
"načrtovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:252
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Allow Bookings`: set a minimum hour window to ensure appointments "
"are confirmed a specified amount of time in advance. For example, set "
"`01:00` to require attendees to confirm at least one hour before their "
"appointment time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Allow Bookings`: nastavite najmanjše časovno okno v urah, da "
"zagotovite, da so sestanki potrjeni določen čas vnaprej. Na primer, "
"nastavite `01:00`, da zahtevate od udeležencev potrditev vsaj eno uro pred "
"časom njihovega sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:255
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Cancellation`: set a maximum hour window before the appointment "
"that attendees are able to cancel."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Cancellation`: nastavite največje časovno okno v urah pred "
"sestankom, v katerem lahko udeleženci preklicujejo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar.rst:257
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Timezone`: This defaults to the company's timezone selected in "
"the **Settings** app. To change the timezone, select the desired option from "
"the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Časovni pas`: privzeto je nastavljen časovni pas podjetja, izbran "
"v aplikaciji **Nastavitve**. Za spremembo časovnega pasu izberite želeno "
"možnost iz spustnega menija."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:3
msgid "Google Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija Google Koledarja"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronize Google Calendar with Odoo to see and manage meetings from both "
"platforms (updates go in both directions). This integration helps organize "
"schedules, so a meeting is never missed."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizirajte Google Koledar z Odoo, da si ogledate in upravljate sestanke "
"z obeh platform (posodobitve se izvajajo v obe smeri). Ta integracija pomaga "
"organizirati razporede, tako da nikoli ne zamudite sestanka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/users/google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`/applications/general/email_communication/google_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:13
msgid "Setup in Google"
msgstr "Nastavitev v Googlu"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:16
msgid "Select (or create) a project"
msgstr "Izberite (ali ustvarite) projekt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:18
msgid ""
"Create a new Google API project and enable the Google Calendar API. First, "
"go to the `Google API Console <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ and "
"log into the Google account."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarite nov projekt Google API in omogočite Google Calendar API. Najprej "
"pojdite na `konzolo Google API <https://console.developers.google.com>`_ in "
"se prijavite v račun Google."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:22
msgid ""
"If this is the first time visiting this page, Google will prompt the user to "
"enter a country and agree to the Terms of Service. Select a country from the "
"drop-down list and agree to the :abbr:`ToS (Terms of Service)`."
msgstr ""
"Če je to prvi obisk te strani, bo Google pozval uporabnika, da vnese državo "
"in soglaša s pogoji storitve. Izberite državo iz spustnega seznama in "
"sprejmite :abbr:`pogoje storitve (Terms of Service)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:26
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Select a project` and select (or create) an API "
"project to configure OAuth in, and store credentials. Click :guilabel:`New "
"Project`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Izberite projekt` in izberite (ali ustvarite) API "
"projekt za konfiguracijo OAuth ter shranjevanje poverilnic. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Nov projekt`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Create a new API project to store credentials."
msgstr "Ustvarite nov API projekt za shranjevanje poverilnic."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:32
msgid ""
"Give the API project a clear name, like `Odoo Sync`, so it can be "
"identified. Then click the :guilabel:`Create` button."
msgstr ""
"API projektu dodelite jasno ime, kot je `Odoo Sync`, da ga bo mogoče "
"prepoznati. Nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:36
msgid "Enable Google calendar API"
msgstr "Omogočanje API-ja Google Koledar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:38
msgid ""
"Now, click on :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` in the left menu. "
"Select :guilabel:`Enabled APIs and Services` again if the :guilabel:`Search "
"bar` does not appear."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Omogočeni API-ji in storitve` v levem meniju. "
"Ponovno izberite :guilabel:`Omogočeni API-ji in storitve`, če "
"se :guilabel:`Iskalna vrstica` ne prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable APIs and Services on the API Project."
msgstr "Omogočite API-je in storitve v API projektu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:44
msgid ""
"After that, search for `Google Calendar API` using the search bar and "
"select :guilabel:`Google Calendar API` from the search results. "
"Click :guilabel:`Enable`."
msgstr ""
"Nato v iskalni vrstici poiščite `Google Calendar API` in iz rezultatov "
"iskanja izberite :guilabel:`Google Calendar API`. "
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Omogoči`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Enable the Google Calendar API."
msgstr "Omogočite Google Calendar API."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:51
msgid "OAuth consent screen"
msgstr "Zaslon za OAuth soglasje"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:53
msgid ""
"Now that the API project has been created, OAuth should be configured. To do "
"that, click on :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` in the left menu, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Get started` button."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj, ko je bil API projekt ustvarjen, je treba konfigurirati OAuth. To "
"storite tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Zaslon za OAuth soglasje` v levem "
"meniju, nato pa kliknete gumb :guilabel:`Začni`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:57
msgid ""
"*Personal* Gmail Accounts are only allowed to be **External** User Type, "
"which means Google may require an approval, or for *Scopes* to be added on. "
"However, using a *Google WorkSpace* account allows for **Internal** User "
"Type to be used."
msgstr ""
"*Osebni* Gmail računi lahko uporabljajo samo vrsto uporabnika **Zunanji**, "
"kar pomeni, da lahko Google zahteva odobritev ali dodajanje *obsegov*. "
"Vendar uporaba *Google WorkSpace* računa omogoča uporabo vrste uporabnika "
"**Notranji**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:61
msgid ""
"Note, as well, that while the API connection is in the *External* testing "
"mode, then no approval is necessary from Google. User limits in this testing "
"mode is set to 100 users."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte tudi, da dokler je povezava API v načinu testiranja *Zunanji*, "
"Google ne zahteva odobritve. Omejitev uporabnikov v tem testnem načinu je "
"nastavljena na 100 uporabnikov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:64
msgid "Follow the proceeding steps, in order:"
msgstr "Sledite naslednjim korakom po vrstnem redu:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:66
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`App Information`, type `Odoo` in the :guilabel:`App name` "
"field, then enter the email address for the :guilabel:`User support email` "
"field and click the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Informacije o aplikaciji` vnesite `Odoo` v polje :guilabel:`Ime "
"aplikacije`, nato vnesite e-poštni naslov v polje :guilabel:`E-pošta za "
"podporo uporabnikom` in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:68
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Audience`, select :guilabel:`External`, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Občinstvo` izberite :guilabel:`Zunanji`, nato kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:69
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Contact Information`, enter the email again, then click "
"the :guilabel:`Next` button."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Kontaktne informacije` ponovno vnesite e-poštni naslov, nato "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Naprej`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:71
msgid ""
"In :guilabel:`Finish`, tick the checkbox to agree to :guilabel:`Google API "
"Services: User Policy.` For the last step, click the :guilabel:`Create` "
"button."
msgstr ""
"V :guilabel:`Zaključek` označite potrditveno polje za strinjanje "
"z :guilabel:`Google API Services: User Policy.` Za zadnji korak kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:75
msgid "Authorized domain setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev pooblaščene domene"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:77
msgid ""
"Next, any domains set to appear on the consent screen or in an OAuth "
"client's configuration must be pre-registered. To do so, navigate "
"to :guilabel:`Branding` in the left menu. In the :guilabel:`Authorized "
"domains` section, click the :guilabel:`Add domain` button to create a field "
"to enter an authorized domain. Enter a domain, such as `odoo.com`, then "
"click the :guilabel:`Save` button at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Nato je treba vnaprej registrirati vse domene, ki bodo prikazane na zaslonu "
"za soglasje ali v konfiguraciji OAuth odjemalca. To storite tako, da "
"odprete :guilabel:`Blagovna znamka` v levem meniju. V "
"razdelku :guilabel:`Pooblaščene domene` kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"domeno`, da ustvarite polje za vnos pooblaščene domene. Vnesite domeno, kot "
"je `odoo.com`, nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Shrani` na dnu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:84
msgid "Test users"
msgstr "Testni uporabniki"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:86
msgid ""
"To give users the ability to sync with personal Gmail accounts, they must be "
"set as a test user. Setup test users by going to :guilabel:`Audience` in the "
"left-side menu and clicking the :guilabel:`Add users` button in "
"the :guilabel:`Test users` section. Enter any desired user emails, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uporabnikom omogočiti sinhronizacijo z osebnimi računi Gmail, "
"morajo biti nastavljeni kot testni uporabniki. Nastavite testne uporabnike "
"tako, da v levem meniju greste na :guilabel:`Audience` in kliknete "
"gumb :guilabel:`Add users` v razdelku :guilabel:`Test users`. Vnesite želene "
"e-poštne naslove uporabnikov in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:92
msgid "Create credentials"
msgstr "Ustvari poverilnice"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:94
msgid ""
"The *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are both needed to connect Google "
"Calendar to Odoo. This is the last step in the Google console. Begin by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Clients` in the left menu. Then, click :guilabel:`Create "
"Credentials`, and select :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`, Google will open a "
"guide to create credentials."
msgstr ""
"*ID odjemalca* in *Skrivnost odjemalca* sta potrebna za povezavo Google "
"Calendarja z Odoo. To je zadnji korak v konzoli Google. Začnite s klikom "
"na :guilabel:`Clients` v levem meniju. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Create "
"Credentials` in izberite :guilabel:`OAuth client ID`. Google bo odprl vodnik "
"za ustvarjanje poverilnic."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:99
msgid ""
"Under :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID`, select :guilabel:`Website "
"application` for the :guilabel:`Application Type` field, and type `My Odoo "
"Database` for the :guilabel:`Name`."
msgstr ""
"V :menuselection:`Create OAuth Client ID` izberite :guilabel:`Website "
"application` za polje :guilabel:`Application Type` in vnesite `My Odoo "
"Database` za :guilabel:`Name`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:102
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins` section, "
"click :guilabel:`+ Add URI` and type the company's Odoo full :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)` address."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Authorized JavaScript Origins` kliknite :guilabel:`+ "
"Add URI` in vnesite popoln :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` naslov "
"Odoo podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:106
msgid ""
"When entering the *Authorized JavaScript Origins*, the exact URL of the Odoo "
"database must be used."
msgstr ""
"Pri vnosu *Dovoljenih izvorov JavaScript* morate uporabiti natančen URL baze "
"podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:109
msgid ""
"If the database is accessible through both an `.odoo.com` subdomain and a "
"custom domain, the custom domain configured as the primary domain should be "
"used. The `.odoo.com` subdomain may not work correctly in all cases and can "
"result in authentication errors."
msgstr ""
"Če je baza podatkov dostopna tako prek poddomene `.odoo.com` kot prek domene "
"po meri, uporabite domeno po meri, konfigurirano kot primarna domena. "
"Poddomena `.odoo.com` v vseh primerih morda ne deluje pravilno in lahko "
"povzroči napake pri avtentikaciji."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:113
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` section, click :guilabel:`+ "
"Add URI` and type the company's Odoo :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` "
"address followed by `/google_account/authentication`. Finally, "
"click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` kliknite :guilabel:`+ Add "
"URI` in vnesite :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` naslov Odoo podjetja, "
"ki mu sledi `/google_account/authentication`. Nazadnje "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Create`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Add the authorized JavaScript origins and the authorized redirect URIs."
msgstr ""
"Dodajte pooblaščena izvora JavaScript in pooblaščene preusmeritvene URI-je."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:120
msgid ""
"A :guilabel:`Client ID` and :guilabel:`Client Secret` will appear, save "
"these somewhere safe."
msgstr ""
"Prikazala se bosta :guilabel:`Client ID` in :guilabel:`Client Secret`, "
"shranite ju na varno mesto."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:123
msgid "Setup in Odoo"
msgstr "Nastavitev v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:125
msgid ""
"Once the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* are located, open the Odoo "
"database and go to :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar` to find "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` feature. Tick the checkbox "
"labeled :guilabel:`Google Calendar`."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta *ID odjemalca* in *Skrivnost odjemalca* pridobljena, odprite bazo "
"Odoo in pojdite na :menuselection:`Settings --> Calendar`, kjer boste našli "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Odkljukajte potrditveno polje z "
"oznako :guilabel:`Google Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "The Google Calendar checkbox in General Settings."
msgstr "Potrditveno polje Google Calendar v splošnih nastavitvah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:132
msgid ""
"Next, copy and paste the *Client ID* and the *Client Secret* from the Google "
"Calendar API credentials page into their respective fields below "
"the :guilabel:`Google Calendar` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nato kopirajte in prilepite *ID odjemalca* in *Skrivnost odjemalca* s strani "
"s poverilnicami Google Calendar API v ustrezna polja pod potrditvenim "
"poljem :guilabel:`Google Calendar`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:137
msgid ""
"Tick the :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization` checkbox to temporarily pause "
"events from being updated. This allows for testing and troubleshooting "
"without removing credentials or uninstalling the synchronization. To resume "
"the sync, clear the checkbox and save."
msgstr ""
"Odkljukajte potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Pause Synchronization`, če želite "
"začasno prekiniti posodabljanje dogodkov. To omogoča testiranje in "
"odpravljanje težav brez odstranjevanja poverilnic ali odstranitve "
"sinhronizacije. Za nadaljevanje sinhronizacije počistite potrditveno polje "
"in shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:142
msgid "Sync calendar in Odoo"
msgstr "Sinhroniziraj koledar v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:144
msgid ""
"Finally, open the :menuselection:`Calendar` app in Odoo and click "
"the :guilabel:`Google` sync button to sync Google Calendar with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje odprite aplikacijo :menuselection:`Koledar` v Odooju in kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Google` za sinhronizacijo, da sinhronizirate Google Koledar "
"z Odoojem."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid ""
"Click the Google sync button in Odoo Calendar to sync Google Calendar with "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite gumb za sinhronizacijo z Googlom v Odoo Koledarju, da "
"sinhronizirate Google Calendar z Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:151
msgid ""
"When syncing Google Calendar with Odoo for the first time, the page will "
"redirect to the Google Account. From there, select the :guilabel:`Email "
"Account` that should have access, then select :guilabel:`Continue` (should "
"the app be unverified), and finally select :guilabel:`Continue` (to give "
"permission for the transfer of data)."
msgstr ""
"Ko prvič sinhronizirate Google Calendar z Odoo, vas stran preusmeri na račun "
"Google. Tam izberite :guilabel:`Email Account`, ki naj ima dostop, nato "
"izberite :guilabel:`Continue` (če aplikacija ni overjena) in končno "
"izberite :guilabel:`Continue` (za dovolitev prenosa podatkov)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Give Odoo permission to access Google Calendar."
msgstr "Dajte Odoo dovoljenje za dostop do Google Calendarja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:159
msgid "Now, Odoo Calendar is successfully synced with Google Calendar!"
msgstr "Sedaj je Odoo Koledar uspešno sinhroniziran z Google Calendarjem!"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:162
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Google calendar synchronization on a test "
"database and a test email address (that is not used for any other purpose) "
"before attempting to sync the desired Google Calendar with the user's "
"production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo močno priporoča testiranje sinhronizacije Google koledarja na testni "
"bazi in testnem e-poštnem naslovu (ki se ne uporablja za noben drug namen), "
"preden poskusite sinhronizirati želeni Google Calendar s produkcijsko bazo "
"uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:166
msgid "Once a user synchronizes their Google calendar with the Odoo calendar:"
msgstr "Ko uporabnik sinhronizira svoj Google koledar z Odoo koledarjem:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:168
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Google to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje dogodka v Odoo povzroči, da Google pošlje povabilo vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:169
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Google to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje dogodka v Odoo povzroči, da Google pošlje odpoved vsem udeležencem "
"dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:170
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Google to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje stika dogodku povzroči, da Google pošlje povabilo vsem udeležencem "
"dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:171
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Google to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Odstranitev stika iz dogodka povzroči, da Google pošlje odpoved vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:173
msgid ""
"Events can be created in *Google Calendar* without sending a notification by "
"selecting :guilabel:`Don't Send` when prompted to send invitation emails."
msgstr ""
"Dogodke lahko ustvarite v *Google Koledarju*, ne da bi poslali obvestilo, "
"tako da ob pozivu za pošiljanje e-poštnih povabil izberete :guilabel:`Don't "
"Send`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:210
msgid "Troubleshoot sync"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav s sinhronizacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:179
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Google Calendar* account does not sync "
"correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se račun *Google Koledar* ne sinhronizira pravilno z Odoo. Težave s "
"sinhronizacijo so vidne v dnevnikih zbirke podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:182
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"V teh primerih je treba račun odpraviti. Ponastavitev lahko izvedete z "
"gumbom :guilabel:`Reset Account`, do katerega dostopate tako, da "
"odprete :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Nato izberite "
"uporabnika za spremembo koledarja in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Calendar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Reset buttons highlighted on the calendar tab of the user."
msgstr "Gumba za ponastavitev, označena na zavihku koledarja uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:190
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:224
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Reset Account` under the correct calendar."
msgstr "Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Reset Account` pod ustreznim koledarjem."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:193
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:227
msgid "Reset options"
msgstr "Možnosti ponastavitve"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:195
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting Google "
"calendar sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Za odpravljanje težav s sinhronizacijo Google koledarja z Odoo so na voljo "
"naslednje možnosti ponastavitve:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Google calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Možnosti ponastavitve Google koledarja v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:200
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:236
msgid ":guilabel:`User's Existing Events`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`User's Existing Events`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:202
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:238
msgid ":guilabel:`Leave them untouched`: no changes to the events."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Leave them untouched`: brez sprememb dogodkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:203
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Google Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Google Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Google Calendar account`: izbriši dogodke "
"iz *Google Koledarja*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:205
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:241
msgid ":guilabel:`Delete from Odoo`: delete the events from the Odoo calendar."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Delete from Odoo`: izbriši dogodke iz Odoo koledarja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Google Calendar* "
"and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: izbriši dogodke iz *Google Koledarja* in Odoo "
"koledarja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:208
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:245
msgid ":guilabel:`Next Synchronization`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Next Synchronization`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sinhroniziraj nove dogodke v "
"*Google Koledarju* in/ali Odoo koledarju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:212
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Google "
"Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj vse obstoječe dogodke`: sinhroniziraj vse dogodke v "
"*Google Calendar* in/ali Odoo koledarju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:215
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:252
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` after making the selection to modify the user's "
"events and the calendar synchronization."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi` po opravljeni izbiri, da spremenite dogodke "
"uporabnika in sinhronizacijo koledarja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:219
msgid "Google OAuth FAQ"
msgstr "Pogosto zastavljena vprašanja o Google OAuth"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:221
msgid ""
"At times there can be configuration errors that occur, and troubleshooting "
"is needed to resolve the issue. Below are the most common errors that may "
"occur when configuring the *Google Calendar* for use with Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Občasno se lahko pojavijo konfiguracijske napake, ki zahtevajo odpravljanje "
"težav. Spodaj so najpogostejše napake, do katerih lahko pride pri "
"konfiguraciji *Google Calendar* za uporabo z Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:226
msgid "Production vs. testing publishing status"
msgstr "Status objave produkcija ali testiranje"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:228
msgid ""
"Choosing :guilabel:`Production` as the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` "
"(instead of :guilabel:`Testing`) displays the following warning message:"
msgstr ""
"Izbira :guilabel:`Production` kot :guilabel:`Publishing Status` "
"(namesto :guilabel:`Testing`) prikaže naslednje opozorilo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:231
msgid ""
"`OAuth is limited to 100 sensitive scope logins until the OAuth consent "
"screen is verified. This may require a verification process that can take "
"several days.`"
msgstr ""
"`OAuth je omejen na 100 prijav z občutljivimi dovoljenji, dokler OAuth "
"zaslon za soglasje ni preverjen. To lahko zahteva postopek preverjanja, ki "
"lahko traja več dni.`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:234
msgid ""
"To correct this warning, navigate to the `Google API Platform <https://"
"console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. If "
"the :guilabel:`Publishing Status` is :guilabel:`In Production`, "
"click :guilabel:`Back to Testing` to correct the issue."
msgstr ""
"Za popravek tega opozorila se pomaknite na `Google API Platform <https://"
"console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials/consent>`_. Če "
"je :guilabel:`Publishing Status` nastavljen na :guilabel:`In Production`, "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Back to Testing`, da popravite težavo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:239
msgid "No test users added"
msgstr "Testni uporabniki niso dodani"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:241
msgid ""
"If no test users are added to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, then "
"an :guilabel:`Error 403: access_denied` populates."
msgstr ""
"Če niso dodani testni uporabniki na :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, se "
"prikaže :guilabel:`Error 403: access_denied`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "403 Access Denied Error."
msgstr "Napaka 403 dostop zavrnjen."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:247
msgid ""
"To correct this error, return to the :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen`, "
"under :guilabel:`APIs & Services`, and add test users to the app. Add the "
"email to be configured in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Za popravek te napake se vrnite na :guilabel:`OAuth consent screen` "
"pod :guilabel:`APIs & Services` in dodajte testne uporabnike aplikaciji. "
"Dodajte e-poštni naslov, ki bo konfiguriran v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:251
msgid "Application Type"
msgstr "Vrsta aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:253
msgid ""
"When creating the credentials (OAuth *Client ID* and *Client Secret*), "
"if :guilabel:`Desktop App` is selected for the :guilabel:`Application Type`, "
"an :guilabel:`Authorization Error` appears (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju poverilnic (OAuth *Client ID* in *Client Secret*), če je "
"za :guilabel:`Application Type` izbrano :guilabel:`Desktop App`, se "
"prikaže :guilabel:`Authorization Error` (:guilabel:`Error "
"400:redirect_uri_mismatch`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:None
msgid "Error 400 Redirect URI Mismatch."
msgstr "Napaka 400 Redirect URI Mismatch."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:260
msgid ""
"To correct this error, delete the existing credentials, and create new "
"credentials, by selecting :guilabel:`Web Application` for "
"the :guilabel:`Application Type`."
msgstr ""
"Za popravek te napake izbrišite obstoječe poverilnice in ustvarite nove "
"tako, da za :guilabel:`Application Type` izberete :guilabel:`Web "
"Application`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:263
msgid ""
"Then, under :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs`, click :guilabel:`ADD URI`, "
"and type: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication` in the "
"field, being sure to replace *yourdbname* in the URL with the **real** Odoo "
"database name."
msgstr ""
"Nato pod :guilabel:`Authorized redirect URIs` kliknite :guilabel:`ADD URI` "
"in v polje vnesite: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/"
"authentication`, pri čemer zamenjajte *yourdbname* v URL-ju z **dejanskim** "
"imenom baze podatkov Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:268
msgid ""
"Ensure that the domain (used in the URI: `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/"
"google_account/authentication`) is the exact same domain as configured in "
"the `web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je domena (uporabljena v URI: `https://"
"yourdbname.odoo.com/google_account/authentication`) popolnoma enaka domeni, "
"kot je konfigurirana v sistemskem parametru `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/google.rst:272
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`."
msgstr ""
"Do `web.base.url` dostopate tako, da aktivirate :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>` in se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Technical header menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:3
msgid "Outlook Calendar synchronization"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija Outlook Calendar"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:5
msgid ""
"Synchronizing a user's *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo is useful for keeping "
"track of tasks and appointments across all related applications."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizacija uporabnikovega *Outlook Calendar* z Odoom je uporabna za "
"sledenje nalogam in sestankom v vseh povezanih aplikacijah."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:9
msgid ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/users/azure`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:10
msgid ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/email_communication/azure_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:13
msgid "Microsoft Azure setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev Microsoft Azure"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:15
msgid ""
"To sync the *Outlook Calendar* with Odoo's *Calendar*, a Microsoft *Azure* "
"account is required. Creating an account is free for users who have never "
"tried, or paid for, *Azure*. For more information, view the account options "
"on the `Azure website <https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/?"
"WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."
msgstr ""
"Za sinhronizacijo *Outlook Calendar* z Odoo *Calendar* je potreben račun "
"Microsoft *Azure*. Ustvarjanje računa je brezplačno za uporabnike, ki še "
"nikoli niso preizkusili ali plačali storitve *Azure*. Za več informacij si "
"oglejte možnosti računa na `spletni strani Azure <https://"
"azure.microsoft.com/en-us/free/?WT.mc_id=A261C142F>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:20
msgid ""
"Refer to `Microsoft's documentation <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/"
"active-directory/ develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ on how to set up a "
"Microsoft *Entra ID* (formally called Microsoft *Azure Active Directory "
"(Azure AD)*). This is an API console to manage and register Microsoft "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Glejte `Microsoftovo dokumentacijo <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/"
"active-directory/develop/quickstart-create-new-tenant>`_ o tem, kako "
"nastaviti Microsoft *Entra ID* (prej imenovan Microsoft *Azure Active "
"Directory (Azure AD)*). To je konzola API za upravljanje in registracijo "
"Microsoftovih aplikacij."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:25
msgid ""
"Existing Microsoft *Entra ID* users should log in at the `Microsoft Azure "
"developer portal <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Next, "
"select :guilabel:`View` under the section labeled :guilabel:`Manage "
"Microsoft Entra ID`."
msgstr ""
"Obstoječi uporabniki Microsoft *Entra ID* se morajo prijaviti na "
"`razvijalski portal Microsoft Azure <https://portal.azure.com/#home>`_. Nato "
"izberite :guilabel:`View` v razdelku z oznako :guilabel:`Manage Microsoft "
"Entra ID`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:30
msgid "Register application"
msgstr "Registracija aplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:32
msgid ""
"After logging in with the Microsoft *Entra ID*, `register an application "
"<https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-"
"register-app>`_."
msgstr ""
"Po prijavi z Microsoft *Entra ID* `registrirajte aplikacijo <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/quickstart-register-"
"app>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:35
msgid ""
"To create an application, click :guilabel:`+ Add` in the top menu. From the "
"resulting drop-down menu, select :guilabel:`App Registration`."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje aplikacije kliknite :guilabel:`+ Add` v zgornjem meniju. Iz "
"spustnega menija izberite :guilabel:`App Registration`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Microsoft Azure management page with + Add and App Registration menu "
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Stran za upravljanje Microsoft Azure s poudarjenima menijema + Add in App "
"Registration."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:42
msgid "Enter a unique :guilabel:`Name` for the connected application."
msgstr "Vnesite edinstveno :guilabel:`Name` za povezano aplikacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:44
msgid ""
"Choosing the appropriate :guilabel:`Supported account type` is essential, or "
"else the connected application will not work. Users who wish to connect "
"their *Outlook Calendar* to Odoo should select the :guilabel:`Accounts in "
"any organizational directory (Any Microsoft Entra ID directory - "
"Multitenant) and personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. Skype, Xbox)` option "
"for :guilabel:`Supported account types`."
msgstr ""
"Izbira ustrezne :guilabel:`Supported account type` je bistvena, sicer "
"povezana aplikacija ne bo delovala. Uporabniki, ki želijo povezati svoj "
"*Outlook Calendar* z Odoom, naj izberejo možnost :guilabel:`Accounts in any "
"organizational directory (Any Microsoft Entra ID directory - Multitenant) "
"and personal Microsoft accounts (e.g. Skype, Xbox)` za :guilabel:`Supported "
"account types`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:50
msgid ""
"When configuring the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`, choose the :guilabel:`Web` "
"option from the first drop-down menu. Then, enter the Odoo database URI "
"(URL) followed by `/microsoft_account/authentication`."
msgstr ""
"Pri konfiguraciji :guilabel:`Redirect URI` izberite možnost :guilabel:`Web` "
"iz prvega spustnega menija. Nato vnesite URI (URL) zbirke podatkov Odoo, ki "
"mu sledi `/microsoft_account/authentication`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:55
msgid ""
"Enter `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` for "
"the :guilabel:`Redirect URI`. Replace `yourdbname.odoo.com` with "
"the :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)`."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite `https://yourdbname.odoo.com/microsoft_account/authentication` "
"za :guilabel:`Redirect URI`. Zamenjajte `yourdbname.odoo.com` z :abbr:`URL "
"(Uniform Resource Locator)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:59
msgid ""
"Ensure the database's :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (domain) used "
"in the URI is the exact same domain as the one configured on the "
"`web.base.url` system parameter."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je :abbr:`URL (Uniform Resource Locator)` (domena) zbirke "
"podatkov, uporabljen v URI, popolnoma enak domeni, konfigurirani v "
"sistemskem parametru `web.base.url`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:62
msgid ""
"Access the `web.base.url` by activating :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`, and navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Technical header "
"menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`. Then, select it from "
"the :guilabel:`Key` list on the :guilabel:`System Parameters` page."
msgstr ""
"Do `web.base.url` dostopate tako, da aktivirate :ref:`razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode>` in se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Technical header menu --> Parameters section --> System Parameters`. Nato ga "
"izberite s seznama :guilabel:`Key` na strani :guilabel:`System Parameters`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"The \"Supported account type\" and \"Redirect URI\" settings in the "
"Microsoft Entra ID portal."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitvi \"Supported account type\" in \"Redirect URI\" v portalu "
"Microsoft Entra ID."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:71
msgid ""
"For more information on the restrictions and limitations of URIs, check "
"Microsoft's `Redirect URI (reply URL) restrictions and limitations <https://"
"docs.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/active-directory/develop/reply-url>`_ page."
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o omejitvah URI glejte Microsoftovo stran `Redirect URI "
"(reply URL) restrictions and limitations <https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/"
"azure/active-directory/develop/reply-url>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:75
msgid ""
"Finally, on the application registration page, click :guilabel:`Register` "
"button to complete the application registration. The :guilabel:`Application "
"(client) ID` is produced. Copy this value, as it is needed later, in "
"the :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje na strani za registracijo aplikacije kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Register`, da dokončate registracijo aplikacije. Ustvari "
"se :guilabel:`Application (client) ID`. Kopirajte to vrednost, saj bo "
"potrebna pozneje v :ref:`outlook_calendar/odoo_setup`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"Application client ID highlighted in the essentials section of the newly "
"created\n"
"application."
msgstr ""
"ID odjemalca aplikacije označen v razdelku z osnovnimi podatki na novo "
"ustvarjene aplikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:85
msgid "Create client secret"
msgstr "Ustvari skrivnost odjemalca"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:87
msgid ""
"The second credential needed to complete the synchronization of the "
"Microsoft *Outlook Calendar* is the *Client Secret*. The user **must** add a "
"client secret, as this allows Odoo to authenticate itself, requiring no "
"interaction from the user's side. *Certificates* are optional."
msgstr ""
"Druga poverilnica, potrebna za dokončanje sinhronizacije koledarja Microsoft "
"*Outlook*, je *skrivnost odjemalca*. Uporabnik **mora** dodati skrivnost "
"odjemalca, saj to omogoča, da se Odoo avtenticira brez interakcije s strani "
"uporabnika. *Certifikati* so neobvezni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:91
msgid ""
"To add a client secret, click :menuselection:`Certificates & secrets` in the "
"left menu. Then click :guilabel:`+ New client secret` to create the client "
"secret."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje skrivnosti odjemalca kliknite :menuselection:`Certifikati in "
"skrivnosti` v levem meniju. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`+ Nova skrivnost "
"odjemalca`, da ustvarite skrivnost odjemalca."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid ""
"New client secret page with certificates and secrets menu and new client "
"secret option\n"
"highlighted."
msgstr ""
"Stran za novo skrivnost odjemalca s poudarjenima menijem za certifikate in "
"skrivnosti ter možnostjo za novo skrivnost odjemalca."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:99
msgid ""
"Next, type a :guilabel:`Description`, and select when the client "
"secret :guilabel:`Expires`. Available options include: :guilabel:`90 days (3 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`365 days (12 months)`, :guilabel:`545 days (18 "
"months)`, :guilabel:`730 days (24 months)` or :guilabel:`Custom`. "
"The :guilabel:`Custom` option allows the administrator to set "
"a :guilabel:`Start` and :guilabel:`End` date."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite :guilabel:`Opis` in izberite, kdaj skrivnost "
"odjemalca :guilabel:`Poteče`. Na voljo so možnosti: :guilabel:`90 dni (3 "
"mesece)`, :guilabel:`365 dni (12 mesecev)`, :guilabel:`545 dni (18 "
"mesecev)`, :guilabel:`730 dni (24 mesecev)` ali :guilabel:`Po meri`. "
"Možnost :guilabel:`Po meri` omogoča skrbniku, da nastavi "
"datum :guilabel:`Začetek` in :guilabel:`Konec`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:105
msgid "Finally, click :guilabel:`Add` to :guilabel:`Add a client secret`."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`, da :guilabel:`Dodate skrivnost "
"odjemalca`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:108
msgid ""
"Since resetting the synchronization can be tricky, Odoo recommends setting "
"the maximum allowed expiration date for the client secret (24 months or "
"custom), so there is no need to re-synchronize soon."
msgstr ""
"Ker je lahko ponovna nastavitev sinhronizacije zapletena, Odoo priporoča "
"nastavitev najdaljšega dovoljenega datuma poteka za skrivnost odjemalca (24 "
"mesecev ali po meri), da ne bo potrebe po ponovni sinhronizaciji v kratkem "
"času."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:112
msgid "Copy the :guilabel:`Value` for use in the next section."
msgstr "Kopirajte :guilabel:`Vrednost` za uporabo v naslednjem razdelku."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:115
msgid ""
"Client secret values cannot be viewed, except immediately after creation. Be "
"sure to save the secret when created *before* leaving the page."
msgstr ""
"Vrednosti skrivnosti odjemalca ni mogoče pregledati, razen takoj po "
"ustvarjanju. Prepričajte se, da skrivnost shranite ob ustvarjanju, *preden* "
"zapustite stran."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:121
msgid "Configuration in Odoo"
msgstr "Konfiguracija v Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:123
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, go to :menuselection:`Calendar app --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, and tick the checkbox beside the :guilabel:`Outlook Calendar` "
"setting. Remember to click :guilabel:`Save` to implement the changes."
msgstr ""
"V zbirki podatkov Odoo pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Koledar --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in potrdite potrditveno polje poleg "
"nastavitve :guilabel:`Koledar Outlook`. Ne pozabite "
"klikniti :guilabel:`Shrani`, da uveljavite spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook Calendar\" setting activated in Odoo."
msgstr "Nastavitev \"Koledar Outlook\" aktivirana v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:130
msgid ""
"From the Microsoft *Azure* portal, under the :guilabel:`Overview` section of "
"the application, copy the :guilabel:`Application (Client) ID`, if it has not "
"already been copied, and paste it into the :guilabel:`Client ID` field in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Na portalu Microsoft *Azure*, v razdelku :guilabel:`Pregled` aplikacije, "
"kopirajte :guilabel:`ID aplikacije (odjemalca)`, če še ni bil kopiran, in ga "
"prilepite v polje :guilabel:`ID odjemalca` v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client ID\" in the Microsoft Azure portal."
msgstr "\"ID odjemalca\" na portalu Microsoft Azure."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:138
msgid ""
"Copy the previously-acquired :guilabel:`Value` (Client Secret Value), and "
"paste it into the :guilabel:`Client Secret` field in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kopirajte predhodno pridobljeno :guilabel:`Vrednost` (vrednost skrivnosti "
"odjemalca) in jo prilepite v polje :guilabel:`Skrivnost odjemalca` v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Client Secret\" token to be copied from Microsoft to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Žeton \"Skrivnost odjemalca\", ki ga je treba kopirati iz Microsofta v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:145
msgid ""
"Finally, on the Odoo :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings` page, "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje na strani Odoo :menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Splošne nastavitve` "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:150
msgid "Sync with Outlook"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija z Outlookom"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:154
msgid ""
"Odoo highly recommends testing the Outlook calendar synchronization on a "
"test database and a test email address (that is not used for any other "
"purpose) before attempting to sync the desired Outlook Calendar with the "
"user's production database."
msgstr ""
"Odoo močno priporoča testiranje sinhronizacije koledarja Outlook v testni "
"zbirki podatkov in s testnim e-poštnim naslovom (ki se ne uporablja za noben "
"drug namen), preden poskusite sinhronizirati želeni koledar Outlook z "
"produkcijsko zbirko podatkov uporabnika."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:158
msgid ""
"If the user has any past, present, or future events on their Odoo calendar "
"before syncing their Outlook calendar, Outlook will treat the events pulled "
"from Odoo's calendar during the sync as new events, causing an email "
"notification to be sent from Outlook to all the event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Če ima uporabnik kakršne koli pretekle, sedanje ali prihodnje dogodke v "
"svojem Odoo koledarju pred sinhronizacijo z Outlookovim koledarjem, bo "
"Outlook dogodke, prenesene iz Odoovega koledarja med sinhronizacijo, "
"obravnaval kot nove dogodke, kar bo povzročilo, da bo Outlook poslal e-"
"poštno obvestilo vsem udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:162
msgid ""
"To avoid unwanted emails being sent to all past, present, and future event "
"attendees, the user must add the events from the Odoo calendar to the "
"Outlook calendar before the first ever sync, delete the events from Odoo, "
"and then start the sync."
msgstr ""
"Da se izognete pošiljanju neželenih e-poštnih sporočil vsem preteklim, "
"sedanjim in prihodnjim udeležencem dogodkov, mora uporabnik dogodke iz Odoo "
"koledarja dodati v Outlookov koledar pred prvo sinhronizacijo, izbrisati "
"dogodke iz Odooja in šele nato začeti sinhronizacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:166
msgid ""
"Even after synchronizing the Odoo Calendar with the Outlook calendar, "
"Outlook will still send a notification to all event participants every time "
"an event is edited (created, deleted, unarchived, or event date/time "
"changed), with no exceptions. This is a limitation that cannot be fixed from "
"Odoo's side."
msgstr ""
"Tudi po sinhronizaciji Odoo koledarja z Outlookovim koledarjem bo Outlook še "
"vedno pošiljal obvestilo vsem udeležencem dogodka vsakič, ko je dogodek "
"urejen (ustvarjen, izbrisan, razarhiviran ali spremenjen datum/čas dogodka), "
"brez izjem. To je omejitev, ki je ni mogoče odpraviti s strani Odooja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:171
msgid ""
"In summary, once a user synchronizes their Outlook calendar with the Odoo "
"calendar:"
msgstr ""
"Skratka, ko uporabnik sinhronizira svoj Outlookov koledar z Odoo koledarjem:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:173
msgid ""
"Creating an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Ustvarjanje dogodka v Odooju povzroči, da Outlook pošlje vabilo vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:174
msgid ""
"Deleting an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all event "
"attendees."
msgstr ""
"Brisanje dogodka v Odooju povzroči, da Outlook pošlje preklic vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:175
msgid ""
"Unarchiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Razarhiviranje dogodka v Odooju povzroči, da Outlook pošlje vabilo vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:176
msgid ""
"Archiving an event in Odoo causes Outlook to send a cancellation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Arhiviranje dogodka v Odooju povzroči, da Outlook pošlje preklic vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:177
msgid ""
"Adding a contact to an event causes Outlook to send an invitation to all "
"event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje stika dogodku povzroči, da Outlook pošlje vabilo vsem udeležencem "
"dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:178
msgid ""
"Removing a contact from an event causes Outlook to send a cancellation to "
"all event attendees."
msgstr ""
"Odstranjevanje stika iz dogodka povzroči, da Outlook pošlje preklic vsem "
"udeležencem dogodka."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:181
msgid "Sync Odoo Calendar and Outlook"
msgstr "Sinhronizacija Odoo koledarja in Outlooka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:183
msgid ""
"In the Odoo database, open to the *Calendar* module, and click "
"the :guilabel:`Outlook` sync button on the right-side of the page, beneath "
"the monthly calendar."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo bazi odprite modul *Koledar* in kliknite gumb za "
"sinhronizacijo :guilabel:`Outlook` na desni strani strani, pod mesečnim "
"koledarjem."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "The \"Outlook\" sync button in Odoo Calendar."
msgstr "Gumb za sinhronizacijo \"Outlook\" v Odoo koledarju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:190
msgid ""
"The synchronization is a two-way process, meaning that events are reconciled "
"in both accounts (*Outlook* and Odoo). The page redirects to a Microsoft "
"login page, and the user is asked to log in to their account, if they are "
"not already. Finally, grant the required permissions by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Accept`."
msgstr ""
"Sinhronizacija je dvosmeren proces, kar pomeni, da se dogodki uskladijo v "
"obeh računih (*Outlook* in Odoo). Stran preusmeri na Microsoftovo prijavno "
"stran in uporabnik je pozvan, da se prijavi v svoj račun, če še ni "
"prijavljen. Končno dodelite zahtevana dovoljenja s klikom "
"na :guilabel:`Sprejmi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Authentication process on Microsoft Outlook OAuth page."
msgstr "Postopek preverjanja pristnosti na Microsoftovi Outlook OAuth strani."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:200
msgid ""
"All users that want to use the synchronization simply need to :ref:`sync "
"their calendar with Outlook <outlook/sync>`. The configuration of "
"Microsoft's *Azure* account is only done once, as Microsoft *Entra ID* "
"tenants' client IDs and client secrets are unique, and help the user manage "
"a specific instance of Microsoft cloud services for internal and external "
"users."
msgstr ""
"Vsi uporabniki, ki želijo uporabljati sinhronizacijo, morajo "
"preprosto :ref:`sinhronizirati svoj koledar z Outlookom <outlook/sync>`. "
"Konfiguracija Microsoftovega računa *Azure* se izvede samo enkrat, saj so ID-"
"ji odjemalcev in skrivnosti odjemalcev Microsoftovih najemnikov *Entra ID* "
"edinstveni in uporabniku pomagajo upravljati določen primerek Microsoftovih "
"storitev v oblaku za notranje in zunanje uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:206
msgid ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:207
msgid ":doc:`google`"
msgstr ":doc:`google`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:212
msgid ""
"There may be times when the *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* account does not "
"sync correctly with Odoo. Sync issues can be seen in the database logs."
msgstr ""
"Včasih se račun *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* ne sinhronizira pravilno z "
"Odoojem. Težave s sinhronizacijo so vidne v dnevnikih baze podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:215
msgid ""
"In these cases, the account needs troubleshooting. A reset can be performed "
"using the :guilabel:`Reset Account` button, which can be accessed by "
"navigating to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Manage Users`. Then, select "
"the user to modify the calendar, and click on the :guilabel:`Calendar` tab."
msgstr ""
"V teh primerih je treba račun diagnosticirati. Ponastavitev je mogoče "
"izvesti z gumbom :guilabel:`Ponastavi račun`, do katerega lahko dostopate "
"tako, da se pomaknete na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> "
"Upravljanje uporabnikov`. Nato izberite uporabnika za spreminjanje koledarja "
"in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Koledar`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:229
msgid ""
"The following reset options are available for troubleshooting *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* sync with Odoo:"
msgstr ""
"Naslednje možnosti ponastavitve so na voljo za odpravljanje težav pri "
"sinhronizaciji *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* z Odoo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:None
msgid "Outlook calendar reset options in Odoo."
msgstr "Možnosti ponastavitve koledarja Outlook v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:239
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from the current Microsoft Calendar account`: delete the "
"events from *Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbriši iz trenutnega računa Microsoft Calendar`: izbriši dogodke "
"iz *Microsoft Outlook Calendar*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:242
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delete from both`: delete the events from both *Microsoft Outlook "
"Calendar* and Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbriši iz obeh`: izbriši dogodke iz *Microsoft Outlook Calendar* "
"in koledarja Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:247
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize only new events`: sync new events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj samo nove dogodke`: sinhroniziraj nove dogodke v "
"*Microsoft Outlook Calendar* in/ali koledarju Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/calendar/outlook.rst:249
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Synchronize all existing events`: sync all events on *Microsoft "
"Outlook Calendar* and/or Odoo calendar."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sinhroniziraj vse obstoječe dogodke`: sinhroniziraj vse dogodke v "
"*Microsoft Outlook Calendar* in/ali koledarju Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:5
msgid "Dashboards"
msgstr "Nadzorne  plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Odoo Dashboards** allows you to consult, interact with, customize, and "
"build interactive dashboards that display real-time data from your Odoo "
"database in an easy-to-understand way. By centralizing data from various "
"Odoo sources in a single location, dashboards provide an overview of key "
"business metrics that can help you monitor business performance and make "
"informed decisions."
msgstr ""
"**Nadzorne plošče Odoo** vam omogočajo pregledovanje, interakcijo, "
"prilagajanje in gradnjo interaktivnih nadzornih plošč, ki prikazujejo "
"podatke v realnem času iz vaše podatkovne baze Odoo na enostaven in "
"razumljiv način. S centralizacijo podatkov iz različnih virov Odoo na enem "
"mestu nadzorne plošče zagotavljajo pregled ključnih poslovnih meritev, ki "
"vam lahko pomagajo spremljati poslovno uspešnost in sprejemati informirane "
"odločitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:18
msgid ""
":doc:`Odoo spreadsheets <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` serve "
"as the foundation for dashboards, with tables and charts used to structure "
"and visualize dynamic Odoo data. :ref:`Data sources <spreadsheet/insert/data-"
"sources>` connect a dashboard's underlying spreadsheet to your database, "
"ensuring the most recent data is retrieved every time the dashboard is "
"opened or refreshed."
msgstr ""
":doc:`Odoo preglednice <../../applications/productivity/spreadsheet>` "
"služijo kot osnova za nadzorne plošče, s tabelami in grafikoni, ki se "
"uporabljajo za strukturiranje in vizualizacijo dinamičnih podatkov "
"Odoo. :ref:`Podatkovni viri <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` povežejo "
"osnovno preglednico nadzorne plošče z vašo podatkovno bazo in zagotavljajo, "
"da se ob vsakem odprtju ali osveževanju nadzorne plošče pridobijo najnovejši "
"podatki."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:24
msgid ""
"With Odoo Dashboards, users can, depending on their :ref:`access rights "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`:"
msgstr ""
"Z Odoo Nadzornimi ploščami lahko uporabniki, odvisno od svojih :ref:`pravic "
"dostopa <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:27
msgid ""
":ref:`consult and interact with dashboards <dashboards/use-dashboards>`, "
"including :ref:`standard, pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`pregledovanje nadzornih plošč in interakcija z njimi <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards>`, vključno s :ref:`standardnimi, vnaprej konfiguriranimi "
"nadzornimi ploščami <dashboards/standard>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:29
msgid ""
"use :ref:`global filters <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` to "
"filter all the data shown on a dashboard"
msgstr ""
"uporaba :ref:`globalnih filtrov <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` "
"za filtriranje vseh podatkov, prikazanih na nadzorni plošči"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:31
msgid ""
":ref:`share a snapshot of a dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` with "
"internal users who do not have the appropriate access rights or with "
"external users"
msgstr ""
":ref:`delijo posnetek nadzorne plošče <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` z "
"notranjimi uporabniki, ki nimajo ustreznih pravic dostopa, ali z zunanjimi "
"uporabniki"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:33
msgid ""
":doc:`build custom dashboards <../../applications/productivity/dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>` using Odoo Spreadsheet"
msgstr ""
":doc:`gradijo nadzorne plošče po meri <../../applications/productivity/"
"dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` z uporabo Odoo Preglednice"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:36
msgid ""
":ref:`customize dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` to "
"modify what data is shown, the layout, or the filters available"
msgstr ""
":ref:`prilagodijo nadzorne plošče <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>`, da spremenijo, kateri podatki se prikazujejo, razporeditev ali "
"razpoložljive filtre"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`manage access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` to dashboards"
msgstr ""
":ref:`upravljajo pravice dostopa <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` do "
"nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:39
msgid ""
"centralize frequently consulted Odoo views in a personal :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"
msgstr ""
"centralizacija pogosto pregledovanih pogledov Odoo v osebni :doc:`../../"
"applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only be "
"accessed via the Dashboards app."
msgstr ""
"Ko je preglednica pretvorjena v nadzorno ploščo, je dostopna samo prek "
"aplikacije Nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:45
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, :guilabel:`My Dashboard` is not based on Odoo "
"Spreadsheet, but rather on :doc:`Odoo views <../studio/views>`."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od drugih Odoo nadzornih plošč :guilabel:`Moja nadzorna plošča` "
"ni osnovana na Odoo Preglednici, temveč na :doc:`Odoo pogledih <../studio/"
"views>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:51
msgid "Use dashboards"
msgstr "Uporaba nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"When the Dashboards app is opened, the left panel lists all :ref:`standard, "
"pre-configured dashboards <dashboards/standard>` and :doc:`custom-built "
"dashboards <dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards>` to which a user has "
"been :ref:`granted access <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, grouped by "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Ko je aplikacija Nadzorne plošče odprta, levi panel našteje "
"vse :ref:`standardne, vnaprej konfigurirane nadzorne plošče <dashboards/"
"standard>` in :doc:`nadzorne plošče po meri <dashboards/"
"build_and_customize_dashboards>`, do katerih ima uporabnik :ref:`dodeljen "
"dostop <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`, združene po razdelkih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:58
msgid "Clicking on a dashboard name opens that dashboard in the main view."
msgstr ""
"Klik na ime nadzorne plošče odpre to nadzorno ploščo v glavnem pogledu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Overview of Leads dashboard"
msgstr "Pregled nadzorne plošče priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:64
msgid ""
"Click the :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(double chevron)` icon at "
"the top of the left panel to collapse the left panel, maximizing the space "
"available for dashboards."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-angle-double-left` :guilabel:`(dvojni puščici)` na "
"vrhu levega panela, da zložite levi panel in tako povečate prostor, ki je na "
"voljo za nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:66
msgid ""
"Mark a dashboard as a favorite by clicking the :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Toggle favorite)` icon in the upper-right corner. "
"Favorited dashboards are grouped in a :guilabel:`Favorites` section at the "
"top of the left panel for easy access."
msgstr ""
"Označite nadzorno ploščo kot priljubljeno s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-"
"star` :guilabel:`(Preklopi priljubljeno)` v zgornjem desnem kotu. "
"Priljubljene nadzorne plošče so združene v razdelku :guilabel:`Priljubljene` "
"na vrhu levega panela za enostaven dostop."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:73
msgid "Filter and sort data"
msgstr "Filtriranje in razvrščanje podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:75
msgid ""
"Filtering and sorting allow you to manage what data is displayed and how it "
"is displayed. This can help tailor the view to answer specific business "
"questions."
msgstr ""
"Filtriranje in razvrščanje omogočata upravljanje s tem, kateri podatki so "
"prikazani in kako so prikazani. To lahko pomaga prilagoditi pogled za "
"odgovarjanje na specifična poslovna vprašanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:78
msgid ""
":ref:`Filtering <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` limits the data "
"presented in charts and tables, allowing you to focus only on records that "
"meet specific criteria,  e.g., viewing sales data only for a specific sales "
"team."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Filtriranje <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` omejuje "
"podatke, prikazane v grafikonih in tabelah, kar vam omogoča osredotočenje "
"samo na zapise, ki izpolnjujejo določena merila, npr. ogled podatkov o "
"prodaji samo za določeno prodajno ekipo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:81
msgid ""
":ref:`Sorting <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` reorders the data presented "
"in table columns, allowing you to see the data from different perspectives, "
"e.g., viewing products by sales revenue from highest to lowest."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Razvrščanje <dashboards/use-dashboards/sort>` preuredi podatke, "
"prikazane v stolpcih tabele, kar vam omogoča ogled podatkov iz različnih "
"perspektiv, npr. ogled izdelkov po prihodkih od prodaje od najvišjih do "
"najnižjih."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:88
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:387
msgid "Apply global filters"
msgstr "Uporabi globalne filtre"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:90
msgid ""
"If :doc:`global filters <spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` have "
"been configured for a dashboard, a search bar is available above the "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Če so bili za nadzorno ploščo konfigurirani :doc:`globalni filtri "
"<spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>`, je nad nadzorno ploščo na "
"voljo iskalna vrstica."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Global filters on the Project dashboard"
msgstr "Globalni filtri na nadzorni plošči Projekt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:98
msgid ""
"Global filters are available for all :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/"
"standard>`. Additional :doc:`global filters can be added <spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/global_filters>` by a user with the appropriate :ref:`access "
"rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`."
msgstr ""
"Globalni filtri so na voljo za vse :ref:`standardne nadzorne plošče "
"<dashboards/standard>`. Dodatni :doc:`globalni filtri se lahko dodajo "
"<spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters>` s strani uporabnika z "
"ustreznimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-"
"configure-build>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:102
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`search for values <search/values>` by typing "
"directly in the search bar; the search categories shown reflect the "
"available global filters."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako je mogoče :ref:`iskati vrednosti <search/values>` z neposrednim "
"vpisovanjem v iskalno vrstico; prikazane kategorije iskanja odražajo "
"razpoložljive globalne filtre."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:105
msgid "To apply global filters:"
msgstr "Za uporabo globalnih filtrov:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:107
msgid ""
"Click within the search bar or click on the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon to access all filters available for that "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite v iskalno vrstico ali kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(spustni meni)`, da dostopate do vseh filtrov, ki so na "
"voljo za to nadzorno ploščo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:109
msgid ""
"For the relevant filter, select a conditional operator from the first "
"dropdown, e.g., :guilabel:`is in`, then, as relevant, enter or select the "
"appropriate value."
msgstr ""
"Za ustrezen filter izberite pogojni operator iz prvega spustnega menija, "
"npr. :guilabel:`je v`, nato po potrebi vnesite ali izberite ustrezno "
"vrednost."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/work_with_data/global_filters.rst:401
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Filter`."
msgstr "Kliknite :guilabel:`Filtriraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:113
msgid ""
"For dashboards with a date filter, this filter can be set via the search bar "
"or via the button with the :icon:`fa-calendar` :guilabel:`(calendar)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Za nadzorne plošče z datumskim filtrom se ta filter lahko nastavi prek "
"iskalne vrstice ali prek gumba z ikono :icon:`fa-"
"calendar` :guilabel:`(koledar)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Filtering a dashboard by date period"
msgstr "Filtriranje nadzorne plošče po datumskem obdobju"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:119
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Custom Range` at the bottom of the period selector shows "
"either a manually entered custom range, if relevant, or the start and end "
"date of the selected period."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Območje po meri` na dnu izbirnika obdobja prikazuje bodisi ročno "
"vneseno območje po meri, če je relevantno, ali začetni in končni datum "
"izbranega obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:122
msgid ""
"To remove a value from a filter, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon beside the name of the value; to empty a "
"filter, click the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon at the far "
"right of the filter."
msgstr ""
"Za odstranitev vrednosti iz filtra kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(odstrani)` poleg imena vrednosti; za praznjenje filtra "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(odstrani)` na skrajni desni "
"strani filtra."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:129
msgid "Sort data"
msgstr "Razvrsti podatke"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:131
msgid ""
"Depending on the dashboard and the table in question, it may be possible to "
"sort the data by column, by clicking the column heading. A :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(caret down)` or :icon:`fa-caret-up` :guilabel:`(caret up)` "
"icon beside a column heading indicates that the column has been sorted in "
"descending or ascending order, respectively. If, when hovering over other "
"column headings, a :icon:`fa-sort` :guilabel:`(sort)` icon appears, the "
"column can be sorted."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od nadzorne plošče in zadevne tabele je morda mogoče razvrstiti "
"podatke po stolpcu s klikom na glavo stolpca. Ikona :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(puščica navzdol)` ali :icon:`fa-caret-"
"up` :guilabel:`(puščica navzgor)` poleg glave stolpca označuje, da je bil "
"stolpec razvrščen v padajočem oziroma naraščajočem vrstnem redu. Če se pri "
"preletavanju nad drugimi glavami stolpcev pojavi ikona :icon:`fa-"
"sort` :guilabel:`(razvrsti)`, je stolpec mogoče razvrstiti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:138
msgid ""
"If conditional formatting has been applied to a table, the original "
"formatting is maintained when the table is resorted by a different column."
msgstr ""
"Če je bilo na tabelo uporabljeno pogojno oblikovanje, se prvotno oblikovanje "
"ohrani, ko je tabela ponovno razvrščena po drugem stolpcu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:142
msgid ""
"In this example, the table was originally sorted by revenue per CRM tag, in "
"decreasing order. Conditional formatting was defined to visualize the "
"proportional revenue using data bars. When the table is resorted by number "
"of leads in descending order, the data bars still reflect the revenue per "
"tag in decreasing order."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru je bila tabela prvotno razvrščena po prihodkih na oznako CRM v "
"padajočem vrstnem redu. Pogojno oblikovanje je bilo definirano za "
"vizualizacijo sorazmernih prihodkov z uporabo podatkovnih trakov. Ko je "
"tabela ponovno razvrščena po številu potencialnih strank v padajočem vrstnem "
"redu, podatkovni trakovi še vedno odražajo prihodke na oznako v padajočem "
"vrstnem redu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Sorting a table with conditional formatting using data bars"
msgstr ""
"Razvrščanje tabele s pogojnim oblikovanjem z uporabo podatkovnih trakov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:154
msgid "Access underlying records"
msgstr "Dostop do osnovnih zapisov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:156
msgid ""
"While dashboards provide a user-friendly summary of key data, drilling down "
"to the underlying data allows a more detailed analysis. This can be useful "
"for investigating anomalies or providing the full context needed for "
"decision-making."
msgstr ""
"Medtem ko nadzorne plošče zagotavljajo uporabniku prijazen povzetek ključnih "
"podatkov, raziskovanje osnovnih podatkov omogoča podrobnejšo analizo. To je "
"lahko uporabno za preiskovanje anomalij ali zagotavljanje celotnega "
"konteksta, potrebnega za odločanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:160
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database records**: To access database records referenced "
"by a dashboard, click on the relevant value in a table or on a data point on "
"a chart. Doing so opens either the individual record, or, in the case of "
"charts or tables displaying consolidated data, a list of the referenced "
"records."
msgstr ""
"**Odpiranje osnovnih podatkovnih zapisov**: Za dostop do podatkovnih "
"zapisov, na katere se sklicuje nadzorna plošča, kliknite ustrezno vrednost v "
"tabeli ali na točko podatkov na grafikonu. S tem odprete bodisi posamezen "
"zapis bodisi, v primeru grafikonov ali tabel, ki prikazujejo konsolidirane "
"podatke, seznam referenčnih zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:165
msgid ""
"**Open underlying database views**: To access the view from which the data "
"for a specific chart or table is retrieved, click on the title of the chart "
"or table. Doing so opens the corresponding list view, pivot view or graph "
"view."
msgstr ""
"**Odpiranje osnovnih podatkovnih pogledov**: Za dostop do pogleda, iz "
"katerega se pridobivajo podatki za določen grafikon ali tabelo, kliknite "
"naslov grafikona ali tabele. S tem odprete ustrezen seznamski pogled, "
"vrtilni pogled ali grafični pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:170
msgid ""
"To return to a dashboard after drilling down to underlying records or views, "
"click the :guilabel:`Dashboards` breadcrumb in the upper-left corner."
msgstr ""
"Če se želite vrniti na nadzorno plošč o po raziskovanju osnovnih zapisov ali "
"pogledov, kliknite drobtino :guilabel:`Nadzorne plošče` v zgornjem levem "
"kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:176
msgid "Expand, copy or download charts"
msgstr "Razširitev, kopiranje ali prenos grafikonov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:178
msgid ""
"To see charts in full screen, hover over a chart and click the :icon:`fa-"
"expand` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti grafikone v celozaslonskem načinu, se premaknite nad "
"grafikon in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-expand`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:180
msgid ""
"It is also possible to copy or download a chart by hovering over the chart "
"and clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (vertical ellipsis) icon, then "
"clicking :icon:`os-copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Copy as image` or :icon:`fa-"
"download` :guilabel:`Download` as relevant."
msgstr ""
"Grafikon je mogoče tudi kopirati ali prenesti tako, da se premaknete nad "
"grafikon in kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` (navpične tri pike), nato "
"pa kliknete :icon:`os-copy-as-image` :guilabel:`Kopiraj kot sliko` "
"ali :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`Prenesi`, kot je ustrezno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:185
msgid ""
":ref:`Expanding a time-series chart to full screen <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` allows a more detailed analysis."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Razširitev grafikona časovne vrste na celozaslonski način <dashboards/"
"use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` omogoča podrobnejšo analizo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:191
msgid "Analyze time-series charts"
msgstr "Analiza grafikonov časovnih vrst"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:193
msgid ""
"Time-series charts, i.e., charts showing data over time, can be analyzed "
"more closely by:"
msgstr ""
"Grafikone časovnih vrst, tj. grafikone, ki prikazujejo podatke skozi čas, je "
"mogoče podrobneje analizirati z:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:195
msgid ""
":ref:`adjusting the granularity <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-"
"charts-granularity>`;"
msgstr ""
":ref:`prilagajanjem stopnje podrobnosti <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-"
"series-charts-granularity>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:196
msgid ""
":ref:`zooming in <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` "
"on a chosen time span."
msgstr ""
":ref:`povečavo <dashboards/use-dashboards/time-series-charts-zoom-scroll>` "
"izbranega časovnega obdobja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:202
msgid "Adjust granularity"
msgstr "Prilagoditev stopnje podrobnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:204
msgid ""
"For many time-series charts it is possible to adjust the granularity of the "
"unit of time on the x-axis."
msgstr ""
"Pri mnogih grafikonih časovnih vrst je mogoče prilagoditi stopnjo "
"podrobnosti časovne enote na osi x."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:207
msgid ""
"To do so, hover over the chart, click the :icon:`fa-caret-"
"down` :guilabel:`(dropdown)` icon, then select the desired granularity."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da se premaknete nad grafikon, kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-"
"caret-down` :guilabel:`(spustni meni)`, nato pa izberete želeno stopnjo "
"podrobnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:None
msgid "Changing time granularity on a chart's y-axis"
msgstr "Spreminjanje časovne stopnje podrobnosti na osi y grafikona"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:217
msgid "Zoom in on a time span and scroll"
msgstr "Povečava časovnega obdobja in pomikanje"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:219
msgid ""
"When a time-series chart is :ref:`expanded to full screen <dashboards/use-"
"dashboards/charts>`, a slider below the chart allows you to:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je grafikon časovne vrste :ref:`razširjen na celozaslonski način "
"<dashboards/use-dashboards/charts>`, vam drsnik pod grafikonom omogoča:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:222
msgid ""
"zoom in on a specific time span by dragging the ends of the slider to select "
"the desired time span;"
msgstr ""
"povečajte določeno časovno obdobje z vlečenjem koncev drsnika za izbiro "
"želenega časovnega obdobja;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:224
msgid ""
"when you have zoomed in, to scroll through the chart while maintaining the "
"level of zoom by dragging the slider to the left or right."
msgstr ""
"ko ste povečali, se pomikajte po grafu ob ohranjanju stopnje povečave z "
"vlečenjem drsnika na levo ali desno."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:227
msgid "Resize the slider to return to the initial view."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost drsnika za vrnitev na začetni pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:230
msgid ""
"In this example from the :guilabel:`Warehouse Daily Operations` dashboard, "
"the chart shows transfers yet to be assigned to a responsible user, by day. "
"The zoom of the chart has been adjusted to show data for five days, and the "
"current position of the slider allows data from the last five days to be "
"shown."
msgstr ""
"V tem primeru iz nadzorne plošče :guilabel:`Warehouse Daily Operations` graf "
"prikazuje prenose, ki še niso dodeljeni odgovornemu uporabniku, po dnevih. "
"Povečava grafa je bila prilagojena tako, da prikazuje podatke za pet dni, "
"trenutni položaj drsnika pa omogoča prikaz podatkov zadnjih petih dni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Zoomed-in chart with slider"
msgstr "Povečan graf z drsnikom"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:241
msgid "Standard dashboards"
msgstr "Standardne nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:243
msgid ""
"Depending on which apps are installed, a series of standard dashboards is "
"available by default."
msgstr ""
"Odvisno od tega, katere aplikacije so nameščene, je privzeto na voljo vrsta "
"standardnih nadzornih plošč."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:245
msgid ""
"These pre-configured dashboards have been designed to provide the most "
"relevant insights for the topic in question, and users with the "
"appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` "
"can :ref:`consult and interact <dashboards/use-dashboards>` with them. "
"Dashboard-specific :ref:`filters <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-"
"filters>`, available via the search bar, allow the entire dashboard to be "
"filtered for selected values."
msgstr ""
"Te vnaprej konfigurirane nadzorne plošče so bile zasnovane za zagotavljanje "
"najbolj relevantnih vpogledov za obravnavano temo, uporabniki z "
"ustreznimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa <dashboards/access-and-sharing>` pa "
"lahko :ref:`pregledujejo in komunicirajo <dashboards/use-dashboards>` z "
"njimi. :ref:`Filtri <dashboards/use-dashboards/global-filters>` za posamezno "
"nadzorno ploščo, dostopni preko iskalne vrstice, omogočajo filtriranje "
"celotne nadzorne plošče za izbrane vrednosti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:251
msgid ""
"Standard dashboards can be :ref:`customized <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` by a user with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/"
"access-and-sharing/customize-configure-build>`. For example, dashboard "
"elements like tables and charts, or global filters can be added, edited, or "
"removed."
msgstr ""
"Standardne nadzorne plošče lahko :ref:`prilagodi "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` uporabnik z "
"ustreznimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa <dashboards/access-and-sharing/customize-"
"configure-build>`. Na primer, elementi nadzorne plošče, kot so tabele in "
"grafikoni, ali globalni filtri so lahko dodani, urejeni ali odstranjeni."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:257
msgid ""
"When customizing a standard dashboard, it is highly recommended "
"to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` and make any changes on the duplicated version. "
"Standard dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo version upgrade, meaning "
"any customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Pri prilagajanju standardne nadzorne plošče je zelo "
"priporočljivo :ref:`podvojiti nadzorno ploščo "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` in narediti "
"vse spremembe na podvojeni različici. Standardne nadzorne plošče se ponovno "
"namestijo pri vsaki nadgradnji različice Odoo, kar pomeni, da so vse "
"prilagoditve izvirne različice izgubljene."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:265
msgid "Configuration settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve konfiguracije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:268
msgid ""
"Only a user with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <access-rights/groups>` "
"can configure or modify settings for dashboards and dashboard sections."
msgstr ""
"Samo uporabnik z ustreznimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa <access-rights/groups>` "
"lahko konfigurira ali spreminja nastavitve za nadzorne plošče in razdelke "
"nadzornih plošč."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:271
msgid ""
"To manage dashboards and dashboard sections, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`. The following actions are "
"possible at the level of dashboard sections:"
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje nadzornih plošč in razdelkov nadzornih plošč pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Konfiguracija --> Nadzorne plošče`. Naslednja dejanja so "
"mogoča na ravni razdelkov nadzorne plošče:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:274
msgid ""
"**Change the order of dashboard sections** by using the :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(drag handle)` icon to move a section to a new "
"position."
msgstr ""
"**Spremenite vrstni red razdelkov nadzorne plošče** z uporabo "
"ikone :icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(ročica za vlečenje)` za premik "
"razdelka na nov položaj."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:277
msgid ""
"**Duplicate a dashboard section** by selecting the relevant section name, "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button, and then :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`Duplicate`. The dashboards within the section are not "
"duplicated."
msgstr ""
"**Podvojite razdelek nadzorne plošče** tako, da izberete ustrezno ime "
"razdelka, kliknete gumb :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in nato :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`Podvoji`. Nadzorne plošče znotraj razdelka niso podvojene."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:281
msgid ""
"**Delete a dashboard section** by selecting the relevant section name, "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Actions` button then :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`Delete`."
msgstr ""
"**Izbrišite razdelek nadzorne plošče** tako, da izberete ustrezno ime "
"razdelka, kliknete gumb :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`Dejanja` in nato :icon:`fa-"
"trash-o` :guilabel:`Izbriši`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:285
msgid ""
"Standard, pre-installed dashboard sections cannot be deleted; custom "
"dashboard sections, on the other hand, can be deleted."
msgstr ""
"Standardnih, vnaprej nameščenih razdelkov nadzorne plošče ni mogoče "
"izbrisati; razdelke nadzorne plošče po meri pa je mogoče izbrisati."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:288
msgid ""
"**Create a new dashboard section** by clicking :guilabel:`New`, then "
"entering the section name. When creating a new section, it is possible to "
"add a dashboard to the new section directly by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"**Ustvarite nov razdelek nadzorne plošče** s klikom na :guilabel:`Novo` in "
"nato vnesite ime razdelka. Pri ustvarjanju novega razdelka je mogoče dodati "
"nadzorno ploščo v nov razdelek neposredno s klikom na :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"preglednico`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:292
msgid ""
"Clicking on an individual dashboard section lists all dashboards within that "
"section. The following actions are possible:"
msgstr ""
"Klik na posamezen razdelek nadzorne plošče prikaže vse nadzorne plošče v tem "
"razdelku. Na voljo so naslednja dejanja:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:295
msgid ""
"**Change the order of a dashboard within its section** by using "
"the :icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(drag handle)` icon to move the "
"dashboard to a new position."
msgstr ""
"**Spremenite vrstni red nadzorne plošče v njenem razdelku** tako, da "
"uporabite ikono :icon:`oi-draggable` :guilabel:`(ročica za vlečenje)`, da "
"premaknete nadzorno ploščo na nov položaj."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:298
msgid ""
"**Edit the name of a dashboard section or dashboard** by clicking the name "
"and modifying it."
msgstr ""
"**Uredite ime razdelka nadzorne plošče ali nadzorne plošče** tako, da "
"kliknete ime in ga spremenite."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:300
msgid ""
"**Add or remove user groups** to :ref:`control access to the dashboard "
"<dashboards/access-and-sharing>`."
msgstr ""
"**Dodajte ali odstranite skupine uporabnikov** za :ref:`nadzor dostopa do "
"nadzorne plošče <dashboards/access-and-sharing>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:303
msgid ""
"**Select one or more companies** if, in a :doc:`multi-company <../../"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>` database, the dashboard "
"should only be visible to users of a specific company or companies. If this "
"field is left blank, the dashboard is visible to all users with the "
"appropriate access rights, regardless of which company is currently selected "
"in the database."
msgstr ""
"**Izberite eno ali več podjetij**, če naj bo v :doc:`večpodjetniški <../../"
"applications/general/companies/multi_company>` bazi podatkov nadzorna plošča "
"vidna samo uporabnikom določenega podjetja ali podjetij. Če to polje ostane "
"prazno, je nadzorna plošča vidna vsem uporabnikom z ustreznimi pravicami "
"dostopa, ne glede na to, katero podjetje je trenutno izbrano v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:309
msgid ""
"**Unpublish a dashboard** by disabling the :guilabel:`Is Published` toggle."
msgstr ""
"**Umakni nadzorno ploščo iz objave** tako, da onemogočite "
"preklop :guilabel:`Je objavljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:311
msgid ""
"**Edit the underlying spreadsheet** of a dashboard by clicking :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`Edit` on the line of the relevant dashboard."
msgstr ""
"**Uredite osnovno preglednico** nadzorne plošče tako, da kliknete :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`Uredi` v vrstici ustrezne nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:315
msgid ""
"When customizing a standard dashboard, it is highly recommended "
"to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/"
"duplicate-dashboard>` and make any changes on the underlying spreadsheet of "
"the duplicated version. Standard dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo "
"version upgrade, meaning any customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Pri prilagajanju standardne nadzorne plošče je zelo "
"priporočljivo :ref:`podvojiti nadzorno ploščo "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` in narediti "
"vse spremembe na osnovni preglednici podvojene različice. Standardne "
"nadzorne plošče so ponovno nameščene ob vsaki nadgradnji različice Odoo, kar "
"pomeni, da so vse prilagoditve na izvirni različici izgubljene."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:320
msgid ""
"**Delete a dashboard** by clicking the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` "
"icon."
msgstr ""
"**Izbrišite nadzorno ploščo** tako, da kliknete ikono :icon:`fa-"
"trash` :guilabel:`(koš)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:323
msgid ""
"A standard dashboard that is deleted is reinstalled at the next Odoo version "
"upgrade."
msgstr ""
"Standardna nadzorna plošča, ki je izbrisana, je ponovno nameščena ob "
"naslednji nadgradnji različice Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:325
msgid ""
"**Add a new dashboard to the section** by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"spreadsheet`. Two options exist:"
msgstr ""
"**Dodajte novo nadzorno ploščo v razdelek** tako, da "
"kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj preglednico`. Obstajata dve možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:328
msgid ""
"To convert an existing spreadsheet into a dashboard and add it to the new "
"section, select the relevant spreadsheet, then click :guilabel:`Confirm`. "
"Back in the section overview, update the :guilabel:`Group` "
"and :guilabel:`Company` fields if needed."
msgstr ""
"Če želite obstoječo preglednico pretvoriti v nadzorno ploščo in jo dodati v "
"nov razdelek, izberite ustrezno preglednico in nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`. Nazaj v pregledu razdelka po potrebi posodobite "
"polji :guilabel:`Skupina` in :guilabel:`Podjetje`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:332
msgid ""
"To start creating a dashboard from scratch, select :guilabel:`Blank "
"spreadsheet`. To return to the section overview, click the name of the "
"section in the top-left corner, above the menu bar. Update "
"the :guilabel:`Group` and :guilabel:`Company` fields if needed."
msgstr ""
"Za začetek ustvarjanja nadzorne plošče od začetka izberite :guilabel:`Blank "
"spreadsheet`. Za vrnitev na pregled razdelka kliknite ime razdelka v "
"zgornjem levem kotu nad menijsko vrstico. Po potrebi posodobite "
"polji :guilabel:`Group` in :guilabel:`Company`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:337
msgid ""
"After a spreadsheet has been converted into a dashboard, it can only "
"be :ref:`accessed and edited via the Dashboards app "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je preglednica pretvorjena v nadzorno ploščo, je :ref:`dostopna in jo je "
"mogoče urejati samo prek aplikacije Nadzorne plošče "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:341
msgid ""
"A newly created dashboard is by default accessible to users belonging to the "
"default internal :ref:`user group <access-rights/groups>`. Edit this if "
"needed via the :guilabel:`Configuration` settings of the relevant dashboard "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Novo ustvarjena nadzorna plošča je privzeto dostopna uporabnikom, ki "
"pripadajo privzeti notranji :ref:`skupini uporabnikov <access-rights/"
"groups>`. Po potrebi to uredite prek nastavitev :guilabel:`Configuration` "
"ustreznega razdelka nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:344
msgid ""
"It is also possible to :ref:`convert a spreadsheet into a dashboard "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>` and add it to a dashboard "
"section starting from the spreadsheet in the Documents app."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako je mogoče :ref:`pretvoriti preglednico v nadzorno ploščo "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>` in jo dodati razdelku "
"nadzorne plošče, začenši s preglednico v aplikaciji Documents."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:351
msgid "Access rights and sharing"
msgstr "Pravice dostopa in skupna raba"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:356
msgid "Using dashboards"
msgstr "Uporaba nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:358
msgid ""
"The *right to view and interact with a dashboard* is based on :ref:`user "
"groups <access-rights/groups>`, and is managed in the :ref:`Configuration "
"settings <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>` of the "
"Dashboards app. Only users who are part of a group that has been granted "
"access to a specific dashboard see that dashboard in the left-hand panel "
"when the Dashboards app is opened. Users with `Dashboard / Admin` access "
"rights can view all dashboards."
msgstr ""
"*Pravica do ogledu nadzorne plošče in interakcije z njo* temelji "
"na :ref:`skupinah uporabnikov <access-rights/groups>` in se upravlja "
"v :ref:`nastavitvah konfiguracije <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-"
"access>` aplikacije Dashboards. Samo uporabniki, ki so del skupine, ki ji je "
"bil dodeljen dostop do določene nadzorne plošče, vidijo to nadzorno ploščo v "
"levem panelu, ko je aplikacija Dashboards odprta. Uporabniki s pravicami "
"dostopa `Dashboard / Admin` lahko vidijo vse nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:365
msgid ""
"However, the *visibility of dynamic Odoo data within a dashboard* is handled "
"separately. This is based on a user's :ref:`access rights <access-rights/"
"user-permissions>` to the model from which the data has been retrieved, and "
"takes into account any record rules that may restrict access."
msgstr ""
"Vendar pa se *vidnost dinamičnih podatkov Odoo v nadzorni plošči* obravnava "
"ločeno. To temelji na uporabnikovih :ref:`pravicah dostopa <access-rights/"
"user-permissions>` do modela, iz katerega so bili podatki pridobljeni, in "
"upošteva vsa pravila zapisov, ki lahko omejujejo dostop."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:370
msgid ""
"User permissions are taken into account when a user opens a dashboard, with "
"the dashboard only being populated with data the user is authorized to see. "
"This means that a user could in theory be able to view a dashboard but, due "
"to a lack of appropriate permissions, not be able to see the Odoo data the "
"dashboard's creator intended to be displayed."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniške pravice se upoštevajo, ko uporabnik odpre nadzorno ploščo, pri "
"čemer se nadzorna plošča napolni samo s podatki, ki jih ima uporabnik "
"dovoljenje videti. To pomeni, da bi uporabnik teoretično lahko gledal "
"nadzorno ploščo, vendar zaradi pomanjkanja ustreznih dovoljenj ne bi mogel "
"videti podatkov Odoo, ki jih je avtor nadzorne plošče želel prikazati."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:375
msgid ""
"Therefore, it is crucial to take user permissions into consideration when "
"granting dashboard access to groups."
msgstr ""
"Zato je ključnega pomena, da se pri dodeljevanju dostopa do nadzorne plošče "
"skupinam upoštevajo uporabniške pravice."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:379
msgid ""
"Granting the user group `Sales / User: Own Documents Only` access to "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` dashboard would serve little purpose. While users "
"belonging to that group would be able to view and interact with the "
"dashboard, they would only see data related to their own sales, rendering "
"the overall dashboard misleading."
msgstr ""
"Dodelitev dostopa do nadzorne plošče :guilabel:`Prodaja` skupini uporabnikov "
"`Prodaja / Uporabnik: Samo lastni dokumenti` bi imelo malo smisla. Čeprav bi "
"uporabniki, ki pripadajo tej skupini, lahko gledali in sodelovali z nadzorno "
"ploščo, bi videli samo podatke, povezane z lastno prodajo, kar bi celotno "
"nadzorno ploščo naredilo zavajajoče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:387
msgid "Manage access rights to view dashboards"
msgstr "Upravljanje pravic dostopa za ogled nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:389
msgid "To manage users' rights to view and interact with a dashboard:"
msgstr ""
"Za upravljanje pravic uporabnikov za ogled in interakcijo z nadzorno ploščo:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:391
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:121
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:163
msgid ""
"In the Dashboards app, go to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Dashboards`."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Nadzorne plošče pojdite na :menuselection:`Konfiguracija --> "
"Nadzorne plošče`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:392
msgid "From the list of dashboard sections, open the relevant section."
msgstr "Na seznamu razdelkov nadzorne plošče odprite ustrezen razdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:393
msgid "On the line of the relevant dashboard, in the :guilabel:`Group` column:"
msgstr ""
"V vrstici ustrezne nadzorne plošče v stolpcu :guilabel:`Naziv skupine`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:395
msgid ""
"add a user group by clicking the field until a dropdown with user groups "
"appears, then selecting the appropriate user group. In the dropdown, "
"click :guilabel:`Search More` to access the full list of user groups;"
msgstr ""
"dodajte uporabniško skupino tako, da kliknete polje, dokler se ne prikaže "
"spustni meni z uporabniškimi skupinami, nato pa izberete ustrezno "
"uporabniško skupino. V spustnem meniju kliknite :guilabel:`Išči več`, da "
"dostopate do celotnega seznama uporabniških skupin;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:398
msgid ""
"remove a user group by clicking the relevant group name, then "
"clicking :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(Delete)`."
msgstr ""
"odstranite uporabniško skupino tako, da kliknete ustrezen naziv skupine, "
"nato pa kliknete :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(Izbriši)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:404
msgid "Building, customizing and configuring dashboards"
msgstr "Gradnja, prilagajanje in konfiguracija nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:406
msgid ""
"Only users with `Dashboards / Admin` access rights can :ref:`customize "
"dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` or :ref:`configure "
"dashboard settings <dashboards/configuration>`. To :ref:`build a dashboard "
"from scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`, a user must have both "
"`Dashboards / Admin` and, at minimum for the Documents app, `Documents / "
"User` access rights."
msgstr ""
"Samo uporabniki z dostopno pravico `Dashboards / Admin` "
"lahko :ref:`prilagajajo nadzorne plošče <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"customize>` ali :ref:`konfigurirajo nastavitve nadzorne plošče <dashboards/"
"configuration>`. Za :ref:`gradnjo nadzorne plošče od začetka "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` mora imeti uporabnik tako dostopno "
"pravico `Dashboards / Admin` kot tudi vsaj `Documents / User` za aplikacijo "
"Documents."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:415
msgid "Sharing a dashboard snapshot"
msgstr "Skupna raba posnetka nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards.rst:417
msgid ""
"To share a frozen version of a dashboard with an internal user who does not "
"have the appropriate access or with an external party, click :icon:`fa-share-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Share` at the top-right of the page then click the :icon:`fa-"
"clone` :guilabel:`(copy)` icon to copy a shareable link to your clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Če želite z notranjim uporabnikom, ki nima ustreznega dostopa, ali z zunanjo "
"osebo deliti zamrznjeno različico nadzorne plošče, kliknite :icon:`fa-share-"
"alt` :guilabel:`Deli` v zgornjem desnem kotu strani, nato pa kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`(kopiraj)`, da kopirate povezavo za "
"deljenje v odložišče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:3
msgid "Build and customize dashboards"
msgstr "Gradnja in prilagajanje nadzornih plošč"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:5
msgid ""
"In addition to consulting :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/standard>`, "
"users with the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-and-"
"sharing/customize-configure-build>` can :ref:`build custom dashboards from "
"scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` or :ref:`customize existing "
"dashboards <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` to respond to "
"specific business needs."
msgstr ""
"Poleg pregledovanja :ref:`standardnih nadzornih plošč <dashboards/standard>` "
"lahko uporabniki z ustreznimi :ref:`pravicami dostopa <dashboards/access-and-"
"sharing/customize-configure-build>` :ref:`zgradijo nadzorne plošče po meri "
"od začetka <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>` ali :ref:`prilagodijo "
"obstoječe nadzorne plošče <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize>` za "
"odziv na specifične poslovne potrebe."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:14
msgid "Build a dashboard"
msgstr "Gradnja nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:16
msgid ""
"In its most simple terms, building a dashboard involves :doc:`inserting Odoo "
"data into a spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/insert>` then :ref:`converting that "
"spreadsheet into a dashboard <spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>`."
msgstr ""
"V najbolj preprostem smislu gradnja nadzorne plošče "
"vključuje :doc:`vstavljanje podatkov Odoo v preglednico <../spreadsheet/"
"insert>`, nato pa :ref:`pretvarjanje te preglednice v nadzorno ploščo "
"<spreadsheet/get-started/convert-to-dashboard>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:20
msgid ""
"However, to build a dashboard that delivers relevant and valuable insights, "
"it is important to consider the process in terms of three key "
"stages: :ref:`preparation <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"preparation>`, :ref:`data insertion and manipulation "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build-insertion-manipulation>`, "
"and :ref:`data visualization <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"visualization>`."
msgstr ""
"Vendar pa je za gradnjo nadzorne plošče, ki zagotavlja ustrezne in dragocene "
"vpoglede, pomembno upoštevati proces v smislu treh ključnih "
"stopenj: :ref:`priprava <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"preparation>`, :ref:`vstavljanje in obdelava podatkov "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/build-insertion-manipulation>` "
"ter :ref:`vizualizacija podatkov <build_and_customize_dashboards/build-"
"visualization>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:29
msgid "Preparation"
msgstr "Priprava"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:48
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:64
msgid "This stage involves:"
msgstr "Ta stopnja vključuje:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:33
msgid ""
"defining the purpose of the dashboard, in other words, the business "
"questions it needs to answer, and deciding what data would answer those "
"questions;"
msgstr ""
"opredelitev namena nadzorne plošče, tj. poslovnih vprašanj, na katera mora "
"odgovoriti, in odločitev, kateri podatki bi odgovorili na ta vprašanja;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:35
msgid ""
"determining where to find the relevant Odoo data and deciding "
"which :doc:`type of view <../../studio/views>` (i.e., list, pivot table, or "
"chart) is most suited for the data analysis needed;"
msgstr ""
"določitev, kje najti ustrezne podatke Odoo in odločitev, katera :doc:`vrsta "
"pogleda <../../studio/views>` (tj. seznam, vrtilna tabela ali graf) je "
"najprimernejša za potrebno analizo podatkov;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:38
msgid ""
"preparing the Odoo data by refining the views to focus on the most relevant "
"information, e.g., by using :doc:`search filters <../../essentials/search>`, "
"by making only certain list fields visible, or by deciding which dimensions "
"and measures a pivot table should use;"
msgstr ""
"priprava podatkov Odoo z izboljšanjem pogledov za osredotočenje na najbolj "
"relevantne informacije, npr. z uporabo :doc:`iskalnih filtrov <../../"
"essentials/search>`, z vidnostjo samo določenih polj seznama ali z "
"odločitvijo, katere dimenzije in mere naj uporablja vrtilna tabela;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:41
msgid "sourcing any other information needed to support the dashboard."
msgstr "pridobitev drugih informacij, potrebnih za podporo nadzorni plošči."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:46
msgid "Data insertion and manipulation"
msgstr "Vstavljanje in obdelava podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:50
msgid ""
"inserting the prepared :doc:`lists <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_list>`, :doc:`pivot tables <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_pivot_table>` or :doc:`charts <../spreadsheet/insert/insert_chart>` "
"into the spreadsheet you will use to build your dashboard;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:53
msgid ""
"manipulating the data, if needed, to be able to draw the necessary insights. "
"This may involve performing calculations or creating custom metrics "
"using :doc:`standard or Odoo-specific functions and formulas <../spreadsheet/"
"work_with_data/functions>`, referencing data from various sources within the "
"spreadsheet, or :ref:`converting static pivot tables to dynamic pivot tables "
"<spreadsheet/insert-pivot-table/static-convert>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:62
msgid "Data visualization"
msgstr "Vizualizacija podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:66
msgid ""
"presenting the data on at least the first sheet of your spreadsheet (i.e., "
"the sheet that will serve as the front end of your dashboard) in a clear, "
"visual, and meaningful way so it is easy to interpret. Concretely, this "
"means deciding on the layout and order of elements such as tables and "
"charts, as well as using tools and techniques to guide the user, such as "
"clear and descriptive headings, text formatting and colors, carefully chosen "
"chart types, and conditional formatting to highlight specific data visually;"
msgstr ""
"predstavitev podatkov vsaj na prvem listu vaše preglednice (tj. listu, ki bo "
"služil kot vmesnik vaše nadzorne plošče) na jasen, vizualen in smiseln "
"način, tako da jih je enostavno interpretirati. Konkretno to pomeni "
"odločanje o razporeditvi in vrstnem redu elementov, kot so tabele in "
"grafikoni, ter uporabo orodij in tehnik za vodenje uporabnika, kot so jasni "
"in opisni naslovi, oblikovanje besedila in barve, skrbno izbrane vrste "
"grafikonov ter pogojno oblikovanje za vizualno poudarjanje določenih "
"podatkov;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:72
msgid ""
":doc:`inserting clickable links <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_clickable_links>`, if relevant, to provide access to Odoo menu items, "
"URLs, or other sheets within the same spreadsheet if these should also be "
"accessible from the front end of your dashboard;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:75
msgid ""
":doc:`creating global filters <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` to allow users to tailor the view to their needs;"
msgstr ""
":doc:`ustvarjanje globalnih filtrov <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>`, ki uporabnikom omogočajo prilagoditev pogleda njihovim "
"potrebam;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:77
msgid ""
":ref:`converting the spreadsheet into a dashboard <spreadsheet/get-started/"
"convert-to-dashboard>`, determining whether to add the dashboard to an "
"existing or new dashboard section, and :ref:`managing access rights to the "
"dashboard <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>`."
msgstr ""
":ref:`pretvorba preglednice v nadzorno plošco <spreadsheet/get-started/"
"convert-to-dashboard>`, določitev, ali dodati nadzorno ploščo v obstoječi "
"ali nov razdelek nadzorne plošče, ter :ref:`upravljanje pravic dostopa do "
"nadzorne plošče <dashboards/access-and-sharing/manage-view-access>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:83
msgid ""
"Use standard dashboards as inspiration for how to best present and visualize "
"data. For example, for charts, :ref:`open the underlying spreadsheet "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>` of a standard "
"dashboard, hover over a chart and click the :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(menu)` icon, then :icon:`fa-pencil-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Edit` to see the chart properties on the right side of the "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite standardne nadzorne plošče kot navdih za najboljšo predstavitev in "
"vizualizacijo podatkov. Npr. za grafikone :ref:`odprite osnovno preglednico "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>` standardne "
"nadzorne plošče, premaknite kazalec nad grafikon in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"bars` :guilabel:`(meni)`, nato pa :icon:`fa-pencil-square-"
"o` :guilabel:`Uredi`, da si ogledate lastnosti grafikona na desni strani "
"zaslona."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:89
msgid ""
"The possibility to link to other sheets within the same spreadsheet allows "
"the creation of a multi-page dashboard, with users able to navigate between "
"pages thanks to clickable links. Global filters apply across all pages of a "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Možnost povezovanja na druge liste znotraj iste preglednice omogoča "
"ustvarjanje večstranske nadzorne plošče, pri čemer lahko uporabniki krmarijo "
"med stranmi zahvaljujoč povezavam, ki jih je mogoče klikniti. Globalni "
"filtri se uporabijo na vseh straneh nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:94
msgid ""
"`Odoo Tutorial: Dashboard from scratch <https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"dashboard-from-scratch-8957>`_"
msgstr ""
"` Odoo vadnica: Nadzorna plošča od začetka<https://www.odoo.com/slides/slide/"
"dashboard-from-scratch-8957>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:100
msgid "Customize a dashboard"
msgstr "Prilagoditev nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:102
msgid ""
"A dashboard can be customized by :ref:`opening its underlying spreadsheet "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>`, i.e., the Odoo "
"spreadsheet from which the dashboard has been created, and :ref:`making any "
"desired changes <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet>`."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorno ploščo je mogoče prilagoditi z :ref:`odpiranjem njene osnovne "
"preglednice <build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/open-spreadsheet>`, "
"tj. preglednice Odoo, iz katere je bila nadzorna plošča ustvarjena, "
"in :ref:`izvajanjem želenih sprememb <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-"
"spreadsheet>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:110
msgid "Open the underlying spreadsheet"
msgstr "Odpiranje podlage preglednice"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:113
msgid ""
"When customizing a :ref:`standard dashboard <dashboards/standard>`, it is "
"highly recommended to :ref:`duplicate the dashboard "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` and make any "
"changes on the underlying spreadsheet of the duplicated version. Standard "
"dashboards are reinstalled at each Odoo version upgrade, meaning any "
"customizations on the original version are lost."
msgstr ""
"Pri prilagajanju :ref:`standardne nadzorne plošče <dashboards/standard>` je "
"zelo priporočljivo :ref:`podvojiti nadzorno ploščo "
"<build_and_customize_dashboards/customize/duplicate-dashboard>` in izvesti "
"vse spremembe na osnovni preglednici podvojene različice. Standardne "
"nadzorne plošče se ponovno namestijo ob vsakem nadgradnji različice Odoo, "
"kar pomeni, da so vse prilagoditve izvirne različice izgubljene."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:119
msgid "To open a dashboard's underlying spreadsheet:"
msgstr "Za odprtje podlage preglednice nadzorne plošče:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:122
msgid ""
"Open the relevant dashboard section, then, on the line of the relevant "
"dashboard, click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite ustrezni razdelek nadzorne plošče, nato v vrstici ustrezne nadzorne "
"plošče kliknite :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:126
msgid ""
"To temporarily unpublish a dashboard while you make changes, "
"disable :guilabel:`Is Published` *before* editing the dashboard, making note "
"to republish it when the customization has been finalized."
msgstr ""
"Za začasno umikanje objave nadzorne plošče med izvajanjem sprememb "
"onemogočite :guilabel:`Je objavljeno` *pred* urejanjem nadzorne plošče in ne "
"pozabite jo ponovno objaviti, ko je prilagoditev dokončana."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:129
msgid ""
"Users who do not have the appropriate :ref:`access rights <dashboards/access-"
"and-sharing/customize-configure-build>` to customize a dashboard can still "
"access a read-only version of the dashboard's underlying spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki, ki nimajo ustreznih :ref:`pravic dostopa <dashboards/access-and-"
"sharing/customize-configure-build>` za prilagajanje nadzorne plošče, lahko "
"še vedno dostopajo do različice podlage preglednice nadzorne plošče samo za "
"branje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:132
msgid ""
"With :ref:`developer mode <developer-mode>` activated, click on "
"the :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)` icon beside the name of a dashboard "
"in the left panel to open its underlying spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Z aktiviranim :ref:`razvijalskim načinom <developer-mode>` kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Uredi)` poleg imena nadzorne plošče v "
"levem pultu, da odprete njeno podlago preglednice."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:136
msgid "The spreadsheet that opens typically consists of at least two sheets:"
msgstr "Preglednica, ki se odpre, običajno sestoji iz vsaj dveh listov:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:138
msgid ""
"**The first sheet** always serves as the front end of your dashboard, and "
"contains the tables and charts used to structure and visualize the data."
msgstr ""
"**Prvi list** vedno služi kot uporabniški vmesnik vaše nadzorne plošče in "
"vsebuje tabele ter grafikone, ki se uporabljajo za strukturiranje in "
"vizualizacijo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:141
msgid ""
"**The second and any subsequent sheets** typically contain data used for the "
"calculation of key metrics shown on the first sheet."
msgstr ""
"**Drugi in vsi nadaljnji listi** običajno vsebujejo podatke, ki se "
"uporabljajo za izračun ključnih metrik, prikazanih na prvem listu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:145
msgid ""
"The :ref:`data sources <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` that maintain the "
"connection between the spreadsheet and the relevant models in your database "
"can be viewed by clicking :menuselection:`Data` on the spreadsheet's menu "
"bar. These data sources are identified by their respective :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot table)`, :icon:`oi-view-list` :guilabel:`(list)` "
"or :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(chart)` icon, followed by their ID and "
"name, e.g., :icon:`oi-view-pivot` *(#1) Sales Analysis by Product*."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Viri podatkov <spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>`, ki ohranjajo "
"povezavo med preglednico in ustreznimi modeli v vaši zbirki podatkov, si "
"lahko ogledate s klikom na :menuselection:`Podatki` v menijski vrstici "
"preglednice. Ti viri podatkov so označeni z ustrezno ikono :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(vrtilna tabela)`, :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :guilabel:`(seznam)` ali :icon:`fa-bar-chart` :guilabel:`(grafikon)`, "
"ki ji sledi njihov ID in ime, npr. :icon:`oi-view-pivot` *(#1) Analiza "
"prodaje po izdelku*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:152
msgid ""
"For :ref:`standard dashboards <dashboards/standard>`, while the data sources "
"are still active and visible in the :menuselection:`Data` menu, the "
"corresponding lists and pivot tables have been removed from the spreadsheet "
"for better performance and a neater appearance."
msgstr ""
"Za :ref:`standardne nadzorne plošče <dashboards/standard>`, medtem ko so "
"podatkovni viri še vedno aktivni in vidni v meniju :menuselection:`Podatki`, "
"so bili ustrezni seznami in vrtilne tabele odstranjeni iz preglednice za "
"boljšo zmogljivost in bolj urejen videz."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:159
msgid "Duplicate a dashboard"
msgstr "Podvajanje nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:161
msgid "To duplicate a dashboard:"
msgstr "Za podvojitev nadzorne plošče:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:164
msgid ""
"Open the relevant dashboard section, then, on the line of the dashboard you "
"want to duplicate, click :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Odprite ustrezni razdelek nadzorne plošče, nato v vrstici nadzorne plošče, "
"ki jo želite podvojiti, kliknite :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`Uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:166
msgid ""
"In the spreadsheet that opens, click :menuselection:`File -->` :icon:`os-"
"copy-file` :menuselection:`Make a copy`."
msgstr ""
"V preglednici, ki se odpre, kliknite :menuselection:`Datoteka -->` :icon:`os-"
"copy-file` :menuselection:`Ustvari kopijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:168
msgid ""
"Rename the duplicated dashboard by clicking the name of the spreadsheet at "
"the top left of the screen and editing as needed."
msgstr ""
"Preimenujte podvojeno nadzorno ploščo tako, da kliknete ime preglednice "
"zgoraj levo na zaslonu in po potrebi uredite."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:172
msgid ""
"To return to the overview of the dashboard section, click the name of the "
"original dashboard at the top left of the page, then the name of the "
"dashboard section."
msgstr ""
"Za vrnitev na pregled razdelka nadzorne plošče kliknite ime izvirne nadzorne "
"plošče zgoraj levo na strani, nato ime razdelka nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:174
msgid ""
"After duplicating a dashboard, delete the original dashboard by clicking "
"the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(trash)` icon or rename it by clicking on "
"the name then editing it."
msgstr ""
"Po podvajanju nadzorne plošče izbrišite izvirno nadzorno ploščo s klikom na "
"ikono :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(koš)` ali jo preimenujte s klikom na ime "
"in nato urejanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:180
msgid "Add, edit, or remove dashboard elements"
msgstr "Dodajanje, urejanje ali odstranjevanje elementov nadzorne plošče"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:182
msgid "Dashboards can be customized in various ways, such as by:"
msgstr "Nadzorne plošče lahko prilagodite na različne načine, na primer z:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:184
msgid ""
"adding new tables and charts based on previously inserted or :ref:`newly "
"inserted Odoo data <dashboards/customize-dashboard/edit-spreadsheet-new-odoo-"
"data>`. This requires a similar approach to :ref:`building a dashboard from "
"scratch <build_and_customize_dashboards/build>`;"
msgstr ""
"dodajanjem novih tabel in grafov na podlagi predhodno vstavljenih "
"ali :ref:`novo vstavljenih podatkov Odoo <dashboards/customize-dashboard/"
"edit-spreadsheet-new-odoo-data>`. To zahteva podoben pristop "
"kot :ref:`gradnja nadzorne plošče od začetka <build_and_customize_dashboards/"
"build>`;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:187
msgid ""
":doc:`adding new global filters <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` or editing or deleting existing ones;"
msgstr ""
":doc:`dodajanje novih globalnih filtrov <../spreadsheet/work_with_data/"
"global_filters>` ali urejanje ali brisanje obstoječih;"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:189
msgid ""
":doc:`adding or editing clickable links <../spreadsheet/insert/"
"insert_clickable_links>` to Odoo menus, URLs, or to other sheets within the "
"same spreadsheet."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:193
msgid ""
"The first tab of the spreadsheet serves as the front end of the dashboard. "
"Any tables or charts that should be visible on the final dashboard need to "
"be added to this sheet."
msgstr ""
"Prvi zavihek preglednice služi kot čelni del nadzorne plošče. Vse tabele ali "
"grafikone, ki naj bodo vidni na končni nadzorni plošči, je treba dodati na "
"ta list."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:195
msgid ""
"Dashboard elements that are no longer needed can be deleted from the "
"spreadsheet. If, after deleting a dashboard element, a :ref:`data source "
"<spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` is no longer being used in the "
"spreadsheet, this is indicated by a :icon:`fa-exclamation-"
"triangle` :guilabel:`(warning)` icon in the :guilabel:`Data` menu."
msgstr ""
"Elementi nadzorne plošče, ki jih ne potrebujete več, se lahko izbrišejo iz "
"preglednice. Če po izbrisu elementa nadzorne plošče :ref:`vir podatkov "
"<spreadsheet/insert/data-sources>` več ni uporabljen v preglednici, je to "
"označeno z ikono :icon:`fa-exclamation-triangle` :guilabel:`(opozorilo)` v "
"meniju :guilabel:`Podatki`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:0
msgid "Warning to indicate data source no longer used in spreadsheet"
msgstr ""
"Opozorilo, ki označuje vir podatkov, ki se več ne uporablja v preglednici"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:206
msgid "Insert new Odoo data"
msgstr "Vstavite nove podatke Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:208
msgid ""
"New Odoo data, such as lists, pivot tables, or charts, can be inserted into "
"a dashboard, starting from the relevant list view, pivot view, or graph "
"view. Concretely, a list or pivot table is inserted into a new sheet in the "
"dashboard's underlying spreadsheet; a chart is inserted on the first sheet "
"of the spreadsheet."
msgstr ""
"Nove podatke Odoo, kot so seznami, vrtilne tabele ali grafikoni, je mogoče "
"vstaviti v nadzorno ploščo, začenši z ustreznim pogledom seznama, pogledom "
"vrtilne tabele ali grafičnim pogledom. Konkretno, seznam ali vrtilna tabela "
"se vstavi v nov list v osnovni preglednici nadzorne plošče; grafikon se "
"vstavi na prvi list preglednice."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:213
msgid "To insert new data:"
msgstr "Za vstavljanje novih podatkov:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:215
msgid ""
"With the relevant list view, pivot view or graph view open in your database, "
"proceed as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je v vaši zbirki podatkov odprt ustrezen pogled seznama, pogled "
"razpredelnice ali pogled grafa, nadaljujte na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:217
msgid ""
"For a list view, click the :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon beside "
"the name of the view, then :guilabel:`Spreadsheet -->` :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :menuselection:`Insert list in spreadsheet`."
msgstr ""
"Za pogled seznama kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-cog` :guilabel:`(Dejanja)` poleg "
"imena pogleda, nato :guilabel:`Preglednica -->` :icon:`oi-view-"
"list` :menuselection:`Vstavi seznam v preglednico`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:220
msgid ""
"For a pivot or graph view, click :guilabel:`Insert in Spreadsheet` at the "
"top left of the view."
msgstr ""
"Za pogled razpredelnice ali grafa kliknite :guilabel:`Vstavi v preglednico` "
"v zgornjem levem delu pogleda."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:222
msgid ""
"In the window that opens, edit the name if needed. For a list, edit the "
"number of records, i.e., rows to be inserted, if needed."
msgstr ""
"V oknu, ki se odpre, po potrebi uredite ime. Za seznam po potrebi uredite "
"število zapisov, tj. vrstic, ki jih želite vstaviti."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:224
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Dashboards` tab then select in which dashboard the "
"list, pivot table, or chart should be inserted."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Nadzorne plošče` in nato izberite, v katero "
"nadzorno plošče naj se vstavi seznam, razpredelnica ali graf."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:227
msgid ""
"The dashboard's underlying spreadsheet opens, with the new data inserted "
"either on a new sheet (list or pivot table) or on the first sheet (chart)."
msgstr ""
"Osnovna preglednica nadzorne plošče se odpre z novimi podatki, vstavljenimi "
"bodisi na novem listu (seznam ali vrtilna tabela) bodisi na prvem listu "
"(grafikon)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/build_and_customize_dashboards.rst:231
msgid ":doc:`Inserting Odoo data into a spreadsheet <../spreadsheet/insert>`"
msgstr ":doc:`Vstavljanje podatkov Odoo v preglednico <../spreadsheet/insert>`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:3
msgid "My Dashboard"
msgstr "Moja nadzorna plošča"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:6
msgid ""
"To have access to **My Dashboard**, make sure the :guilabel:`Dashboards` "
"(`board`) module is :ref:`installed <general/install>` in addition to "
"the :guilabel:`Spreadsheet dashboard` (`spreadsheet_dashboard)` module."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do **Moja nadzorna plošča** se prepričajte, da je "
"modul :guilabel:`Nadzorne  plošče` (`board`) :ref:`nameščen <general/"
"install>` poleg modula :guilabel:`Preglednica nadzorne plošče` "
"(`spreadsheet_dashboard)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:10
msgid ""
"**My Dashboard** allows you to centralize the :doc:`Odoo views <../../studio/"
"views>` you consult most regularly, making it possible to see critical tasks "
"at a glance without having to first navigate through multiple apps."
msgstr ""
"**Moja nadzorna plošča** vam omogoča centralizacijo :doc:`pogledov Odoo "
"<../../studio/views>`, ki jih najbolj redno pregledujete, kar omogoča "
"pregled kritičnih nalog na hiter pogled brez predhodnega krmarjenja skozi "
"več aplikacij."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:14
msgid "My Dashboard is empty until at least one view has been added."
msgstr "Moja nadzorna plošča je prazna, dokler ni dodan vsaj en pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Example of views added to My Dashboard"
msgstr "Primer pogledov, dodanih na Mojo nadzorno ploščo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:19
msgid ""
"Views inserted in My Dashboard are fully dynamic and retain many features of "
"the source view, e.g., sorting of lists, changing the measures used for a "
"pivot table or cohort view, changing the chart type, or clicking on a value "
"or data point to view the underlying record(s)."
msgstr ""
"Pogledi, vstavljeni v Moja nadzorna plošča, so popolnoma dinamični in "
"ohranijo številne funkcije izvornega pogleda, npr. razvrščanje seznamov, "
"spreminjanje mer, uporabljenih za pogled razpredelnice ali kohortni pogled, "
"spreminjanje vrste grafa ali klikanje na vrednost ali podatkovno točko za "
"ogled osnovnih zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:24
msgid ""
"It is not possible to change the domain, i.e., the :doc:`filtering or "
"grouping <../../essentials/search>`, of a view that has been added to My "
"Dashboard. To change the domain, make the necessary changes in the original "
"view, then re-insert the view in My Dashboard and delete the originally "
"inserted view."
msgstr ""
"Ni mogoče spremeniti domene, tj. :doc:`filtriranja ali združevanja <../../"
"essentials/search>`, pogleda, ki je bil dodan na Mojo nadzorno ploščo. Za "
"spremembo domene izvedite potrebne spremembe v izvirnem pogledu, nato znova "
"vstavite pogled v Mojo nadzorno ploščo in izbrišite izvorno vstavljeni "
"pogled."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:28
msgid ""
"Unlike other Odoo dashboards, My Dashboard is not based on **Odoo "
"Spreadsheet**."
msgstr ""
"Za razliko od drugih nadzornih plošč Odoo, Moja nadzorna plošča ni osnovana "
"na **Odoo Spreadsheet**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:33
msgid "Add views"
msgstr "Dodajte poglede"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:35
msgid "Most Odoo views can be added to My Dashboard, including:"
msgstr "Večino pogledov Odoo lahko dodate v Moja nadzorna plošča, vključno z:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:37
msgid ""
":ref:`multiple record views <studio/views/multiple-records>` like list, "
"kanban, and map"
msgstr ""
":ref:`pogledi več zapisov <studio/views/multiple-records>`, kot so seznam, "
"kanban in zemljevid"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:38
msgid ""
":ref:`timeline views <studio/views/timeline>` like calendar, cohort, and "
"gantt"
msgstr ""
":ref:`pogledi časovnice <studio/views/timeline>`, kot so koledar, kohorta in "
"gantt"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:39
msgid ":ref:`reporting views <studio/views/reporting>` like pivot and graph"
msgstr ""
":ref:`pogledi poročanja <studio/views/reporting>`, kot so razpredelnica in "
"graf"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:41
msgid "To add a view to My Dashboard:"
msgstr "Če želite dodati pogled v Moja nadzorna plošča:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:43
msgid ""
"With the relevant view open in your database, click the :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Actions)` icon beside the name of the view, "
"then :menuselection:`Dashboard`."
msgstr ""
"Ko je v vaši zbirki podatkov odprt ustrezen pogled, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"cog` :guilabel:`(Dejanja)` poleg imena pogleda, "
"nato :menuselection:`Nadzorna plošča`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:45
msgid ""
"Under :guilabel:`Add to my Dashboard`, rename the view if desired, then "
"click :guilabel:`Add`."
msgstr ""
"Pod :guilabel:`Dodaj v mojo nadzorno plošče` po želji preimenujte pogled, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Adding a view to My Dashboard"
msgstr "Dodajanje pogleda v Moja nadzorna plošča"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:51
msgid "Refresh the page."
msgstr "Osvežite stran."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:53
msgid ""
"The added view is now visible as a widget in My Dashboard in the Dashboards "
"app."
msgstr ""
"Dodani pogled je zdaj viden kot gradnik v Moja nadzorna plošča v aplikaciji "
"Nadzorne plošče."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:56
msgid ""
"If added views are not showing in My Dashboard, refresh the browser page."
msgstr ""
"Če dodani pogledi niso prikazani v Moja nadzorna plošča, osvežite stran "
"brskalnika."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:61
msgid "Customize layout"
msgstr "Prilagoditev postavitve"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:63
msgid ""
"When at least one view has been added to My Dashboard, the page can be "
"customized as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je vsaj en pogled dodan v Moja nadzorna plošča, lahko stran prilagodite "
"na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:65
msgid ""
"**Change the layout of the page**: Click :guilabel:`Change Layout` in the "
"top-right corner and select the desired layout."
msgstr ""
"**Spremenite postavitev strani**: Kliknite :guilabel:`Spremeni postavitev` v "
"zgornjem desnem kotu in izberite želeno postavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:69
msgid ""
"For multi-column layouts, the column limits are identified by :icon:`fa-"
"caret-left` :guilabel:`(left caret)` and :icon:`fa-caret-"
"right` :guilabel:`(right caret)` icons at the bottom of the page. If needed, "
"scroll to the bottom of the page to see the column limits."
msgstr ""
"Pri postavitvah z več stolpci so meje stolpcev označene z ikonama :icon:`fa-"
"caret-left` :guilabel:`(leva puščica)` in :icon:`fa-caret-"
"right` :guilabel:`(desna puščica)` na dnu strani. Po potrebi se pomaknite na "
"dno strani, da vidite meje stolpcev."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:0
msgid "Column limits visible at bottom of page"
msgstr "Meje stolpcev vidne na dnu strani"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:76
msgid ""
"**Collapse and expand widgets**: By default, an inserted widget is shown "
"fully expanded. To collapse, or minimize, a widget, and show only the title, "
"click the :icon:`fa-window-minimize` :guilabel:`(minimize)` icon at the top "
"right of the widget. To expand a widget, click the :icon:`fa-window-"
"maximize` :guilabel:`(maximize)` icon."
msgstr ""
"**Skrči in razširi gradnike**: Privzeto je vstavljen gradnik prikazan "
"popolnoma razširjen. Če želite skrčiti ali minimizirati gradnik in prikazati "
"samo naslov, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-window-"
"minimize` :guilabel:`(minimiziraj)` v zgornjem desnem delu gradnika. Če "
"želite razširiti gradnik, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-window-"
"maximize` :guilabel:`(maksimiziraj)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Move widgets**: Drag and drop widgets to the desired location in the same "
"column or a different column."
msgstr ""
"**Premikanje gradnikov**: Povlecite in spustite gradnike na želeno mesto v "
"istem stolpcu ali drugem stolpcu."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/dashboards/my_dashboard.rst:82
msgid ""
"**Remove widgets**: To remove a widget from the page, click the :icon:`fa-"
"times` :guilabel:`(remove)` icon."
msgstr ""
"**Odstranitev gradnikov**: Če želite odstraniti gradnik s strani, kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(odstrani)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:3
msgid "Data Cleaning"
msgstr "Čiščenje podatkov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Data Cleaning** app maintains data integrity and consistency with "
"the following features:"
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo **Čiščenje podatkov** vzdržuje integriteto in doslednost "
"podatkov z naslednjimi funkcijami:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:7
msgid ""
":ref:`Deduplicates <data_cleaning/deduplication>`: merges or removes "
"duplicate entries to ensure data is unique."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Odstrani podvojene vnose <data_cleaning/deduplication>`: združi ali "
"odstrani podvojene vnose, da zagotovi edinstvenost podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:9
msgid ""
":ref:`Recycles <data_cleaning/recycle>`: identifies outdated records to "
"either archive or delete them."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Reciklira <data_cleaning/recycle>`: prepozna zastarele zapise za "
"arhiviranje ali brisanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:11
msgid ""
":ref:`Formats <data_cleaning/field-cleaning>`: standardizes text data by "
"finding and replacing it according to specified needs."
msgstr ""
":ref:`Oblikuje <data_cleaning/field-cleaning>`: standardizira besedilne "
"podatke z iskanjem in nadomeščanjem glede na določene potrebe."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:14
msgid ""
"Customizable rules ensure text data stays up-to-date, streamlined, "
"consistently formatted, and aligned with company-specific formatting "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"Prilagodljiva pravila zagotavljajo, da so besedilni podatki posodobljeni, "
"poenostavljeni, dosledno oblikovani in usklajeni s specifičnimi zahtevami "
"podjetja glede oblikovanja."

