msgstr ":guilabel:`Računovodsko združevanje WMS`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:0
msgid "`data_merge_stock_account`"
msgstr "`data_merge_stock_account`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:65
msgid ""
"Creates a warning in cases of products merging that may affect inventory "
"valuation, if the **Inventory** app is installed."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari opozorilo v primerih združevanja izdelkov, ki lahko vplivajo na "
"vrednotenje zaloge, če je nameščena aplikacija **Zaloga**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:71
msgid "Deduplication"
msgstr "Deduplikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:73
msgid ""
"The *Duplicates* dashboard groups similar records to be :ref:`merged "
"<data_cleaning/merge-records>` by matching conditions within the records set "
"by the :ref:`deduplication rules <data_cleaning/deduplication-rules>`."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna plošča *Duplikati* združuje podobne zapise, ki jih je "
"treba :ref:`združiti <data_cleaning/merge-records>`, s primerjavo pogojev "
"znotraj zapisov, določenih z :ref:`deduplikacijskimi pravili <data_cleaning/"
"deduplication-rules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:77
msgid ""
"Navigate to this dashboard by going to :menuselection:`Data Cleaning app --> "
"Deduplication`."
msgstr ""
"Do te nadzorne plošče pridete tako, da izberete :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"za čiščenje podatkov --> Deduplikacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:None
msgid "Deduplication dashboard in the Data Cleaning application."
msgstr "Nadzorna plošča deduplikacije v aplikaciji Čiščenje podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:82
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`RULE` sidebar lists each of the active deduplication rules, "
"and displays the total number of duplicates detected beside each rule."
msgstr ""
"Stranska vrstica :guilabel:`PRAVILO` navaja vsa aktivna pravila za "
"deduplikacijo in prikazuje skupno število zaznanih duplikatov poleg vsakega "
"pravila."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:85
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`All` rule is selected. Records are grouped by "
"their rule, with a :guilabel:`Similarity` rating (out of 100%), with the "
"following columns:"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je izbrano pravilo :guilabel:`Vse`. Zapisi so združeni po svojem "
"pravilu z oceno :guilabel:`Podobnost` (od 100 %) z naslednjimi stolpci:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:88
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Created On`: the date and time the original record was created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ustvarjeno dne`: datum in čas, ko je bil ustvarjen izvirni zapis."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:89
msgid ":guilabel:`Name`: the name or title of the original record."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime`: ime ali naslov izvirnega zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:90
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Field Values`: the original record's values for the fields used "
"to detect duplicates."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrednosti polja`: vrednosti izvirnega zapisa za polja, "
"uporabljena za zaznavanje duplikatov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:91
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Used In`: lists other models referencing the original record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabljeno v`: navaja druge modele, ki se sklicujejo na izvirni "
"zapis."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`ID`: the original record's unique ID."
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID`: edinstveni ID izvirnega zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:93
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Is Master`: the duplicates are merged into the *master* record. "
"There can only be **one** master record in a grouping of similar records."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Je glavno`: duplikati so združeni v *glavni* zapis. V skupini "
"podobnih zapisov je lahko **en** glavni zapis."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:96
msgid ""
"Select a specific rule in the :guilabel:`RULE` sidebar to filter the "
"duplicate records."
msgstr ""
"Izberite določeno pravilo v stranski vrstici :guilabel:`PRAVILO`, da "
"filtrirate podvojene zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:101
msgid "Merge duplicate records"
msgstr "Združi podvojene zapise"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:103
msgid ""
"To merge records, first choose a *master* record within the grouping of "
"similar records. The master record acts as the base, at which any additional "
"information from similar records are merged into."
msgstr ""
"Za združevanje zapisov najprej izberite *glavni* zapis v skupini podobnih "
"zapisov. Glavni zapis deluje kot osnova, v katero so združene vse dodatne "
"informacije iz podobnih zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:106
msgid ""
"Optionally, no master record can be set, leaving Odoo to choose a record at "
"random to merge into."
msgstr ""
"Po želji lahko glavni zapis ni nastavljen, pri čemer Odoo naključno izbere "
"zapis za združevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:108
msgid ""
"Next, click the :guilabel:`Merge` button at the top of the similar records "
"grouping. Then, click :guilabel:`Ok` to confirm the merge."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Združi` na vrhu skupine podobnih zapisov. Nato "
"kliknite :guilabel:`V redu`, da potrdite združevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:111
msgid ""
"Once a record is merged, a message is logged in the chatter of the master "
"record, describing the merge. Certain records, like **Project** tasks, are "
"logged in the chatter with a link to the old record as a convenient "
"reference of the merge."
msgstr ""
"Ko je zapis združen, je sporočilo zabeleženo v pogovoru glavnega zapisa, ki "
"opisuje združitev. Nekateri zapisi, kot so opravila **Projekt**, so "
"zabeleženi v pogovoru s povezavo do starega zapisa kot priročna referenca "
"združitve."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:116
msgid ""
"Discard groupings by clicking the :guilabel:`DISCARD` button. Upon doing so, "
"the grouping is hidden from the list and archived."
msgstr ""
"Zavrzite skupine s klikom na gumb :guilabel:`ZAVRZI`. Po tem je skupina "
"skrita s seznama in arhivirana."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:119
msgid ""
"View discarded groupings by selecting the :guilabel:`Discarded` filter from "
"the :ref:`search bar <search/filters>`."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si zavržene skupine tako, da izberete filter :guilabel:`Zavrženo` "
"v :ref:`iskalnem polju <search/filters>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:125
msgid "Deduplication rules"
msgstr "Pravila za deduplikacijo"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:127
msgid ""
"The *Deduplication Rules* set the conditions for how records are detected as "
"duplicates."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za deduplikacijo določajo pogoje za zaznavanje zapisov kot "
"duplikatov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:129
msgid ""
"These rules can be configured for each model in the database, and with "
"varying levels of specificity. To get started, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Data Cleaning app --> Configuration --> Deduplication`."
msgstr ""
"Ta pravila je mogoče konfigurirati za vsak model v zbirki podatkov in z "
"različnimi stopnjami specifičnosti. Za začetek pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Čiščenje podatkov --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Deduplikacija`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:134
msgid ""
"The deduplication rules run once every day, by default, as part of a "
"scheduled action cron (*Data Merge: Find Duplicate Records*). However, each "
"rule can be :ref:`ran manually <data_cleaning/run-deduplication-rule>` "
"anytime."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov se privzeto izvajajo enkrat "
"dnevno kot del načrtovanega opravila cron (*Data Merge: Find Duplicate "
"Records*). Vendar pa je mogoče vsako pravilo :ref:`zagnati ročno "
"<data_cleaning/run-deduplication-rule>` kadar koli."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:139
msgid "Modify a deduplication rule"
msgstr "Spreminjanje pravila za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:141
msgid ""
"Select a default rule to edit, or create a new rule by clicking on "
"the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Izberite privzeto pravilo za urejanje ali ustvarite novo pravilo s klikom na "
"gumb :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:143
msgid ""
"First, choose a :guilabel:`Model` for this rule to target. Selecting a model "
"updates the rule title to the chosen model."
msgstr ""
"Najprej izberite :guilabel:`Model` za to pravilo. Izbira modela posodobi "
"naslov pravila na izbrani model."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:146
msgid ""
"Optionally, configure a :guilabel:`Domain` to specify the records eligible "
"for this rule. The number of eligible records is shown in the :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`# record(s)` link."
msgstr ""
"Izbirno konfigurirajte :guilabel:`Domeno`, da določite zapise, za katere "
"velja to pravilo. Število upravičenih zapisov je prikazano v "
"povezavi :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`št. zapisov`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:149
msgid ""
"Depending on the selected :guilabel:`Model`, the :guilabel:`Duplicate "
"Removal` field appears. Choose whether to :guilabel:`Archive` "
"or :guilabel:`Delete` merged records."
msgstr ""
"Glede na izbrani :guilabel:`Model` se prikaže "
"polje :guilabel:`Odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov`. Izberite, ali "
"želite :guilabel:`Arhivirati` ali :guilabel:`Izbrisati` združene zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:152
msgid "Next, select a :guilabel:`Merge Mode`:"
msgstr "Nato izberite :guilabel:`Način združevanja`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:154
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manual`: requires each duplicate grouping to be manually merged, "
"also enables the :guilabel:`Notify Users` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ročno`: zahteva ročno združevanje vsake skupine podvojenih "
"zapisov, omogoči tudi polje :guilabel:`Obvesti uporabnike`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:156
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Automatic`: automatically merges duplicate groupings, without "
"notifying users, based on the records with a similarity percentage above the "
"threshold set in the :guilabel:`Similarity Threshold` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno`: samodejno združi skupine podvojenih zapisov, brez "
"obveščanja uporabnikov, na podlagi zapisov s podobnostjo nad pragom, "
"določenim v polju :guilabel:`Prag podobnosti`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:160
msgid ""
"Enable the :guilabel:`Active` toggle to start capturing duplicates with this "
"rule as soon as it is saved."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite preklopnik :guilabel:`Aktivno`, da začnete zajemati podvojene "
"zapise s tem pravilom takoj, ko ga shranite."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:163
msgid ""
"Lastly, create at least one deduplication rule in "
"the :guilabel:`Deduplication Rules` field, by clicking :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`, under the :guilabel:`Unique ID Field` column."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje ustvarite vsaj eno pravilo za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov v "
"polju :guilabel:`Pravila za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov` tako, da "
"kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` pod stolpcem :guilabel:`Polje enolične "
"oznake`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:166
msgid ""
"Select a field in the model from the :guilabel:`Unique ID Field` drop-down "
"menu. This field is referenced for similar records."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem meniju :guilabel:`Polje enolične oznake` izberite polje v modelu. "
"To polje se uporablja za iskanje podobnih zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:168
msgid ""
"Select a matching condition in the :guilabel:`Match If` field to apply the "
"deduplication rule, depending on the text in the :guilabel:`Unique ID Field`:"
msgstr ""
"V polju :guilabel:`Ujemanje, če` izberite pogoj ujemanja za uporabo pravila "
"za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov, odvisno od besedila v :guilabel:`Polju "
"enolične oznake`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:171
msgid ":guilabel:`Exact Match`: the characters in the text match exactly."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Natančno ujemanje`: znaki v besedilu se natančno ujemajo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:172
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Case/Accent Insensitive Match`: the characters in the text match, "
"regardless of casing and language-specific accent differences."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ujemanje brez razlikovanja velikih/malih črk in naglasov`: znaki "
"v besedilu se ujemajo ne glede na velikost črk in jezikovne razlike v "
"naglaševanju."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:176
msgid ""
"At least one :guilabel:`Deduplication Rules` must be set for the rule to "
"capture duplicates."
msgstr ""
"Vsaj eno pravilo v :guilabel:`Pravilih za odstranjevanje podvojenih zapisov` "
"mora biti nastavljeno, da pravilo zajema podvojene zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:179
msgid "A few more fields are available for an advanced configuration."
msgstr "Na voljo je še nekaj polj za napredno konfiguracijo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:181
msgid ""
"If on a multi-company database, the :guilabel:`Cross-Company` field is "
"available. When enabled, duplicates across different companies are suggested."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabljate večpodjetniško bazo podatkov, je na voljo "
"polje :guilabel:`Med podjetji`. Ko je omogočeno, so predlagani podvojeni "
"zapisi iz različnih podjetij."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:184
msgid ""
"Activate :ref:`developer-mode` to display the :guilabel:`Suggestion "
"Threshold` field. Duplicates with a similarity below the threshold set in "
"this field are **not** suggested."
msgstr ""
"Aktivirajte :ref:`developer-mode`, da se prikaže polje :guilabel:`Prag za "
"predloge`. Podvojeni zapisi s podobnostjo pod pragom, določenim v tem polju, "
"**niso** predlagani."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:187
msgid ""
"With the rule's configuration complete, either close the rule form, "
"or :ref:`run the rule manually <data_cleaning/run-deduplication-rule>` to "
"instantly capture duplicate records."
msgstr ""
"Ko je konfiguracija pravila končana, bodisi zaprite obrazec pravila "
"bodisi :ref:`ročno zaženite pravilo <data_cleaning/run-deduplication-rule>`, "
"da takoj zajamete podvojene zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:193
msgid "Manually run a deduplication rule"
msgstr "Ročno zaženi pravilo deduplikacije"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:195
msgid ""
"To manually run a specific deduplication rule at any time, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Data Cleaning app --> Configuration --> Deduplication`, "
"and select the rule to run."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ročno zagnati določeno pravilo deduplikacije kadarkoli, pojdite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Čiščenje podatkov --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Deduplikacija` in izberite pravilo za zagon."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:198
msgid ""
"Then, on the rule form, select the :guilabel:`Deduplicate` button on the top-"
"left. Upon doing so, the :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplicates` smart "
"button displays the number of duplicates captured."
msgstr ""
"Nato v obrazcu pravila izberite gumb :guilabel:`Dedupliraj` zgoraj levo. Ko "
"to storite, pametni gumb :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplikati` prikaže "
"število zajetih duplikatov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:201
msgid ""
"Click on the :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplicates` smart button "
"to :ref:`manage these records <data_cleaning/merge-records>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na pametni gumb :icon:`fa-clone` :guilabel:`Duplikati`, "
"da :ref:`upravljate te zapise <data_cleaning/merge-records>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:207
msgid "Recycle records"
msgstr "Recikliraj zapise"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:209
msgid ""
"Use the *recycle records* feature to rid the database of old and outdated "
"records."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite funkcijo *recikliranje zapisov*, da se znebite starih in "
"zastarelih zapisov iz podatkovne baze."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:211
msgid ""
"The *Field Recycle Records* dashboard displays records that can be archived "
"or deleted, by matching conditions within the records set by "
"the :ref:`recycle record's rules <data_cleaning/recylce-rule>`."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna plošča *Reciklirani zapisi polja* prikazuje zapise, ki jih je "
"mogoče arhivirati ali izbrisati, glede na ujemajoče se pogoje znotraj "
"zapisov, ki jih določajo :ref:`pravila za recikliranje zapisov "
"<data_cleaning/recylce-rule>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:214
msgid ""
"Navigate to this dashboard by going to :menuselection:`Data Cleaning app --> "
"Recycle Records`."
msgstr ""
"Do te nadzorne plošče pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Čiščenje "
"podatkov --> Recikliraj zapise`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:None
msgid "Field Recycle Records dashboard in the Data Cleaning application."
msgstr ""
"Nadzorna plošča Reciklirani zapisi polja v aplikaciji Čiščenje podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:219
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`RECYCLE RULES` sidebar lists each of the active recycle "
"record rules."
msgstr ""
"Stranska vrstica :guilabel:`PRAVILA ZA RECIKLIRANJE` navaja vsako od "
"aktivnih pravil za recikliranje zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:221
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`All` option is selected. Records are displayed "
"with the following columns:"
msgstr ""
"Privzeto je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Vse`. Zapisi so prikazani z "
"naslednjimi stolpci:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:224
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:339
msgid ":guilabel:`Record ID`: the ID of the original record."
msgstr ":guilabel:`ID zapisa`: ID izvirnega zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:225
#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:340
msgid ":guilabel:`Record Name`: the name or title of the original record."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ime zapisa`: ime ali naslov izvirnega zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:227
msgid ""
"Select a specific rule in the :guilabel:`RECYCLE RULES` sidebar to filter "
"the records."
msgstr ""
"Izberite določeno pravilo v stranski vrstici :guilabel:`PRAVILA ZA "
"RECIKLIRANJE`, da filtrirate zapise."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:229
msgid ""
"To recycle records, click the :icon:`fa-check` :guilabel:`Validate` button "
"on the row of the record."
msgstr ""
"Če želite reciklirati zapise, kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-"
"check` :guilabel:`Potrdi` v vrstici zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:231
msgid ""
"Upon doing so, the record is recycled, depending on how the rule is "
"configured, to be either archived or deleted from the database."
msgstr ""
"Ko to storite, je zapis recikliran glede na to, kako je pravilo "
"konfigurirano, bodisi arhiviran ali izbrisan iz podatkovne baze."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:235
msgid ""
"Discard groupings by clicking the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Discard` "
"button. Upon doing so, the record is hidden from the list, and is not "
"detected by the recycle rule again in the future."
msgstr ""
"Zavrzite združevanja s klikom na gumb :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`Zavrzi`. "
"Ko to storite, je zapis skrit s seznama in ga pravilo za recikliranje v "
"prihodnje ne zazna več."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:238
msgid ""
"View discarded records by selecting the :guilabel:`Discarded` filter from "
"the :ref:`search bar <search/filters>` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Oglejte si zavržene zapise z izbiro filtra :guilabel:`Zavrženo` iz spustnega "
"menija :ref:`iskalne vrstice <search/filters>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:244
msgid "Recycle record rules"
msgstr "Pravila za recikliranje zapisov"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:246
msgid ""
"The *Recycle Records Rules* set the conditions for how records are recycled."
msgstr ""
"Pravila za recikliranje zapisov določajo pogoje za recikliranje zapisov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:248
msgid ""
"These rules can be configured for each model in the database, and with "
"varying levels of specificity. To get started, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Data Cleaning app --> Configuration --> Recycle Records`."
msgstr ""
"Ta pravila je mogoče nastaviti za vsak model v zbirki podatkov, z različnimi "
"stopnjami specifičnosti. Za začetek se pomaknite "
"na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Čiščenje podatkov --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Recikliraj zapise`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:253
msgid ""
"Recycle rules run once a day, by default, as part of a scheduled action cron "
"(*Data Recycle: Clean Records*). However, each rule can be :ref:`run "
"manually <data-cleaning/run-recycle-rule>` anytime."
msgstr ""
"Pravila recikliranja se privzeto izvajajo enkrat na dan kot del načrtovanega "
"dejanja cron (*Recikliranje podatkov: Čiščenje zapisov*). Vendar pa je "
"mogoče vsako pravilo :ref:`zagnati ročno <data-cleaning/run-recycle-rule>` "
"kadar koli."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:257
msgid ""
"By default, no recycle record rules exist. Click the :guilabel:`New` button "
"to create a new rule."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto ne obstaja nobeno pravilo za recikliranje zapisov. Kliknite "
"gumb :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite novo pravilo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:259
msgid ""
"On the recycle record rule form, first choose a :guilabel:`Model` for this "
"rule to target. Selecting a model updates the rule title to the chosen model."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu pravila za recikliranje zapisov najprej "
"izberite :guilabel:`Model`, na katerega naj se usmerja to pravilo. Izbira "
"modela posodobi naslov pravila na izbrani model."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:262
msgid ""
"Optionally, configure a :guilabel:`Filter` to specify the records eligible "
"for this rule. The number of eligible records is shown in the :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`# record(s)` link."
msgstr ""
"Izbirno nastavite :guilabel:`Filter`, da določite zapise, ki so upravičeni "
"za to pravilo. Število upravičenih zapisov je prikazano v povezavi :icon:`oi-"
"arrow-right` :guilabel:`# zapis(i)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:265
msgid ""
"Next, configure the field and time range for how the rule detects the "
"records to recycle:"
msgstr ""
"Nato nastavite polje in časovno obdobje za način, kako pravilo zazna zapise "
"za recikliranje:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:267
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Time Field`: select a field from the model to base the time "
"(:dfn:`Delta`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Časovno polje`: izberite polje iz modela kot osnovo za čas "
"(:dfn:`Delta`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:268
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delta`: type the length of time, which must be a whole number "
"(e.g. `7`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Delta`: vnesite dolžino časa, ki mora biti celo število (npr. "
"`7`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:269
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delta Unit`: select the unit of time "
"(:guilabel:`Days`, :guilabel:`Weeks`, :guilabel:`Months`, "
"or :guilabel:`Years`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Enota delte`: izberite časovno enoto "
"(:guilabel:`Dni`, :guilabel:`Tedni`, :guilabel:`Meseci` "
"ali :guilabel:`Leta`)."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:272
msgid "Then, select a :guilabel:`Recycle Mode`:"
msgstr "Nato izberite :guilabel:`Način recikliranja`:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:274
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Manual`: requires each detected record to be manually recycled, "
"and enables the :guilabel:`Notify Users` field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ročno`: zahteva, da se vsak zaznan zapis reciklira ročno, in "
"omogoči polje :guilabel:`Obvesti uporabnike`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:276
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Automatic`: automatically merges recycled groupings, without "
"notifying users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno`: samodejno združi reciklirane skupine, ne da bi "
"obvestilo uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:278
msgid ""
"Lastly, select a :guilabel:`Recycle Action` to either :guilabel:`Archive` "
"or :guilabel:`Delete` records. If :guilabel:`Delete` is selected, choose "
"whether or not to :guilabel:`Include Archived` records in the rule."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje izberite :guilabel:`Dejanje recikliranja`, da "
"zapise :guilabel:`Arhivirate` ali :guilabel:`Izbrišete`. Če je "
"izbrano :guilabel:`Izbriši`, izberite, ali želite :guilabel:`Vključiti "
"arhivirane` zapise v pravilo."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:282
msgid ""
"With the rule's configuration complete, either close the rule form, "
"or :ref:`run the rule manually <data-cleaning/run-recycle-rule>` to "
"instantly capture records to recycle."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nastavitev pravila dokončana, zaprite obrazec pravila ali :ref:`ročno "
"zaženite pravilo <data-cleaning/run-recycle-rule>`, da takoj zajamete zapise "
"za recikliranje."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:286
msgid ""
"A recycle rule can be configured to delete archived leads and opportunities "
"that were last updated a year ago, and with a specific lost reason, by using "
"the following configuration:"
msgstr ""
"Pravilo za recikliranje je mogoče nastaviti tako, da izbriše arhivirane "
"priložnosti in potencialne stranke, ki so bile nazadnje posodobljene pred "
"enim letom in imajo določen razlog za izgubo, z uporabo naslednje "
"konfiguracije:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:289
msgid ":guilabel:`Model`: :guilabel:`Lead/Opportunity`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Model`: :guilabel:`Potencialna stranka/Priložnost`"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/data_cleaning.rst:290
msgid ":guilabel:`Filter`:"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Filter`:"

