msgid "Article editing"
msgstr "Urejanje članka"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:62
msgid ""
"To edit an article, select it in the sidebar tree, then edit its content and "
"format it using the :ref:`text editor toolbar <knowledge/articles_editing/"
"text-editor>`, typing :ref:`powerbox commands <knowledge/articles_editing/"
"commands>`, and adding a :ref:`cover picture <knowledge/articles_editing/"
"cover>` with a :ref:`title emoji <knowledge/articles_editing/emoji>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti članek, ga izberite v drevesu stranske vrstice, nato "
"uredite njegovo vsebino in jo oblikujte z uporabo :ref:`orodne vrstice "
"urejevalnika besedila <knowledge/articles_editing/text-editor>`, "
"vnašanja :ref:`ukazov powerbox <knowledge/articles_editing/commands>` ter "
"dodajanja :ref:`naslovne slike <knowledge/articles_editing/cover>` "
"z :ref:`čustvenim simbolom v naslovu <knowledge/articles_editing/emoji>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:68
msgid ""
"To enlarge or reduce the article's width, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
"(:guilabel:`More actions`) icon, then toggle the :icon:`oi-arrows-"
"h` :guilabel:`Full Width` on or off."
msgstr ""
"Če želite povečati ali zmanjšati širino članka, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-"
"ellipsis-v` (:guilabel:`Več dejanj`), nato pa vklopite ali "
"izklopite :icon:`oi-arrows-h` :guilabel:`Polna širina`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:74
msgid "Text editor toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica urejevalnika besedila"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:76
msgid ""
