"the text editor toolbar and apply the desired :doc:`formatting options </"
"applications/essentials/html_editor>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite urediti besedo, stavek ali odstavek, ga izberite ali dvokliknite, "
"da se prikaže orodna vrstica urejevalnika besedila, in uporabite "
"želene :doc:`možnosti oblikovanja </applications/essentials/html_editor>`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/knowledge.rst:80
msgid ""
"Click :icon:`fa-commenting-o` :guilabel:`Comment` to add a comment to the "
"selected text."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :icon:`fa-commenting-o` :guilabel:`Komentar`, da izbranemu besedilu "
