#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:57
msgid ""
"Next, each user's Axivox credentials must be configured in Odoo. Navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Users & Companies --> Users` select the "
"user, and click the :guilabel:`VoIP` tab."
msgstr ""
"Nato je treba poverilnice Axivox za vsakega uporabnika konfigurirati v Odoo. "
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> Uporabniki in podjetja "
"--> Uporabniki`, izberite uporabnika in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`VoIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:61
msgid ""
"Add the following :ref:`Axivox credentials <productivity/voip/view-axivox-"
"credentials>` for the user:"
msgstr ""
"Dodajte naslednje :ref:`poverilnice Axivox <productivity/voip/view-axivox-"
"credentials>` za uporabnika:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:64
msgid ":guilabel:`Provider`: select :guilabel:`Axivox`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Ponudnik`: izberite :guilabel:`Axivox`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:65
msgid ":guilabel:`Username`: the Axivox :guilabel:`SIP username`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Uporabniško ime`: Axivox :guilabel:`uporabniško ime SIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:66
msgid ":guilabel:`OnSip Auth Username`: the Axivox :guilabel:`SIP username`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Uporabniško ime za avtentikacijo OnSip`: "
"Axivox :guilabel:`uporabniško ime SIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:67
msgid ":guilabel:`Secret`: the Axivox :guilabel:`SIP password`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrivnost`: Axivox :guilabel:`geslo SIP`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/axivox/axivox_config.rst:70
msgid ""
"Make sure to manually type the :guilabel:`SIP password` into the "
