#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:7
msgid ""
"The **Phone** widget is an add-on made available to Odoo users by installing "
"the **Phone** app. Instead of managing mobile devices for every salesperson, "
"fumbling through call transfers for upset customers, or needing a meeting "
"room to handle a conference call, utilize the **Phone** widget to tackle any "
"of these business needs."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik **Telefon** je dodatek, ki je na voljo uporabnikom Odoo z "
"namestitvijo aplikacije **Telefon**. Namesto upravljanja mobilnih naprav za "
"vsakega prodajalca, prebiranja med prenosi klicev za vznemirjene stranke ali "
"potrebe po sejni sobi za obravnavo konferenčnega klica, uporabite gradnik "
"**Telefon** za reševanje katerihkoli od teh poslovnih potreb."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:13
msgid "Navigate the Phone widget"
msgstr "Krmarjenje po gradniku Telefon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:15
msgid ""
"The **Phone** widget contains four "
"tabs: :guilabel:`Keypad`, :guilabel:`Recent`, :guilabel:`Contacts`, "
"and :guilabel:`Activities`, which are used for managing calls and day-to-day "
"activities in Odoo. Use the search bar to find contacts faster."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik **Telefon** vsebuje štiri "
"zavihke: :guilabel:`Tipkovnica`, :guilabel:`Nedavno`, :guilabel:`Stiki` "
"in :guilabel:`Aktivnosti`, ki se uporabljajo za upravljanje klicev in "
"vsakodnevnih aktivnosti v Odoo. Uporabite iskalno vrstico za hitrejše "
"iskanje stikov."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:None
msgid ""
"The **Phone** widget has four tabs: **Keypad**, **Recent**, **Contacts**, "
"and **Activities**."
msgstr ""
"Gradnik **Telefon** ima štiri zavihke: **Tipkovnica**, **Nedavno**, "
"**Stiki** in **Aktivnosti**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:23
msgid "Keypad tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Tipkovnica"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:25
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Keypad` tab of the **Phone** widget, the user can type "
"a name or number to make a call. There is also a numeric keypad for the user "
"to enter the phone number."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Tipkovnica` gradnika **Telefon** lahko uporabnik vpiše "
"ime ali številko za izvedbo klica. Na voljo je tudi številčna tipkovnica, v "
"katero uporabnik vnese telefonsko številko."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:29
msgid "Recent tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Nedavno"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:31
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Recent` tab of the **Phone** widget, the call history "
"for the user is available. This includes incoming and outgoing calls. Any "
"number can be clicked to begin a call."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Nedavno` gradnika **Telefon** je na voljo zgodovina "
"klicev za uporabnika. To vključuje dohodne in odhodne klice. Za začetek "
"klica je mogoče klikniti katero koli številko."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:35
msgid "Contacts tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Stiki"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:37
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Contacts` tab of the **Phone** widget, the user can "
"access a contact in the **Contacts** app."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Stiki` gradnika **Telefon** lahko uporabnik dostopa do "
"stika v aplikaciji **Stiki**."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:40
msgid ""
"Any contact that has a saved phone number can be called by clicking into the "
"contact from the *Phone* widget's :guilabel:`Contacts` tab."
msgstr ""
"Katerega koli stika, ki ima shranjeno telefonsko številko, je mogoče "
"poklicati s klikom na stik iz zavihka :guilabel:`Stiki` gradnika *Telefon*."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:43
msgid ""
"A search feature is also available at the top of the widget, represented by "
"a :icon:`fa-search` :guilabel:`(search)` icon. Use this tool to find a "
"specific contact. Scheduled activities will not appear as search results."
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu gradnika je na voljo tudi funkcija iskanja, ki jo predstavlja "
"ikona :icon:`fa-search` :guilabel:`(iskanje)`. To orodje uporabite za "
"iskanje določenega stika. Načrtovane aktivnosti se ne bodo prikazale med "
"rezultati iskanja."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:48
msgid "Activities tab"
msgstr "Zavihek Aktivnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:50
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Activities` tab of the **Phone** widget, a user can see "
"any calls assigned to them, and which ones are due to be completed for the "
"day."
msgstr ""
"V zavihku :guilabel:`Aktivnosti` gradnika **Telefon** lahko uporabnik vidi "
"vse klice, ki so mu dodeljeni, in katere je treba opraviti za ta dan."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:53
msgid ""
"Click an activity from this tab to perform any of these actions to prepare "
