msgid ""
":icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`Leads/Create Lead`: opens the lead information "
"for this contact."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-star` :guilabel:`Potencialne stranke/Ustvari potencialno stranko`: "
"odpre informacije o potencialni stranki za ta stik."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:59
msgid ""
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Open related record)`: opens the attached "
"record in Odoo (like"
msgstr ""
":icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`Odpri povezan zapis`: odpre priloženi "
"zapis v Odoo (kot so"

