"the :guilabel:`Activities` tab. After that, hover over the opportunity that "
"should have a call and click the :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(phone)` with "
"the small green :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Na domači strani baze podatkov kliknite :menuselection:`aplikacijo CRM`. "
"Na :guilabel:`Cevovodu` se prepričajte, da je odprt pogled Kanban. Nato v "
"zgornjem delu zaslona kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Prikaži "
"softphone)` in se prepričajte, da je pripomoček **Telefon** odprt na "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Aktivnosti`. Nato se pomaknite čez priložnost, ki bi "
"morala imeti klic, in kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-phone` :guilabel:`(telefon)` "
"z majhno zeleno ikono :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:None
