#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:91
msgid "Make a VoIP call with the Phone widget"
msgstr "Opravite VoIP klic s pripomočkom Telefon"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:93
msgid ""
"One of the primary purposes of the Odoo **Phone** app is to make calls "
"without needing a phone. Here are the three ways to make a phone call in the "
"Odoo database. First, click the :icon:`oi-voip` :guilabel:`(Show Softphone)` "
"icon, located in the top-right of the navigation bar. From here:"
msgstr ""
"Eden od glavnih namenov aplikacije Odoo **Telefon** je opravljanje klicev "
"brez potrebe po telefonu. Tukaj so trije načini za opravitev telefonskega "
"klica v bazi podatkov Odoo. Najprej kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-"
"voip` :guilabel:`(Prikaži softphone)`, ki se nahaja v zgornjem desnem delu "
"navigacijske vrstice. Od tod:"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/phone/phone_widget.rst:97
msgid ""
"Enter the phone number to be called by clicking the :icon:`fa-keyboard-"
"o` :guilabel:`(keyboard)` icon, and then entering the phone number."
msgstr ""
