"(:guilabel:`spustni meni`) v zgornjem desnem kotu poleg imena(-ov) "
"podpisnika(-ov), nato izberite :guilabel:`Zavrni podpis`. Vnesite razlog za "
"zavrnitev, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Zavrni`."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/sign_document.rst:134
msgid ""
"The signature request is then marked as :guilabel:`Cancelled` and the "
"refusal is recorded in the :ref:`signature request's activity logs and "
"chatter <sign/request-signatures/manage-form>`. Any other signers are "
"notified and any remaining signers can no longer sign the document."
msgstr ""
"Zahteva za podpis je nato označena kot :guilabel:`Preklicana` in zavrnitev "
"je zabeležena v :ref:`dnevniku aktivnosti in klepetu zahteve za podpis <sign/"
"request-signatures/manage-form>`. Vsi drugi podpisniki so obveščeni in "
"preostali podpisniki ne morejo več podpisati dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/sign_document.rst:139
